Umubare w'abarwayi ba coronavirus (COVID-19) biyongereye cyane mu Burayi no mu Bwongereza hagati ya tariki ya 1 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abarwayi ba coronavirus (COVID-19) ugenda wiyongera mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, bityo bikagaragaza ko nubwo ibihugu bitandukanye byagiye bifata ingamba zitandukanye mu iterambere ryabyo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu byose.
Urebye ibyo Ubutaliyani bwagezeho, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bikeneye kongera ubushobozi bwo kwitegura ku buryo bwo guhangana n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kuvurwa, cyane cyane mu by'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, habonetse abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'ibihaha idasanzwe.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyorezo cyatewe n'ubwoko bushya bwa koronavirusi, ubu izwi nka koronavirusi y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero y'ubwoko bwa 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yatangiye kwitwa ubwandu bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Amakuru kugeza ubu avuga ko hafi 80% by'abantu barwaye COVID-19 barwara indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara y'ubuhumekero irimo cyangwa idafite ibicurane by'ubuhumekero, kandi abenshi barakira.
Hafi 14 ku ijana by'abantu banduye COVID-19 barwara indwara ikomeye cyane, bityo bagakenera kujya mu bitaro, naho abandi 6 ku ijana barwara indwara ikomeye cyane, bityo bagakenera kuvurwa mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa bavurwa COVID-19 ni 4% by'abamaze kuvurwa.
Ubu bushakashatsi bugenzura uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 buhagaze muri buri gihugu cy'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) / mu karere k'ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EEA) no mu Bwongereza, bugasuzuma uko buhagaze mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone turagereranya imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'ibyabonetse mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'aho COVID-19 itangiriye mu Bushinwa, yageze no mu bindi bihugu, kandi ubu mu bindi bice by'isi, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kugenda gifata indi ntera nk'uko byagenze mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Mu igazeti ya Eurosurveillance yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Bwana Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko hari abantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi, bujuje ibisabwa na OMS.
Abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye muri EU/EEA banditswe mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020  bose uko ari batatu bagarutse baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bagaragaye mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe kuva ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza kuri iyo tariki, hamaze kugaragara abantu 39 768 banduye n'abantu 1 727 bapfuye, muri bo 17 750 barimo 1 441 bapfuye, ni mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kumenya umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 n'umubare w'ababarirwa mu barwayi ba COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) buri munsi saa munani z'amanywa cyasubukura imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, kibikesha amakuru y'ibiro by'ubuzima by'ibyo bihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere ndetse na OMS.
Aya makuru akoreshwa mu gusesengura uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza no kuyasangira n'ibyavuye mu Butaliyani.
Kugira ngo hagaragazwe urugero rw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, hashyizweho imibare y'ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 mu minsi 14 hashingiwe ku mibare isanzwe ya COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twerekanye imibare y'abarwayi bose bari muri buri gihugu ku isaha ya saa munani z'ijoro ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, tugereranyije n'abari mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imiterere y'ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange yari ihuje n'imiterere y'ubwandu bwabonetse mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (ishusho ya 1).
Umubare w'abarwayi bose banduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange watangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, maze ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 habaho kuzamuka cyane (inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'abanduye muri Italy, ariko kandi mu bindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, habayeho kwiyongera nk'uko mu bihugu byinshi (inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'umubare nk'uwo mu Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Aya makuru avuga ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani z'amanywa mu bindi bihugu 15 bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, ugereranywa n'uw'abari baranduye mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara y'ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 ituma twumva ko iki cyorezo kigenda gifata indi ntera mu bihugu byose.
Ibi kandi n'ubwo ibihugu bitandukanye bifite ibihe bitandukanye, uburyo butandukanye inzego z'ubuzima z'igihugu zitabira, ndetse wenda n'uburyo butandukanye bwo kumenya abarwayi n'amategeko atandukanye yo gutoranya abarwayi kugira ngo basuzumwe COVID-19, harimo no gupima "kuzongera".
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twazahajwe na COVID-19 batangaje ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi bakeneye kuvurwa mu byumba by'indembe, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe byo muri utwo turere byuzuye.
Kugeza ubu, amakuru y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bageze mu bitaro no mu byumba by'indembe muri EU/EEA ari kuri 6%, naho ku barwayi 1%, (amakuru ntatangwa).
Ariko kandi, hakenewe gukusanya amakuru nk'ayo mu buryo buhoraho kugira ngo habeho kongeramo amakuru y'ubugenzuzi bugenda bukorwa, agaragaza umubare w'abanduye n'abamaze gupfa.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-2011 mu Burayi, hari itandukaniro rikomeye mu mibare y'ibitanda mu byumba by'indembe n'ibyumba by'indembe: kuva ku miterere 29,2 mu Budage kugeza ku miterere 4,2 ku bantu 100,000 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibindi bihugu bishobora kuba bifite ibikoresho byinshi cyangwa bike ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (ibitanda 12,5 mu bigo by'indembe n'iby'indembe ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-2011).
Raporo ya gatandatu iheruka gusubirwamo ya ECDC ku byavuye mu igenzura ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 yerekana uko imibare y'ubwiyongere bw'ubwisungane mu kwivuza mu bihugu byose by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza igaragaza ko ibitanda biboneka mu bigo by'indembe bidashobora kuboneka, aho ibyago byo kubura ibitanda biri hejuru ya 90%.
Kubera ko ubu abantu banduye mu karere runaka ka EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bikunze kwita ku baturage bo mu gace runaka, amakuru ajyanye n'ubwandu n'umubare w'ibitanda mu byumba by'indembe, aho bishoboka, byatangwa hakurikijwe urwego rwa 2 rw'ibarurishamibare (NUTS-2).
Uburyo bw'Ubutaliyani n'ibindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ni yo mpamvu ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bigomba kwitegura ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu buryo bw'imibonano mpuzabitsina, kandi ntiyigabanuke mu gihe kirekire, ndetse n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ukomeza kwiyongera, bagakenera ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bw'indembe, nk'uko bigaragara mu turere two mu Butaliyani twugarijwe n'iyo ndwara.
Nk'uko byavuzwe muri raporo ya vuba y'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya indwara (ECDC) ku byavuye mu igenzura ry'ibyago, uburyo bwihuse, bw'ubwirinzi n'ubw'ubushakashatsi ni ingenzi mu gukumira ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2 nyuma yo kuva ku gukumira bukagera ku kugabanya ingaruka, kuko mu gihe imibare y'abarwayi igenda yiyongera cyane, abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro bishobora kutagira igihe gihagije cyo gutekereza, gufata ingamba no guhinduka mu buryo bukwiriye, niba izo ngamba zitafashwe hakiri kare.
Raporo y'ibyavuye mu isesengura ry'ibyago ry'ibiza kandi ivuga ku ngamba zo mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange zigamije kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Ibihugu bifite igihe gito cyo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya umutwaro ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Niba ibyo bidakozwe, mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zishobora guhura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'indembe.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na coronavirus y'uburwayi bukomeye bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (SARS) bw'ubwoko bwa 2 (SARS-CoV-2), cyabaye ibyago ku bantu: kugeza ubu mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi abantu barenga 3 000 barapfuye, naho umubare w'abanduye urenga 80 000.
Kimwe na virusi ya SARS-CoV ya mbere yateje indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwanduzwa n'imbeba kandi igatera ibimenyetso bisa n'ibyo ikoresheje uburyo nk'ubwo.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buke n'ubukana buke ugereranyije na SARS, ariko yandura cyane kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza ku mubare w'ibitabo by'indwara nshya bigenda byiyongera, iyi nkuru itanga isuzuma ry'ingenzi kandi ryuzuye ku ngingo y'ubushakashatsi yihuta.
Tuzareba ibintu by'ibanze biranga indwara z'ibyorezo, impamvu zitera indwara, virusi, gusuzuma, kuvura, kwitegura no kwirinda iyi ndwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitarasobanuka, twizeye ko iyi raporo izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyi ndwara iteje akaga.
Umunsi mukuru w'ihinga (umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa), wabereye ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020, wabaye ikintu kitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose, kubera ko kubera icyorezo gishya cya virusi basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cyose cy'uwo munsi mukuru ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma yaho.
Bitewe n'aho ihuriye cyane na koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze cyane (SARS) mu 2003, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 ryise iyi virusi SARS-CoV-2, naho indwara iherekejwe na yo  coronavirus infection 19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose, hanyuma kigera mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, abantu barenga 80.000 bari bamaze kwandura COVID-19, abarenga 40.000 barakize, abarenga 3.000 barapfuye.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere ku baturage" kandi ishobora kuba mbi kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hari inyandiko zisaga 200 zasohotse ku bijyanye na COVID-19, harimo inyandiko zivuga ku ndwara, indwara z'ibyorezo, indwara, gusuzuma no kuvura, guhera kuri raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, yagaragaje uko virusi yakurikiranye mu barwayi benshi.
Iyi raporo ni ugushaka gusobanura ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi mu gice gishya kandi kiri gutera imbere vuba.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na koronavirusi  indwara y'ubushyuhe bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS), yaturutse mu 2012.
Tuzaganira kandi ku bimenyekanye kugeza ubu ku bijyanye no kwirinda no guhanura uko indwara izagenda, ndetse n'ibindi bibazo bimwe na bimwe byihutirwa.
Koronavirusi isanzwe iri mu ndwara ziterwa n'ubwandu butari buhitana abantu kandi ahanini zitera hafi 15% by'indwara zose z'ubuhumekero 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye inshuro ebyiri na koronavirusi zanduza abantu cyane, ari zo SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV, zatumye abantu benshi barwara, mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze zageze no mu bindi bihugu byinshi, ziteza indwara nyinshi n'urupfu rwinshi.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni yo ndwara ya gatatu ya koronavirusi yibasiye abantu.
Nkuko bigaragara mu ishusho ya 1.1, amakuru y'ibikoresho by'imiterere y'indwara y'ubuhumekero butaramenyekana, yatangiriye muri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya China, ivuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, urutonde rw'ibinyabuzima bya virusi rwarasohotse.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wapfuye muri Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyahise gikwira mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, byamenyekanye ko abakozi b'ubuvuzi banduye, bituma bishoboka ko virusi ishobora kwanduzwa n'umuntu ikajya ku wundi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu mujyi wa Wuhan hashyizweho gahunda yo kugenzura abantu, imodoka z'abaturage zarahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe kuri iki cyorezo bwagaragaje ko 21 mu barwayi 41 banduye coronavirus bari bafitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho icyorezo cyaturutse.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari ikibazo cy'ubukene ku isi mu by'ubuzima rusange.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yategurwaga, iki cyorezo cyari cyakwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa hose, ndetse kikaba kimaze kugera mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (ishusho ya 2).
Bitewe n'uko ibintu bigenda byiyongera, urugero rw'ihindagurika ry'icyorezo n'ingaruka zabyo biracyari kugenzurwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8 866 bakorewe mu bigo bitandukanye, harimo n'abarwayi 4 021 banduye COVID-19, bwashyize ahagaragara ibi bikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
Abantu bose bafite imyaka y'ubukure bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, ariko abenshi muri bo bari hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
