Koronavirusi ni umuryango muto wa virusi nini z'uruhu, zirimo umuringa umwe wa RNA ufite icyo usobanura.
Zishobora kugabanywamo amoko ane ari yo alpha, beta, gamma na delta, muri yo alpha na beta coronaviruses bizwiho kwanduza abantu.
Iyo umuntu yanduye coronavirus zo mu bwoko bwa SARS na MERS, poroteyine ya glycoprotein yo mu nkokora (S) ifata ingirabuzimafatizo za angiotensin-converting enzyme yo mu bwoko bwa 2 (ACE2) na dipeptidylpeptidaze-4 (DPP4), hanyuma ikora isanzuramuco.
Muri cytoplasma, genome ya RNA ya virusi irasohoka; nyuma yo gusubiramo genome ya virusi, genome ya RNA hamwe na poroteyine za glycoproteins na poroteyine za nucleocapsid zitanga virion zirimo vesicles, nyuma zifatanya na membrane y'ingirabuzimafatizo, zigasohora virusi.
