SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kandi gukora poroteyine y'igihe gito itari izwi mbere, ifite kode ya orf3b, n'indwara y'imyanda ifite kode ya orf8.
Poroteyine ya SARS-CoV-2 orf3b ishobora kugira uruhare mu gutuma virusi igira ubwandu kandi igahagarika IFNβ; ariko orf8 nta gice cy'imikorere cyangwa impamvu izwi ifite.
