Bityo rero, dushobora kwifashisha gusa ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku zindi koronavirusi, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (ishusho (ishusho 4).4).
Ubusanzwe, virusi yinjiye mu mubiri w'umushitsi, mbere na mbere imyanya ndangagitsina iba imenya ko ari virusi binyuze mu byuma by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri (ORR), harimo ibifite umusemburo wa C, Toll, NOD na RIG-I.
Binyuze mu buryo butandukanye, virusi ituma ibintu by'ubuhumekero biboneka, ingirabuzimafatizo za dendrites zigakura, na interférons z'ubwoko bwa I zigakora, zihagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi kandi zikihutisha fagocytose y'ama-macrophage ku bijyanye na antigène za virusi.
Icyakora, kubera poroteyine ya N, SARS-CoV ishobora kwirinda kugira icyo ikora ku mubiri.
Bidatinze, umubiri uratangira guhangana n'iyo virusi.
T-lymphocyte, harimo CD4+ na CD8+, zigira uruhare runini mu kurinda umubiri.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za CD4+ zitera inkunga iterwa ry'utugingo ngengakamere tw'ubwoko bwa virusi mu ngirabuzimafatizo za B, naho CD8+ zitera inkunga iterwa n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwoko bwa T zihitana virusi.
T-helper zitanga cytokines zifasha mu kurwanya ububabare.
Icyakora, koronavirusi ishobora kubuza imikorere y'utugingo twa T, bigatuma dupfa.
