Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bavuye mu murwayi wakize, bashoboye kuvanaho MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bufite ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'indwara butuma habaho ibinyigishi byinshi by'umwanda, bishobora kwangiza ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu gihe kibi cyane bikavamo kudakora neza kw'ingingo nyinshi ndetse no gupfa.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2, igaragara mu matsinda, ishobora kwandura cyane abantu bakuze bafite uburwayi bufatika n'abagore batwite.
