Ikimenyetso cy'ibanze cya COVID-19 ni umuriro mwinshi, ushobora kuba ari wo wonyine cyangwa ukaba ujyanirana n'ibindi bimenyetso, urugero nk'umusonga utose, guhumeka nabi, ububabare mu bice by'umubiri, kugira iseseme, umutwe, kubabara mu muhogo, imbeho, kubabara mu gatuza, iseseme, kugira iseseme no gusubiranamo.
Bamwe mu barwayi bamaze icyumweru batangiye kugaragaza impumuro nke n' (cyangwa) impumuro nke.
Mu bihe bikomeye, indwara yagendaga yiyongera vuba, maze abarwayi bagatangira kurwara indwara y'ubuhumekero, sepsis, acidosis y'umubiri n'uburwayi bw'amaraso.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro mwinshi n'ibimenyetso by'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'umuriro ukabije, bagomba gusuzumwa kuri virusi kugira ngo bagaragaze indwara hakiri kare, nubwo nta ndwara zigaragara ku mashusho y'igituza.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019, bwagaragaje ibimenyetso bikurikira: 98%  umuriro mwinshi, 76%  inkorora yumye, 55%  guhumeka nabi na 3%  kuribwa cyane; 8% by'abarwayi basabwaga guhumeka mu bihaha.
Ibisubizo nk'ibyo byabonetse mu bushakashatsi bubiri buheruka bwakozwe ku bantu banduye virusi mu miryango no ku bantu batanduye bayanduye nta bimenyetso.
Ibisubizo bisa n'ibyo byabonetse mu mwaka wa 2012 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi barwaye MERS-CoV, bagaragazaga ibimenyetso by'ingenzi birimo umuriro mwinshi (98%) no kugira inkorora yumye (47%) no guhumeka nabi (55%).
Icyakora, 80% by'abo bantu bari bakeneye guhumeka mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, ibyo bikaba ari byinshi ugereranyije n'abarwayi ba COVID-19, kandi bihuye n'umubare munini w'abapfa bazize MERS ugereranyije na COVID-19.
Abarwayi barwaye MERS kandi bagaragayeho kuribwa n'igifu (26%) n'ububabare bw'umuhogo (21%).
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'abarwayi ba SARS ni umuriro mwinshi (99100 %), inkorora yumye (2975 %), guhumeka nabi (4042 %), impiswi (2025 %) n'ububabare mu muhogo (1325 %), naho guhumeka kw'ibihaha by'abantu 1420 %.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, umubare w'abapfa bishwe na COVID-19 wari 2%, mu gihe umubare w'abamaze kwandura ku isi wose wari 66,576.
Mu kugereranya n'iki kigereranyo, umubare w'abapfa kubera SARS mu Ugushyingo 2002 wari 10% ku bantu 8,096 bari bamaze kwemezwa.
Ku bijyanye na MERS, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Kamena 2012 bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abapfa ku bantu 2,494 bagaragaye ari 37%.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko igipimo cy'ibanze cy'ubwiyongere (R0) cya SARS-CoV-2 cyari 6.47 mu gihe 95% by'ibipimo by'icyizere (CI) byari hagati ya 5.717.23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV yari hagati ya 2 na 4.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARA-CoV mu kugaragaza ibimenyetso, igipimo cy'urupfu na R0 bigaragara mu mbonerahamwe.
Ibipimo byavuzwe haruguru bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko igipimo cy'urupfu mu gihe umuntu yandura virusi nshya kiri hasi ugereranyije na bya bindi byombi.
Ku bw'ibyo, kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 bizagorana cyane kurusha icyorezo cya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Kwirakwira mu matsinda akenshi biba mu gihe ubwandu buba mu muryango umwe cyangwa mu itsinda ry'abantu bari hamwe kubera impamvu runaka cyangwa bari kumwe mu buryo runaka bw'ingendo, urugero nko mu bwato bw'ubwato.
Abarwayi bakunze kujya mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu tundi turere twazahajwe n'icyorezo, bakahaba cyangwa bagasohokana n'abanduye cyangwa abarwayi mu byumweru bibiri bishize mbere y'uko batangira kurwara.
Icyakora, raporo zigaragaza ko abantu bashobora kuba bafite virusi nta bimenyetso bagaragaza mu gihe kirenze ibyumweru bibiri, kandi ko abakize bashobora kongera kuyandura bakirukanwa mu bitaro, ibyo bikaba ari ikimenyetso cy'uko igihe cyo kuguma mu kato gishobora kongerwa.
Mu cyiciro cya mbere, abarwayi bagira umubare usanzwe cyangwa ugabanutse wa leukocyte (cyane cyane lymphocyte) mu maraso y'impande.
Urugero, abarwayi 1 099 barwaye COVID-19 basanganywe indwara y'imyanya y'amaraso ifite ingano y'utugingo tw'amaraso < 4×109/L, harimo n'ingano y'utugingo tw'amaraso < 1×109/L, hamwe n'indwara y'indwara ya Asparagin-aminotransferase n'indwara ya virusi.
Mu maraso y'abarwayi bamwe na bamwe, basanze ingano z'amafunguro yo mu myanya y'ububabare, ingano z'umusatsi n'imyakura yo mu mubiri (myoglobin) ari nyinshi, mu gihe abenshi basanze ingano z'umusemburo wa C-reactive protein n'imyanda y'amaraso ari nyinshi.
Abarwayi bari bafite indwara ikomeye, bari bafite D-dimer, ikorwa mu kuvunagura fibrin mu maraso, yariyongereye, kandi umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso (lymphocyte) wagendaga ugabanuka.
Abenshi mu barwayi ba COVID-19 bagaragaweho indwara z'ubuhumekero mu gihe cyo gufata amashusho y'igituza, zigaragaramo ubumuga butandukanye bw'ibice byombi cyangwa ubumuga bwo mu bihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira indwara y'ibihaha, indwara y'ibihaha n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Iyo indwara y'ubuhumekero idategekwa, kubyimba, gutakaza amazi no gutera imbere kwa fibrose bituma habaho guhungabana kw'umwuka.
Imikorere mibi y'utugingo tw'ibihaha tw'ubwoko bwa I na II igabanya igipimo cy'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibihaha kandi igatuma ibihaha birushaho gukomera, bityo bikongera ibyago byo gukonja.
Bityo rero, ibisubizo bibi cyane bya radiyo akenshi bijyana n'indwara zikomeye.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isuzuma rya mbere rya COVID-19 ryerekanye ko uduhimba tw'ibihaha twashyize hamwe, twashyize hamwe n'udupira tw'amahembe n'udupira tw'ibihaha, kandi uturemangingo tw'amahembe tw'ibihaha tw'abarwayi bapfuye tugereranya indwara z'ubwandu bwa virusi na SARS, kandi ni nk'izo mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Uburyo bwo gutahura RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa polymerase chain reaction (PCR) ikora transcriptase isimbuza, ni bwo bwakoreshejwe cyane mu gusuzuma COVID-19.
Icyakora, kubera ko ibipimo byinshi by'ibisubizo bibi by'ikinyoma bishobora kwihutisha iterambere ry'icyorezo, kuva ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020, mu Bushinwa batangiye gusuzuma indwara bashingiye ku bimenyetso by'uburwayi (batakomeje kwishingikiriza gusa kuri PCR ifite transcriptase isubiramo).
Ni na ko byagenze ku barwayi ba SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, kugira ngo umuntu ashobore gusobanukirwa neza indwara, ni ngombwa ko ashyira hamwe amakuru y'amateka y'uburwayi, ibimenyetso by'uburwayi, ibizamini byo muri laboratwari n'ibisubizo by'imashini z'imashini z'ikoranabuhanga.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga riyobowe na Bwana Feng Zhang ryanditse uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye ku gusubiramo CRISPR mu gutahura SARS-CoV-2; ubwo buryo butuma haboneka ibice bya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 byakozwe mu buryo bw'imikorere ku bunini kuva kuri 20 × 1018 mol/l kugeza kuri 200 × 1018 mol/l (10100 kopi kuri microlitiro y'icyitegererezo cy'ibanze) hifashishijwe uturaso tw'ibimenyetso mu gihe kitarenze isaha, hatakoreshejwe ibikoresho bikomeye.
Ubu buryo bushya, niba bwaratsinze igeragezwa ku miti, bushobora kongera cyane ubushishozi n'ubworoherane mu gupima.
Kubera ko nta buhanga bwo guhangana na coronavirus yari itaraboneka, abaganga bashobora guha abarwayi COVID-19 imiti y'ubufasha gusa, ariko bagerageza gukoresha uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mu kuvura izindi koronavirusi, urugero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe ya 2).2).
Ubwo buryo bwo kuvura burimo gukoresha cyangwa bushobora gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi, imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, siteroyi, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa no gutanga ubufasha bwo mu mutwe.
Byatangajwe ko no gukoresha plasma y'abarwayi bakize byajya bifashishwa mu kuvura.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi yihutira gukora antibody n'inkingo zo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Mu byiciro bya mbere, SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha, ariko ishobora no kugira ingaruka nke ku bindi bice by'umubiri byerekana ACE2, urugero nk'urwungano rw'amaraso n'impyiko.
Nyamara, guhungabana no kunanirwa guhumeka ni byo bintu by'ingenzi bibangamiye abarwayi kandi ni byo bituma bapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, kugira ngo biborohereze ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima, ni ngombwa cyane ko habaho ubufasha bwo guhumeka, harimo imiti rusange ya ogisijeni, umwuka mwinshi, guhumeka mu buryo butari ubunyamwuga no guhumeka mu buryo bw'imashini, bitangwa hakurikijwe ubukana bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka bakeneye ubufasha mu buryo bw'umwuka uturuka mu nkingo z'umubiri (ECMO), uburyo bwo kuvura indwara z'umutima cyangwa z'ubuhumekero.
Byongeye kandi, ni ngombwa cyane ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 gukomeza kugira amazi n'umunyu mu mubiri, kwirinda no kuvura indwara z'ibyorezo n'imyanda y'ibinure, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi.
Birazwi ko cytocin storm ari ingaruka z'ingaruka z'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara z'abarwayi banduye SARS na MERS.
Cytokine storm ni uburyo bw'imiterere y'ubuhumekero bukomoka ku kwanduza umubiri, buterwa no kwanduza ibindi bice by'umubiri, harimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ na MCP-1.
Izi cytokines zitera abasirikare b'umubiri kurekura ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi cyane z'umwanda, zikaba ari zo mpamvu nyamukuru zitera indwara ya ADD n'ubumuga bw'ingingo nyinshi.
Mu kuvura cytocin storm, cyane cyane ku barwayi bafite uburwayi bukabije, guhagarika ubudahangarwa ni ingenzi.
Kuvura cytocin cyorezo, corticosteroids na tocilizumab, intanga z'umubiri umwe zikorera nk'ubufasha bwo guhagarika interleukin-6, zakoreshejwe.
Mu bundi buryo bwo kuvura cytocin inkubi y'umuyaga bushingiye ku gukumira ubudahangarwa, harimo guhindura ibisubizo by'ubudahangarwa bigamije kugenzura ingirabuzimafatizo za T; guhagarika imikorere ya cytocin IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; gukumira i-yanus-kinase; gukoresha blinatumomamab, suppressors ya cytocin 4 na inhibitors ya histondeacetalase.
Kugira ngo bagabanye ubukana bw'ingaruka z'imihango y'ubuhumekero mu kuvura virusi za SARS, steroid zikoreshwa cyane nk'izirwanya ubudahangarwa.
Icyakora, imiti ya Steroid mu bipimo byinshi nta cyo imaze mu kuvura uburwayi bukomeye bw'ibihaha mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo bishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye cyane cyane indwara y'amagufa yo mu magufa, bigatuma umuntu atabasha kwivuza.
Icyakora, imiti ya kortikosteroïde y'igihe gito mu doze nto n'izisanzwe, ihabwa inama yo gukoreshwa mu bwitonzi mu kuvura abarwayi bafite COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
