Mu yandi magambo, abo bombi bashobora kwitwa ko ari bo bonyine barokotse ibyorezo bya coronavirus mu gihe cyashize.
Koronavirusi z'abantu zitera indwara zikomeye mu bantu, n'abantu zitera indwara zikomeye mu bantu, ntizigeze zirokoka.
Kugira ngo ibyo bibe, koronavirusi y'umuntu igomba kwiyongera mu mubiri w'umuntu ku buryo buhagije kugira ngo ibone uburyo bwo guhinduranya imiterere y'umubiri, bigatuma ikumira uwo uyitwara.
Muri ubwo buryo, uko igihe cyo kwandura SARS-CoV-2 kirushaho kwiyongera, n'abantu benshi kurushaho bagatangira kwandura, ni na ko bishoboka ko virusi ihinduka umuntu.
Iyo yifashe neza, kuyandura mu bantu bizagorana kubihagarika binyuze mu kwishyiriraho gahunda yo kugenzura indwara zandurira mu bantu cyangwa izindi ngamba zo kugenzura indwara zandurira mu bantu.
Mu myaka myinshi, abantu benshi bagiye bahura n'ubwoko bune bwa koronavirusi buturuka hanze y'ibitaro butera ibicurane bisanzwe mu bantu bafite ubwirinzi busanzwe.
Iyi virusi ntiyikeneye inyamaswa yo kuyirinda.
Koronavirusi zandura cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV ntizihuza neza n'abantu, bityo ntizishobora gukomeza kwanduzanya.
Bisaba kubana no kororoka mu bigega byabo by'ibinyabuzima no gushaka uburyo bwo kugera ku bantu bashobora kuba babigirira nabi, wenda binyuze mu muvuduko umwe cyangwa myinshi cyangwa mu buryo bwo kongera.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibimenyetso bisa n'ibya SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV na virusi enye zo hanze ya bitaro za HCoV.
Biroroshye cyane ko yandura nk'iyo muri HCoV zitari mu bitaro, nibura ubu.
Ariko ifite ubukana burenze ubwa HCoV zituruka hanze y'ibitaro, kandi nta bwandu bwinshi bufite kurusha SARS-CoV cyangwa MERS-CoV.
Biracyari kugenzurwa niba izahuza n'abantu kandi ikagenda mu bantu nta mazi cyangwa ikagenda n'inyamaswa.
Mbere yo kuganira ku nkomoko y'inyamaswa ya virusi ya HCoV, byaba byiza tubanje gusuzuma ibisobanuro n'ibiranga virusi z'ubwihindurize, ibidukikije, ibisanzwe, ibikuza n'ibikingira virusi ya HCoV.
Inyamaswa ni yo itwara HCoV mu buryo bw'ihindagurika iyo ifite mwene wabo wa bugufi ufite uko guhuza kw'ibanze kwa nucleotide.
Iyi virusi y'umwuzukuru ubusanzwe iba ifite ubushobozi bwo kwihanganira indwara kandi nta ndwara igira.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera SIDA buhoraho igihe kirekire.
Muri ibyo bihe byombi, abanduye banduye mu buryo busanzwe kandi ni ba nyirabayazana ba HCoV cyangwa virusi y'ababyeyi bayo.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo HCoV yanduye mu muntu wa mbere mbere cyangwa nyuma y'aho yanduye, ntiyari ikwiriye uwo muntu mushya kandi akenshi ishobora gutera indwara.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba ari yo ituma abantu banduza, kandi ishobora kuba ari yo ituma iyi virusi ikwirakwira cyane, ikongera ikagera ku bantu, bityo ikongera ubukana bw'ubwandu.
HCoV ishobora kwanduza mu buryo butemewe iyo idashobora guhangana n'ubwandu mu mubyimba w'inyuma.
Ku rundi ruhande, virusi za HCoV zishobora no kwihanganira ubwandu bw'igihe kirekire ndetse no kuba zidakomeza kubaho.
Muri iki gihe, umuterankunga usanzwe uba umuterankunga w'ibikoresho.
Ibipimo by'ubuvuzi byerekanye ko umurwayi wa SARS wa mbere yari afite amateka y'ubwandu bw'inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma bwagaragaje ko abacuruza amatungo bafite IgG nyinshi cyane kurusha abandi bantu.
Ibinyamushongo byo mu misozi ya Himalaya (Paguma larvata) n'imbwa z'ingore ziri ku masoko y'amatungo ni byo bya mbere byemejwe ko byanduye virusi zimeze nka SARS-CoV.
Ibi byemejwe n'uko nyuma yo kurandura ibibyimba byose mu masoko nta bindi bibazo bya SARS byongeye gutangazwa.
Muri icyo gihe, byavuzwe ko mu bantu benshi bo mu misozi ya Himalaya baba mu ishyamba cyangwa mu mirima, SARS-CoV itarashyirwa ku isoko, bityo bikaba byemeza ko imisozi ya Himalaya ishobora kuba yarakoreshejwe nk'umuvuduko wo kongera ubukana bwa SARS-CoV, aho kuba nk'ikigega cy'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV.
Birashishikaje kuba 80% by'inyamaswa zitandukanye zo mu masoko ya Guangzhou zifite abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV, ntibishoboka ko hari amoko menshi y'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bito na byo bishobora kuba ari byo bitwara virusi.
Bose basa n'abari mu nzira yo gutwara virusi ya SARS-CoV.
Ubushakashatsi bwakurikiyeho bwo gushakisha inyamaswa z'ibanze zitwara SARS-CoV bwagaragaje CoV ya mu ngurube ifitanye isano ya bugufi, yitwa HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3) ifitanye isano na Pneumonia y'indwara y'imyanya y'ubuhumekero idasanzwe, kandi iboneka mu ngurube z'Abashinwa.
Iyi mbeba ifite abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV na SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3 bakurikirana mu bwoko bw'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Izi n'izindi koronavirusi z'imbeba zifite 8892% z'imiterere y'udupira tw'ubwoko bumwe na SARS-CoV.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bwatumye hashyirwaho urufatiro rw'igitekerezo gishya cy'uko udusimba twabaye utwo gutwara indwara nshya z'abantu.
Mu mbeba z'inzererezi kandi habonetse koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe zisa na SARS (SL-CoV), ariko nta na imwe muri zo, uretse imwe yitwa WIV1, ishobora gutandukanywa nk'indwara nzima.
Tuzi ko SARS-CoV ifata neza virusi ya SARS, ikagira ingirabuzima fatizo 2 zihindura angiotensin (ACE2).
Byaragaragaye ko WIV1 yakuwe mu cyuma cy'imyanda y'imbeba, ikoresha ACE2 y'imbeba, cyvet n'umuntu nk'urwego rw'imikorere yo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Igishishikaje ni uko serum z'abarwayi ba SARS bakize zishobora kuba zarashoboye guhashya WIV1.
Kugeza ubu, WIV1 ni yo nkomoko ya SARS-CoV iri hafi cyane mu mbeba, ifite 95% by'urusobe rwa nucleotide.
Nubwo izo virusi zombi zifite aho zihuriye cyane, muri rusange abantu batekereza ko WIV1 atari virusi y'ababyeyi ya SARS-CoV, kandi ko udukoko tutari ba nyirabyo wa SARS-CoV.
Ubushakashatsi ku miterere y'ibinyabuzima bwashyize MERS-CoV mu itsinda rimwe na CoV-HKU4 y'imbeba n'iyo mu mbeba.
CoV-HKU4 y'imbeba n'indwara ya MERS-CoV zikoresha imikorere imwe y'indwara ya dipeptildipeptidase-4 (DPP4) mu kwinjiza virusi.
Urukurikirane rwa RNA-rwishingikirije kuri RNA-polymerase ya virusi ya MERS-CoV ni rwo rwegereye cyane urukurikirane rwa betacoronavirus z'imbeba mu buryo bwa phylogenetically, zisanzwe zigaragara mu Burayi no muri Afurika.
Kugeza ubu nta virusi ya MERS-CoV y'ubuzima yigeze iboneka mu ducurama tw'inyamaswa.
Igisobanuro kimwe cy'imiterere ya nucleotide ya MERS-CoV n'iy'umuvandimwe wayo wa hafi CoV-HKU25 mu mbeba z'inzererezi gihuriweho ku kigero cya 87%.
Ibyo bisobanura ko udusimba dushobora kuba tutari dufite virusi ya MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati bwagaragaje ko ingamiya z'ingore z'ingore zifite seropositive ku misemburo ihagarika indwara ya MERS-CoV, kimwe n'ingamiya zo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati ziri mu bihugu byinshi bya Afurika.
MERS-CoV nzima, isa n'iyo mu bantu, yabonetse mu misogoto y'izuru y'ingamiya z'igitsina kimwe, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko ingamiya ari zo z'ukuri zitwara MERS-CoV.
Ni ngombwa kandi kumenya ko ingamiya zanduye MERS-CoV mu buryo bw'igerageza zagaragaje ibimenyetso bike ariko zikaba zaragize ubukana bwinshi.
Igishishikaje ni uko ingamiya zanduye zitashyize virusi mu nzira y'ubuhumekero gusa, ahubwo zinashyize iyi virusi mu nzira y'umwotsi, nayo ikaba ari inzira y'ibanze yo gushyiramo virusi mu mbeba.
Ariko ibibazo biracyariho kuko abenshi mu banduye indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati batigeze bagira aho bahurira n'ingamiya mbere y'uko bagaragaza ibimenyetso kandi birashoboka ko byaturutse ku muntu ku wundi cyangwa ku buryo butaramenyekana, harimo n'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa zitamenyekanye zikwirakwiza MERS-CoV.
Igitsina cya SARS-CoV-2 gihuye na CoV RaTG13 mu mbeba ku kigero cya 96,2% mu nguge za Rhinolophus affinis zo muri Aziya.
Nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, itandukaniro ry'imiterere hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni rinini cyane ku buryo nta mubyeyi ushobora kubivugaho.
Ibyo bisobanura ko udukoko dushobora kuba tutari two twandujwe SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo butaziguye, keretse gusa mu gihe kizaza habonetse udukoko twa koronavirusi tw'imbeba twasaga n'aho duhuriye.
Bivugwa ko inyamaswa zitwara virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 zishobora kuba ziri mu nyamaswa z'inkazi zigurishwa kandi zicirwa ku isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho abantu benshi ba mbere banduye COVID-19 bagaragaye, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko zishobora kuba zanduye zinyuze mu matungo zijya ku bantu.
Ubushakashatsi butandukanye buherutse gukorwa bushingiye ku gupima metagenome bwagaragaje ko itsinda ry'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bw'ibinyamubiri bito ziri mu kaga, zizwi nka 'pangolin' (Manis javanica), zishobora kuba zigize beta-coronavirus y'ababyeyi, ifitanye isano n'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Igitereko cy'udupira tw'imikorere tw'utwo dupira dushya twa virusi ya corona tugereranya 8592% n'ubwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, zifitanye isano ya bugufi na RaTG13, aho kwihuza ku rwego rwa nucleotide ari hafi 90%.
Zishyira hamwe mu byiciro bibiri by'ubwoko bwa virusi, nk'iyi SARS-CoV-2, mu giti cy'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, kimwe muri byo gifite umurongo uhuza receptor (RCD) wegereye SARS-CoV-2 cyane, ufite umwihariko wa amino acide ungana na 97,4%.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, RSD z'udukoko twa SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ziratandukanye cyane nubwo zigaragaza ko zigenda zingana cyane muri za genomes zose.
Mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku bantu barwaye pandolines, nanone hari amakuru yavugaga ko hari ibimenyetso bya virusi mu bipimo by'ibihaha byagaragaye ko bifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi hakoreshejwe ubundi buryo bwo gukusanya no gutunganya intoki kugira ngo haboneke urutonde rwa jenome, rugizwe na 86,3% bya jenome yuzuye ya virusi.
Ntabwo twakwirengagiza ko iyo nyamaswa ishobora kuba ari imwe mu nyamaswa zitwara SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, kubera itandukaniro ry'imiterere hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na beta-coronavirus ya pangolin, afitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2, ubu nta bimenyetso bifatika bihamya ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse kuri pangolin.
Byongeye kandi, intera iri hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni ngufi cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV-2 na virusi ya beta ya coronavirus ya pangolin ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Inzira SARS-CoV-2 yanyuzemo mu nguge, mu bifi n'ibindi binyabuzima ntiziramenyekana.
Mu gihe homologue y'urukurikirane iruta izindi zose yagaragaye muri RCD hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na beta-coronavirus ya pangolin, bene wabo ba SARS-CoV-2, SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni zo zisanzwe zifite homologue y'urukurikirane iruta izindi muri jenome yose.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, urugero rwagutse rw'ubusabane hagati ya virusi ya coronavirusi ya beta ya pangolin, ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2, na SARS-CoV-2 ni uko byagiye bihinduka mu buryo bumwe binyuze mu guhitamo.
Igitekerezo kinyuranye n'icyo ni uko virusi ya Coronavirusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na RaTG13 mu bwoko bwa gatatu bw'inyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Nk'imbaraga zituma habaho iterambere, guhuza no kongera guteranya ibindi bikoko bya koronavirusi ni ibintu bikunze kubaho cyane.
Kugeza ubu nta mwanzuro uremeza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku nyamaswa.
Uretse virusi z'ubwandu bukomeye bwa HCoV, hari izindi virusi z'ubwoko bw'inyamaswa zigiye zigeragezwa, urugero nka HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-HKU1.
Ibihamya bya phylogenetic byerekana ko HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-229E byombi bishobora kuba byaturutse kuri koronavirusi z'imbeba, mu gihe virusi z'ababyeyi za HCoV-OC43 na HCoV-HKU1 zisanzwe ziboneka mu ducurama.
Bivugwa ko virusi ya coronavirusi y'ikinyugunyugu yitwa ARCoV.2 (Appalachian Ridge CoV) yagaragaye mu nyamaswa zo muri Amerika ya Ruguru z'amabara atatu, igaragaza isano ya hafi na HCoV-NL63.
Ku rundi ruhande, HCoV-229E ifitanye isano mu buryo bw'imiterere n'indi koronavirusi y'ikinyugunyugu yitwa Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, yavumbuwe muri Ghana, nubwo hari abakeka ko ishobora kuba yaturutse ku ngamiya.
Kugira ngo dusobanukirwe neza, ubumenyi bugezweho ku nkomoko y'inyamaswa za koronavirusi zizwi bwagarutsweho ku ishusho ya 1 no ku mbonerahamwe ya 2.
Ubushakashatsi ku bwoko bwa HCoV bwatanze ibimenyetso by'uko hari ubwandu bw'ubwoko bwa HCoV mu mateka.
Igihe virusi ya HCoV-OC43 yanduzwa n'inyamaswa zo mu rugo mu myaka ya 1890, abantu bahise banduzwa n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Amateka y'ubwandu bw'ubwoko bwa HCoV-229E ntabwo asobanutse neza.
Hasanzwe alphacoronavirus z'imbeba, zihuriyeho na HCoV-229E.
Hagati aho, hari alpha-coronavirus ya alpaca.
Hari ibimenyetso byemeza ko virusi ishobora kwanduzwa n'imbeba igatangira ku muntu.
Icya mbere, abantu, si alpacas, nibo bashoboraga guhura n'imbeba mu gace rusange k'ibidukikije.
Muri icyo gihe, abantu bagirana imishyikirano ya bugufi n'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa alpaca.
Icya kabiri, alphacoronavirus z'imbeba, zihuriye na HCoV-229E, mu mbeba ni nyinshi kandi ntizitera indwara, mu gihe alphacoronavirus ya alpaca yatumye inyamaswa zanduye zirwaye indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Amaherezo, alpaca alpha coronavirus ntiyabonetse mu nyamaswa zo mu gasozi.
Bityo, ntibishoboka ko alpaca yahawe alpha coronavirus, ifitanye isano na HCoV-229E, n'abantu.
Mu by'ukuri, udukoko ni two dukomokaho virusi zandura abantu, harimo virusi y'ibicurane, Ebola, Nipah na Hendrix.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibitangaje kuba udukoko dushobora kwanduza abantu HCoV-229E mu buryo butaziguye.
Ku rundi ruhande, mu gihe alpha-coronavirus zo mu ducurama zishobora kuba ari zo zigize virusi ya HCoV-229E, alpaca na ingamiya zo mu bwoko bw'ingamiya zishobora kuba ari zo zitwara virusi mu bantu, nk'uko byagenze kuri virusi ya MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV ni urugero rwiza rw'ubwandu bw'ubwoko butandukanye bw'indwara buturuka ku mbeba igera ku ngamiya z'ikiboko kimwe, ndetse n'ubw'ingamiya z'ikiboko kimwe zigera ku bantu.
Inkomoko y'ubwihindurize bwa virusi ya MERS-CoV mu ducurama irazwi kuva yamenyekana bwa mbere, nyuma y'aho byemejwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma.
Biragaragara ko udukoko dutanga ubwoko bwinshi bwa virusi zo guhanahana ibice by'ingirabuzima fatizo no kwanduzanya.
Imyaka myinshi, imiryango ituwe cyane, imikoranire ya hafi n'ubushobozi bwo kuguruka bituma udusimba tuba utwo twanduranya.
Ku rundi ruhande, virusi ya MERS-CoV yageze ku ngamiya z'ingamiya mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize.
Yiteguye neza kuri izi ngamiya, kuva ku mubyimba usanzwe kugeza ku mubyimba uhamye kandi usanzwe.
Muri izo nyamaswa, virusi ya MERS-CoV ituma indwara iba nke cyane kandi igaragaza ko ihinduka gake.
Kuyihinduranya n'indi ndwara ku bantu ni ibintu by'impanuka, kandi umuntu aba ari we utwara MERS-CoV mu buryo butemewe kuko nta buryo bwo kuyandura bwemewe.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uruhare rw'ingamiya mu kwanduza MERS-CoV, uruhare rw'ingona, niba ruriho, mu kwanduza SARS-CoV-2 ni urundi.
By'umwihariko, betacoronavirus ya pangolin ifite indwara nyinshi mu ngurube.
Bashobora kuba ari ba nyirabayazana ba beta-coronavirus, bafitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2, kimwe n'ibinyamushongo mu gihe cya SARS-CoV.
