Muri rusange, RSD ya poroteyine S ya coronavirus ifata mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga n'urwego rw'umusemburo w'ingirabuzimafatizo, maze igisubizo cy'umurwayi cy'umubiri w'inzoka kiyivanaho mu buryo bwihuse.
