Hakenewe kuvugurura ibipimo by'ubushakashatsi ku bantu bakekwaho ubwandu bwa COVID-19 n'abemejwe ko banduye
Ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryatangaje igitabo cy'ubuvanganzo ku byerekeye gusuzuma no kuvura icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV), kigaragaza ibyo twabonye n'inama z'ingirakamaro ku bijyanye no guhangana n'iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Icyakora, icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, bityo ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite byagiye byiyongera buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku bushakashatsi n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura na bwo bwagiye buhinduka.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije igitekerezo kimwe ku nama twabahaye, kandi tuvuga ibipimo bishya by'ubushakashatsi ku "bimwe mu bibazo bikekwaho" n' "bimwe mu byemejwe" nk'uko bivugwa mu nyandiko y'Icyemezo cyo Gusuzuma no Guciraho Ingamba COVID-19" (Inyandiko ya karindwi) cyatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, habaye icyorezo cya coronavirus nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV), ubu cyiswe coronavirus infection 2019 (COVID-19), kandi uburwayi bwa virusi bwiswe indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye igitabo cy'ubuvanganzo gito kandi kiragaragara kuri interineti ku rubuga rwa interineti rw'ikinyamakuru Military Medical Research ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020.
Icyo gitabo cyatumye abantu benshi babyitaho.
Tuzirikane ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, bityo ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite byagiye byiyongera buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku bushakashatsi n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura na bwo bwagiye buhinduka.
Urugero, kuva ku itariki ya 16 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, hasohowe impapuro ndwi z'Icyemezo cyo Gusuzuma no Guciraho Ingamba COVID-19 cyanditswe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), kandi ingingo zimwe na zimwe zaryo zarahindutse cyane.
Mu minsi ishize, Zhou n'abandi banditsi batanze ibitekerezo ku nama zacu, batanga inama z'uburyo bworoshye bwo gusuzuma indwara zishingiye ku buhamya bw'abaganga.
Iki gikorwa cyongereye ibindi bimenyetso ku nama zacu kandi gitanga amakuru y'ingenzi kuri iki cyorezo cyugarije isi.
Turemeza akamaro gakomeye k'umurimo wabo kandi tukabashimira.
Icyakora, ukurikije ibikubiye mu gitabo cya vuba cy'Ibyerekeranye no gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (igitabo cy'igerageza cya karindwi) n'ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi buri gukorwa, ibyo bitabo na byo bikeneye kuvugururwa.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu nyandiko ya karindwi (y'itariki ya 3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo haboneke ibimenyetso byose by'uburwayi, hagomba guhuzwa ibintu bibiri by'uburwayi:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa aho umuntu yagiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu nkengero zawo cyangwa ahandi hantu hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (2) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV-2 (bakoze ikizamini cyagaragaje ko banduye virusi itera SIDA) (3) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abarwayi bafite umuriro mwinshi cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu nkengero zawo cyangwa ahandi hantu hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (4) amateka y'abantu bari mu matsinda y'abantu banduye (≥2 barwaye umuriro mwinshi cyangwa barwaye ibicurane mu byumweru 2 mu byumba bito, nko mu ishuri, mu biro no mu nzu y'ishuri).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi: (1) umuriro mwinshi n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero; (2) ibimenyetso byo hanze bigaragaza ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'utugingo duto tw'umweru ni mwiza cyangwa uri hasi, n'umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso wagabanutse mu gihe ibimenyetso bitangiye kugaragara.
Gushakisha umuntu wemejwe ko arwaye bigomba gushingira ku kuba hari ibimenyetso bikurikira bigaragaza ko yanduye: (1) ibipimo bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 yanduye; (2) ukurikirana neza virusi bigaragaza ko hari ibintu byinshi bihuza virusi z'ubwoko bushya; (3) ibipimo bya seroteste bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite antibody IgM na IgG; cyangwa se ko igisubizo cy'ibizamini byavuye kuri IgG ifite antibody ya SARS-CoV-2 yanduye kijya kuri IgG, cyangwa se ko umubare w'abantu bakize wiyongereyeho nibura inshuro 4 ugereranyije n'ibipimo by'imiterere y'imiterere.
Birashoboka kandi ko mu nomero ya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'iya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020) y'icyo gitabo, hashyizweho ikigo cya PCR mu gihe nyacyo cyo gupima aside ya nucleine mu nzira z'ubuhumekero cyangwa ibipimo by'amaraso.
Gushakisha indwara ziterwa n'ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe mu nomero ya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no mu ya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma mu nomero ya karindwi, hakongerwaho icyemezo cya seroloji.
Izi mpinduka zishingiye ku bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abashakashatsi mu gushakisha uburyo bwiza bwo gutahura aside za nucleic mu gihe cyo gusuzuma vuba, no gusesengura ibipimo bifatwa mu nzira y'ubuhumekero, harimo no gufata ibipimo by'amaraso, bituma haboneka ibipimo bitandukanye kandi bigatuma ibipimo by'abanduye byongera kugaragara neza mu bipimo byemeza indwara.
Ariko kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko abantu bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe n'abadafite ibimenyetso runaka bagomba kwitondera imiti.
Bityo, ikarita y'inzira yatanzwe mu gitabo cya Zhou n'abandi, igomba kuvugururwa, kuko mu isomo ryayo abantu badafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi, bagaragazwa nk'itsinda ry'abafite ibyago bike.
Uburyo bwo gusuzuma bukeneye kandi gusobanurwa mu gihe cy'ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi n'ubushakashatsi.
Mu gusoza, turizera ko tuzabona ibimenyetso by'ukuri kandi turasaba abasomyi bacu kudusigira ibitekerezo.
Ku bijyanye no gusuzuma "imimerere ikekwaho ubwandu" na "imimerere yemejwe", turasaba abasomyi gukurikiza kandi bagakurikiza cyane amabwiriza aheruka atangwa mu bihugu batuyemo.
Itsinda ryacu rizongera kandi kuvugurura inama z'igihe cyabyo mu rwego rwo gutanga ubufasha bwiza.
Bangladesh yatangaje ko abantu batanu bashya bapfuye bazize COVID-19  umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi
