Amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya arimo kugabanya umubare w'impapuro z'isuku umuntu ashobora kugura
Ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Australia yitwa Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije umubare w'amakarito y'isuku ashobora kugurwa rimwe mu maduka yose yo mu gihugu, agera kuri abiri na rimwe.
Ku wa mbere ALDI nayo yashyizeho ihagarikwa ry'ipaki imwe.
Ibi bihano byatangajwe mu matangazo yo ku biro by'ubucuruzi ndetse no ku rubuga rwa Facebook.
Bivugwa ko abaturage batangiye kwitegura mu buryo bwihutirwa kubera ubwoba bw'uko COVID-19 ishobora gutuma abantu bose biyicarira bonyine.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije umubare w'impapuro z'isuku zigurwa ku isanduku imwe.
Mbere yaho, ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe, Woolworths na Coles bamaze kugabanya umubare w'ibyo bicuruzwa ku bipfunyika bine.
Mu itangazo ry'itangazamakuru ryo ku wa 8 Werurwe, urubuga rw'ubucuruzi rwa Coles rwatangaje ko kubera ko hari ibicuruzwa byinshi by'impapuro z'isuku byamaze gufungwa, ko abantu benshi bagura vuba cyane, ko hari impapuro z'isuku zishyirwa mu gihe cy'isaha, kandi ko ibyo bisabwa ari "bitigeze bibaho", mu gihe ALDI yo mu butumwa yashyize kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri, yavuze ko ari "ibitunguranye".
Nk'uko bivugwa n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths, mu cyumweru gishize habaye ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'ubucuruzi.
Ubucuruzi bwa Costco mu mujyi wa Canberra mu cyumweru gishize nabwo bwagabanyije umubare w'ibicuruzwa ku bipaki bibiri.
Kugira ngo haboneke ibiciro, Coles yatangiye gutumiza ibicuruzwa byinshi cyane kandi yongera umubare w'ibicuruzwa, Woolworths yatumije ibindi bicuruzwa, mu gihe ALDI yateguye ibicuruzwa byo kugurisha hakiri kare ku wa Gatatu.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi barimo bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa byabo, ariko bigoranye kubera amategeko agenga ingendo z'amakamyo.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa bizamuka kuko abaguzi bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo ariko hari ibicuruzwa bike cyane biboneka.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko hari amaduka adashobora gukora ibikorwa ku wa gatatu kubera kubura ibicuruzwa.
Mu nkuru yatanzwe na News.com.au, Dr. Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu bucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi muri kaminuza ya Queensland ikora iby'ikoranabuhanga, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibicuruzwa byayo buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ibintu bikomeye, bityo umubare w'ibicuruzwa biri mu bubiko ari muto, kandi ko nyuma yo kugurisha ibicuruzwa byose, imirongo miremire y'ibikoresho iba igaragara, bigatuma abantu bumva ko nta bikoresho bihagije.
Coles na Woolworths batekereza ko niba ibigega byashoboraga kuzura, kandi ibicuruzwa nk'impapuro z'isuku n'imiti yica udukoko mu ntoki bishobora gushyirwa kuri ibigega ku bwinshi, abakiriya bashobora kuba batagize ubwoba bwinshi, Russell Zimmerman avuga.
Ku wa gatatu w'icyumweru gishize, ikigo cy'imashini zikora impapuro z'isuku zisubiwemo, Who Gives a Crap, cyatangaje ko ibikoresho byacyo bigiye kurangira.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na News.com.au, Kimberly-Clark, ikora impapuro z'isuku za Kleenex na Solaris Paper, ikora n'ibikoresho bya Sorbent, bavuze ko bakora amasaha 24 ku munsi kugira ngo babone ibicuruzwa bihagije.
Domain.com, urubuga rw'ubucuruzi bw'imitungo, rwatangaje ko ubwo ibiciro by'idandazwa mu cyamunara byagabanukaga mu mujyi wa Melbourne kubera ko hari abataragura ku cyumweru cy'umunsi mukuru w'umurimo, bamwe mu bacuruzi batangiye guha abinjiye mu cyamunara impapuro z'isuku ku buntu.
Umunara wa kane w'ibanze wa NT News, usohoka buri munsi muri Darwin, wari ufite ipaji umunani zari zigenewe gukata no gukoreshwa nk'impapuro z'isuku.
Nk'uko bivugwa na ABC Australia yo ku wa 3 Werurwe, ku ikubitiro amaduka ntiyari ashishikajwe no gushyiraho imipaka ku bicuruzwa, avuga ko nta gahunda yo kubikora.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko ibindi bikoresho na byo byifuzwa cyane, birimo udupfukamunwa, imiti yica udukoko mu biganza, ibikoresho byo mu nzu, imiti yo gukaraba intoki n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, uretse ibyabaye muri Ositaraliya, ku Cyumweru nimugoroba byaravuzwe ko ububiko bwa Ocado bwo mu Bwongereza na bwo bwahagaritse kugurisha impapuro z'isuku za Andres mu dupaki tubiri tw'ibikoresho 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje icyorezo cya COVID-19
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibyorezo ya COVID-19, iterwa na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2, cyugarije isi yose.
Nubwo ijambo icyorezo ryerekeza gusa ku rugero rw'indwara, aho kwerekeza ku kaga k'ubwandu, OMS ivuga ko leta z'ibihugu zigomba gufata ingamba:
Ibihugu byose hamwe biracyafite ubushobozi bwo kugira icyo bikora ku iterambere ry'iki cyorezo.
Ibi bishobora gukorwa mu gihe ibihugu byiteguye kumenya, gupima, kuvura, gushyira abantu mu kato, gukurikirana ubwandu no guhuza abaturage babyo", ni ko Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze.
Turahangayikishijwe cyane n'umubare uteye impungenge w'ubwandu n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo, ndetse n'umubare uteye impungenge w'ibikorwa bidafatika.
Dr. Tom Friedan, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo ari "kitigeze kibaho".
Mu kiganiro yagiranye na CNN muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko nta virusi y'ubuhumekero itari ibicurane yari yarigeze ikwirakwira ku isi yose.
Bwana Gebreyesus yavuze ko na we yari afite icyo gitekerezo, avuga ko atigeze abona icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus.
Nanone kandi, nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Mu ntangiriro, muri Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukene mu buzima bw'abaturage gifite agaciro mpuzamahanga, hanyuma ikongeraho icyiciro cya  icyorezo.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Indwara z'Ibitera Mbonera n'Indwara Zandura, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ibi ku cyorezo: "Ni intangiriro gusa, bizagenda birushaho kuba bibi".
