Icyorezo cya coronavirus 20192020.  ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), iterwa na coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2).
Icyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, maze ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020 hatangazwa ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukene mu by'ubuzima bw'abaturage ku rwego mpuzamahanga, nyuma ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020 gitangazwa nk'icyorezo.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1,61 barwaye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 no mu turere dutandukanye, kandi hapfuye abantu bagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 bakize.
Igipimo cy'urupfu mu Bushinwa ni 4%, mu gihe ku isi yose gitandukana kuva kuri 13,04% muri Algeria kugeza kuri 0,08% muri Nouvelle Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Mu bibazo bishobora kuvuka harimo indwara y'ibihaha n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Igihe kuva ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara kugeza igihe indwara irengejeho ni iminsi igera kuri itanu, ariko kandi gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza kuri cumi n'ine.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo cyangwa umuti wihariye uraboneka.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvurwa ni ibimenyetso n'uburyo bwo kubungabunga. Ingamba zo kwirinda zisabwa harimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa igihe ukoroye, kugendera kure abantu, kumenya no kwicungira abantu bakeka ko banduye.
Abategetsi ku isi hose bitabiriye iki kibazo bashyiraho ingendo, guhagarika abantu, amasaha yo gutaha, kugenzura ibyago mu kazi no gufunga ibigo bitandukanye.
Icyorezo cyateje ingaruka zikomeye ku bukungu n'imibereho myiza ku isi, gusubika cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa bya siporo, amadini, politiki n'umuco, ndetse n'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa ryabayeho cyane, rikongera kwiyongera kubera kugura ibintu mu buryo bwo gutinya.
Amashuri n'amashuri makuru byafunzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa ku rwego rw'akarere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku banyeshuri bagera kuri 99,4% ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri virusi yatangiye gukwirakwira kuri interineti, habayeho amahano n'ivangura ku baturage b'Ubushinwa, abandi baturage bo mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'uburasirazuba bwa Aziya, cyangwa abantu babagereranya n'abo baturage, ndetse no ku bandi bantu baba mu duce dufite ubwandu bwinshi.
Kuba ingendo zo mu ndege zaragabanutse no gufunga inganda zikomeye byatumye habaho kugabanya imyuka ihumanya ikirere n'umwuka wa karubone.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, inzego z'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei), mu Bushinwa, zatangaje ko hari abantu banduye indwara y'ubuhumekero itagira icyorezo, kandi mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020, hatangiye iperereza.
Abantu benshi banduye iyi ndwara ni abavuye mu isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, bityo iyi ndwara ikaba ishobora kuba yaturutse ku nyamaswa.
Virusi yateje iki cyorezo izwi nka SARS-CoV-2. Ni virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifite byinshi ihuriyeho na koronavirusi z'ikinyugunyugu, koronavirusi ya pangolin na SARS-CoV. Nyuma byaje kugaragara ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye iki cyorezo yabaye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ko uwo muntu wanduye atagiye ku isoko nyuma y'uwo munsi.
Ibice bibiri bya gatatu by'ubwandu bw'indwara bwakozwe mu Ukuboza 2019 bwabayeho muri uru ruganda.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, ikinyamakuru cyo mu majyepfo y'u Bushinwa Morning Post cyatangaje ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye ari umuturage w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye bashya mu Bushinwa wagabanutse ariko utangira kwiyongera mu buryo butunguranye mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, kandi umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'u Bushinwa ku nshuro ya mbere warenze umubare w'abanduye bashya mu Bushinwa ubwabwo.
Umubare w'abarwaye ushobora kuba uri hasi cyane, cyane cyane kubera ko hari abarwayi benshi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, hari umubare muto w'abantu banduye mu rubyiruko, abarwayi bafite imyaka 19 cyangwa munsi yayo bakaba bari munsi ya 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru mu bya siyansi w'Ubwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yagereranyije ko 60% by'abatuye Ubwongereza bazaba banduye mbere y'uko abaturage b'igihugu bagira ubudahangarwa bw'itsinda.
Iyi mibare ikubiyemo abantu banduye basuzumwe COVID-19 kandi bagaragayeho ubwandu bufite ibimenyetso byemewe n'amategeko.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarashoboye gupima abantu barenga 3% mu baturage bacyo, kandi ibihugu byinshi nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi byagize politiki yemewe yo kudapima abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 16 Werurwe, bwagaragaje ko kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 mu Bushinwa batari barigeze bamenyekana, kandi ko abanduye nk'abo batanditswe ari bo batumye banduza 79% by'abanduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu by'ukuri mu Butaliyani warutaga cyane umubare w'abanduye.
Ibipimo bya mbere by'umubare w'ubwandu bw'ibanze (R0) bwa COVID-19 byari hagati ya 1,4 na 2,4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'imiyoborere, bugaragaza ko uwo mubare ushobora kuba uri ku kigero cya 5.7.
Abenshi mu barwayi ba COVID-19 barakira neza.
Mu bindi bibazo bikomeye, igihe cy'ibimenyetso kuva bitangiye kugeza igihe umuntu apfiriye cyari hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, akenshi cyari iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97.000 bapfuye bazize COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, hafi 80% by'abapfuye bari barengeje imyaka 60, naho 75% bari bafite izindi ndwara zirimo indwara z'umutima n'iz'amaraso na diyabete. Amakuru yemewe y'urupfu rw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 akunze kuba arimo abapfuye basuzumwe COVID, bakurikije amategeko yemewe.
Umubare nyawo w'abapfuye bazize COVID-19 ushobora kuba uri hejuru cyane kuko imibare yemewe ishobora kuba itarimo abapfuye batakoze ibizamini  nk'abapfiriye mu ngo zabo, mu bigo byita ku bageze mu za bukuru n'ibindi.
Amakuru adahagije ku Butaliyani agaragaza ko umubare w'abapfuye mu gihe cy'icyorezo warenze inshuro 45 umubare w'abapfuye muri COVID.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cya Leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko: "Turabizi ko [umubare w'abapfuye] uri hasi y'ukuri". Amagambo ye yemezwa n'amakuru y'abantu bamwe na bamwe bo muri Amerika.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa bwagaragaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho hanze ya Aziya mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga icumi bapfuye bari hanze y'u Bushinwa: muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo no mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga mirongo ine ku migabane yose uretse Antarctica, byatangaje ko hari abantu bapfuye.
Ibipimo byose bitandukanye bitewe n'akarere n'igihe cy'ikwirakwira ry'indwara; kandi bigira ingaruka ku bipimo, ubuziranenge bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe, igihe cy'indwara n'ibipimo by'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange.
Nk'uko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins ibigaragaza, ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, umubare w'abamaze gupfa n'abanduye ku isi ni 6,0% (97 039/1 617 204).
Ibipimo bitandukanye mu turere dutandukanye.
Mu Bushinwa, igipimo cy'urupfu ku barwaye cyaragabanutse kiva kuri 17,3% (ku bagaragaje ibimenyetso ku ya 110 Mutarama 2020) kigera kuri 0,7% (ku bagaragaje ibimenyetso nyuma ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ubundi buryo bukubiyemo kumenya igipimo cy'urupfu rw'abarwayi (CFR)  igipimo cy'abarwayi basanganywe uburwayi bapfa kubera uburwayi, n'igipimo cy'urupfu rw'abarwayi (IFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abarwayi banduye (baba basanganywe uburwayi cyangwa batarabubonetse) bapfa kubera uburwayi.
Aya makuru ntabwo afitanye isano n'igihe runaka kandi agaragaza imibare y'abantu bamwe na bamwe kuva igihe cyo kwandura kugeza igihe indwara irangiriye.
Hari abahanga bagerageje kubara ibyo bipimo ku matsinda y'abantu.
Nk'uko ikigo cy'ubuvuzi bw'ibimenyetso cya Kaminuza ya Oxford kibivuga, igipimo cy'urupfu rw'iki cyorezo muri rusange kiri hagati ya 0.1 na 0.39%.
Iyi mibare iri hejuru y'iyi mibare ihuje n'ibyavuye mu igerageza rya mbere rya COVID-19 mu Budage, ndetse n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bugaragaza ingaruka z'igerageza ku bipimo bya CFR.
OMS ivuga ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cyo kwiyongera n'igihe nyacyo cyo kwiyongera ntibishobora kumenyekana kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'aho biri.
Bony, umukozi wo muri kaminuza ya Pennsylvania, avuga ko indwara zitagenzurwa zisanzwe zigenda zigaragara, hanyuma igihe zitarimo abanduye, zigatangira guhera.
Ariko kandi, muri iki gihe, biragoye cyane kumenya igihe ibyo bizabera.
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi muri guverinoma y'Ubushinwa, Zhong Nansheng, avuga ko "ibi byose bishobora kurangira muri Kamena" niba ibihugu byose bishobora gushyira hamwe no gukurikiza inama za OMS ku bijyanye no guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'isuku n'ubuvuzi bw'ikirere i Londres yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuzigaragaza mu gihe cy'umwaka cyangwa ibiri.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Imperial College, buyobowe na Neil Ferguson, buvuga ko "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze gukorwa (hashobora kuba amezi 18 cyangwa arenga) " abantu bagomba kugendera kure abandi.
William Schaffner, umukozi wa Vanderbilt University, avuga ko "Ntekereza ko iyi koronavirusi itazigera ihita irangira burundu kuko yandura mu buryo bworoshye" kandi ko "ishobora guhinduka indwara y'igihe, igatangira kugaragara buri mwaka".
Kuba indwara nshya z'ibyorezo zigiye kwiyongera bizaterwa n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri n'urwego rw'ihindagurika ry'indwara.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi hari abantu banduye bashobora kurwara nta bimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara cyane ni umuriro mwinshi (88%) n'umusuhure ukaze (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara cyane birimo umunaniro, kuvuka kw'ibibyimba mu nzira y'ubuhumekero (umuhogo), kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu bice by'umubiri n'ibihaha, kubabara mu muhogo, umutwe, guhinda umushyitsi, gusubiranamo, kuvoma amaraso, impiswi cyangwa cyanoze. OMS ivuga ko umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwara indwara ikomeye, ariko akaba afite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibimenyetso byihutirwa nk'ububabare bwo guhumeka, kubabara cyangwa kumva mu gatuza, guhungabana mu bwenge, gukanguka nabi no kugira ubururu mu maso cyangwa mu kanwa. Iyo ibi bimenyetso bihari, ugomba guhita ushaka ubufasha.
Hari abantu banduye bashobora kugira uburwayi butagira ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso by'uburwayi, ariko ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abaganga bagasaba ko abantu bahuye cyane n'abarwayi bagaragaweho uburwayi, bashyirwa mu kato kandi bagasuzumwa.
Abahanga mu bya siyansi bo mu Bushinwa bavuga ko umubare w'abarwaye indwara badafite ibimenyetso uhera ku bantu bake ugera kuri 44% by'abarwaye bose.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo kubamo (igihe hagati yo kwandura no kugaragaza ibimenyetso) kiri hagati y'umunsi umwe na 14; ubusanzwe ni iminsi itanu. Kugeza ubu nta cyizere gihari ku bimenyetso byo kubura impumuro: imibare ya mbere y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bagaragaje ibi bimenyetso, yagaragaje ko mu mizo ya mbere bari 30%, hanyuma bagabanuka bagera kuri 15%.
Hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe bitaramenyekana ku buryo iyi ndwara ikwirakwira.
Bivugwa ko iyi ndwara ahanini yandura mu gihe cyo guhura cyane, ndetse no binyuze mu matembabuzi mato aturuka mu kirere hamwe no gukorora, kwitsamura cyangwa mu gihe cyo kuganira; guhura cyane bivuga guhura mu birometero biri hagati ya 1 na 2 (mitero 3 na 6).
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bugaragaza ko iyo umuntu yaturitse yaturitse, ibitonyanga by'amazi bishobora kugenda mu ntera iri hagati ya metero 4,5 na metero 8,2.
Hariho igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ishobora no kwanduzwa n'ibitonyanga bito biterwa mu mwuka mu gihe umuntu avuga, bishobora kuguma mu mwuka igihe kirekire. Bitonyanga byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bishobora no kubaho mu gihe umuntu ahumetse, harimo no mu gihe avuga, nubwo ubusanzwe virusi idashobora kwanduzwa mu mwuka.
Amadontoro ashobora kwinjira mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi, ndetse no mu bihaha.
Hari uburyo bwo kuvura, nko gutera intanga n'imiti y'umutima (CPR), bishobora gutuma ibijumba by'umwuka bihinduka imyanda, bityo virusi ikwirakwira mu mwuka.
Ishobora no kwinjira mu mubiri iyo umuntu akoze ku kintu cyanduye, harimo n'uruhu, nyuma akagira icyo akora ku maso, mu mazuru cyangwa mu kanwa.
Hari n'ubwoba ko virusi ishobora kwanduzwa n'ibinure, ariko ngo ibyago byo kwanduzwa n'iyo nzira ni bike.
Leta y'Ubushinwa irahakana ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduzwa n'umwanda mu kanwa. Virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, nubwo ishobora gukwirakwira mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa mu bihe bya nyuma by'indwara.
Hari igihe ibizamini byagiye bigaragaza ko umuntu yanduye mbere y'iminsi itatu ibimenyetso bitangiye kugaragara, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ushobora kwandura virusi mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara.
Hari raporo nke cyane z'abantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara, ariko ubushakashatsi bwo gukurikirana abakomeje guhura n'abandi mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe na bwo bwagaragaje ko hari abantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Abakozi b'Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurinda no Gukumira Indwara (ECDC) bavuga ko bitaramenyekana neza uko virusi ikwirakwira mu buryo bworoshye, ariko bizwi ko umuntu umwe urwaye ubusanzwe yandura abandi bantu 23.
By'umwihariko, byagaragaye ko kuri plastiki (polypropylene) no ku byuma bidapfa (304) virusi ishobora kubaho iminsi itatu, ku ikarito umunsi umwe, no ku muringa amasaha 4.
Icyakora, ibipimo bitandukanye bitewe n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe. Inyamaswa zo mu ngo n'iz'andi moko na zo zagize COVID-19.
Nta gihamya igaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu, nubwo abategetsi bo mu Bwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo guhura n'inyamaswa, kimwe no guhura n'ibindi bintu bishobora gukorwako n'abantu banduye.
Indwara ikomeye y'uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2)  ni virusi nshya yabonetse bwa mbere mu bantu batatu barwaye indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ibimenyetso byose bya virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 biboneka mu bidukikije muri koronavirusi zihuriyeho. Hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu virusi ishobora kurimburwa hifashishijwe isabune yo mu rugo, ikangiza uruhu rwayo. SARS-CoV-2 isa cyane na virusi ya mbere ya SARS-CoV.
Bivugwa ko ari inyamaswa.
Isesengura ry'imiterere ya koronavirusi ryagaragaje ko ihuje mu buryo bw'imiterere n'ubwoko bwa Betacoronavirus, ubwoko buto bwa Sarbecovirus (urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo B) hamwe n'ubundi bwoko bubiri bwa virusi z'imbeba.
Ku rwego rwa jenome yose, ihuriyeho na 96% n'ibindi bipimo bya koronavirusi y'ikinyugunyugu (BatCov RaTG13).
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi b'Abashinwa bavumbuye ko hari itandukaniro rimwe gusa mu byiciro bya amino acide by'ibice bimwe na bimwe bya genome ya virusi ya pangolin n'iy'umuntu.
Kugereranya genome yose kugeza ubu byerekanye ko igipimo kinini cy'ubusabane (92%) kiri hagati ya coronavirus ya pangolin na SARS-CoV-2, ariko ibyo ntibihagije kugira ngo byemeze ko pangolines ari ba nyir'ubwite ba virusi.
Kwanduzwa na virusi bishobora kwemezwa mbere y'igihe hashingiwe ku bimenyetso, nubwo amaherezo bigomba kwemezwa hifashishijwe isesengura rya polymerase chain reaction (PCR) cyangwa tomography ya mudasobwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwagereranyije uburyo bwa PCR na CT bwakoreshejwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ubushobozi bwo kumva neza kurusha PCR, nubwo idakomeye cyane kuko ibintu byinshi by'imashini zayo zo kureba ibicurane by'imyotsi n'ibindi by'indwara.
Kuva muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika Gishinzwe Imikorere y'Imiradiyo cyatangaje inama yo kudakoresha CT mu gupima cyangwa nk'uburyo bwo gupima bwa mbere mu gupima COVID-19.
OMS yasohoye inyandiko nyinshi z'igerageza rya RNA kuri SARS-CoV-2, iya mbere ikaba yarasohowe ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Hakozwe igerageza ku buryo bwa polymerase mu buryo bw'uruziga mu gihe nyacyo (RT-PCR).
Bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero no ku maraso.
Ibisubizo bikunze kuba biteguye mu gihe cy'amasaha make kugeza ku minsi mike.
Ubusanzwe, ibizamini bikoreshwa mu gusukura mu mazuru, ariko nanone hashobora gukoreshwa mu gusukura mu mazuru.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri byo cyari gihuje n'ukuri bihagije kugira ngo cyemezwe gukoreshwa hose.
Muri Amerika, ikizamini cya seroloji cyakozwe na Cellex cyemejwe gukoreshwa mu bihe by'impanuka gusa n'amavuriro yemewe.
Mu bintu by'umwihariko byerekana ibimenyetso kuri radiogram na tomography ya mudasobwa (CT) harimo imiterere y'ibice byo ku ruhande bitameze kimwe ku buryo bw'ibirahuri bya matte no kutagira ibyuya bya pleural.
Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'imashini z'umucyo ni cyo gitunganya amakuru mpuzamahanga agaragaza abantu banduye.
Kubera ko hari aho bihuriye n'izindi ndwara, urugero nka adenovirus, mu kumenya COVID-19, amafoto atagaragajwe na PCR afite umwihariko muke mu buvuzi.
Mu Bushinwa, hakozwe ubushakashatsi bunini bugereranya ibisubizo bya CT y'igituza n'ibipimo bya PCR, kandi byagaragaye ko nubwo amashusho atari yo agaragaza ubwandu, ashobora gusobanurwa vuba; kandi ko aba afite ubushobozi bwo kumenya aho umuntu ari, bityo ubwo buryo bwo gusuzuma bushobora gufatwa nk'igikoresho cyo gupima ahantu hari ubwandu.
Kugira ngo virusi igaragazwe hakoreshejwe X-ray na tomography ya mudasobwa, hashyizweho imikorere y'imitsi y'ubwenge ishingiye ku bwenge bw'ubuhanga.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura iyi ndwara ni ugukomeza kugira isuku rusange, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa n'intoki zanduye, gukoresha utwenda two gukaraba mu gihe ukoroye cyangwa witsamuye, ibyo bikaba bigomba kujugunywa nyuma yo gukoreshwa.
Abantu bashobora kuba baranduye bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Kugira ngo hatagira ubwandu bwandura, abantu bagirwa inama yo kugendera kure, kandi leta nyinshi zitegeka abantu kwirinda ingendo z'igihe gito mu bihugu n'uturere byugarijwe n'icyorezo, kandi zikumira ingendo z'abaturage.
Nyamara, iyi virusi yashoboye gukwirakwira mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage bamwe batazi aho banduye n'uburyo banduye. Abakozi b'ubuzima bita ku barwayi bashobora kwandura, barasabwa gukoresha ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda, hamwe n'ingamba zo kwirinda guhura n'abandi bantu no kwirinda amaso. Gukurikirana guhura kandi ni uburyo bw'ingenzi bukoreshwa n'inzego z'ubuzima mu kumenya isoko y'ubwandu no kubuhagarika.
Gukoresha amakuru y'aho abaturage baba bari kuri telefoni zabo zigendanwa na leta mu gukora ibyo byatumye havuka impungenge ku bijyanye n'ibanga, kandi imiryango nka Amnesty International n'indi irenga 100 yasabye ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura abantu.
Porogaramu zitandukanye za terefone zigendanwa zakozwe kandi zitangwa kugirango zikoreshwe ku bushake; kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'abahanga arenga icumi yakoraga ku gutunganya ibisubizo byemeza ibanga ry'amakuru bwite  nk'urugero, kwandika aho umukoresha ari hafi ya terefone zigendanwa zikoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth.
Iyo umuntu ukoresha telefoni agiranye imishyikirano ya bugufi n'umuntu wapimwe COVID-19, bamumenyesha ko bamusanganye. Hari n'ibitekerezo bidafite ishingiro ku buryo bwo kwirinda kwandura  nko gusukura izuru n'umunwa, ariko mu by'ukuri ntibigira icyo bigeraho.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 ruriho, nubwo hari imiryango myinshi ikora kugira ngo ruvumbuke.
Mu rwego rwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara, gukaraba intoki ni byiza.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'imibu (CDC) na cyo gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabune n'amazi nibura amasegonda 20, cyane cyane nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero cyangwa mu gihe intoki zawe zanduye cyane, mbere yo kurya, nyuma yo guhumeka, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Ibi ni ngombwa kuko iyo virusi iri hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, isenywa n'isabune yo mu rugo, ikamenagura uruhu rwayo rw'ubwirinzi.
Byongeye kandi, niba isabune n'amazi bidahari, CDC itera inkunga yo gukoresha imiti yica udukoko mu gihe ukoresha intoki ifite nibura 60% bya alukoro.
OMS irasaba abantu kwirinda gukorakora amaso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa n'amaboko yanduye.
Ibibanza bishobora guhumanywa n'imiti myinshi (ku gice cy'icyuma kitagira ingese umuti wica udukoko utangira gukora nyuma y'umunota umwe utangiye gutangwa) ifite 6271% ya éthanol, 50100% ya isopropanol, 0,1% ya hypochlorite ya sodium, 0,5% ya peroxide ya hydrogène na 0,2 7,5% ya povidon-iode.
Ibindi bikoresho, nka benzalkonium chloride na chlorhexidine gluconate, ntabwo bikora neza cyane.
CDC itera inkunga ko mu gihe COVID ikekwa cyangwa igaragaye mu kigo, nk'ibiro cyangwa amavuriro y'abana, ahantu hose muri icyo kigo harimo ibyumba by'akazi, ubwiherero, ibyumba rusange, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki nk'utubasha, udukoresho two gukoramo, konti, udupande tw'ibyuma bya ATM bikoreshwa n'abarwayi, bikwiye guhumanywa.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi avuga ko iyo ukoroye cyangwa ukoroye, ugomba gupfuka umunwa n'izuru ukoresheje agapfukamunwa cyangwa umwenda wo kwiyorosa, kandi ukirinda gukoresha ibikoresho by'isuku.
Abantu bashobora kuba baranduye, barasabwa gukoresha udupfukamunwa kuko gukoresha udupfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ingano n'aho ibicuruzwa byo mu mwuka bituruka mu kanwa, mu guhekenya no mu guhosha bitembera mu kirere.
OMS yashyize hanze amabwiriza y'igihe n'uburyo bwo gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, impuguke mu by'ubwandu bw'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa virusi muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yavuze ko "gukoresha agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya abantu gukorakora mu maso, kandi gukorakora mu maso n'amaboko yanduye ni bwo buryo bw'ibanze bwo kwandura".
