Muri Hong Kong, birasabwa kwambara agapfukamunwa mu modoka rusange cyangwa ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abategetsi bashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand basabye abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'impu mu ngo zabo kandi bakazajya tubanza tukamesa buri munsi.
Muri Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakiya, abaturage babujijwe kujya hanze badafite udupfukamunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, leta ya Vietnam yasabye abaturage bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu ruhame kugira ngo birinde n'abandi.
Guverinoma ya Autriche yasabye abantu bose bajya mu maduka y'ibiribwa kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Guverinoma ya Israel yasabye abaturage kwambara udupfukamunwa mu ruhame.
Ku ya 1 Mata, muri Tayiwani, aho hashize imyaka icumi hatunganywa udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bwa miliyoni icumi ku munsi, abantu bose bari mu modoka zitwara abagenzi n'imodoka z'amaguru basabwe gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bwa miliyoni icumi.
Muri Panama, abaturage basabwa kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bagiye hanze; abadashobora kugura udupfukamunwa basabwe kudukorera mu ngo zabo.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi dukoreshwa cyane kandi n'abaturage bo mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Kwirinda kwegerana (zwi no ku izina ry'irinde umuntu)  ni uburyo bwo kurwanya ubwandu bugamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya guhura cyane kw'abantu.
Ingamba zo kwirinda zirimo guhagarika ingendo, gufunga amashuri, ahantu ho gukorera, ibibuga by'imikino, za sitade n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora gukoresha ingamba zo kwirinda abantu mu kuguma mu ngo zabo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, gukoresha indamukanyo zitagira aho zihurira n'abandi no kwirinda abandi ku mubiri.
Ubu abategetsi benshi mu turere twugarijwe cyane n'iki cyorezo, bategeka cyangwa bagasaba abantu kwitandukanya n'abandi.
Umubare w'abantu ushobora guhurira ahantu hamwe nk'uko byemejwe n'inzego za Leta z'Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima, wagabanyijwe vuba, uhereye ku bantu 250 (mu turere tudafite amakuru y'ikwirakwira rya COVID-19), ugera kuri 50, hanyuma ugahinduka 10 nyuma.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije guteranira mu matsinda arimo abantu barenze babiri. Abasaza n'abantu bafite indwara nk'igisukari, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko w'amaraso no kugabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara virusi mu buryo bukomeye. CDC irabasaba kuguma mu rugo igihe kirekire gishoboka niba akarere kabayemo icyorezo. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gusimbuza gukoresha ijambo kwirinda kure gukwirinda kure , bityo zisobanura neza intego y'iyi ngamba kugabanya guhura mu buryo bw'umubiri mu mibanire y'abantu, byaba binyuze mu gushyikirana kuri interineti cyangwa mu kugendera kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwirinda" byumvikanisha ko abantu bagomba kwigunga mu buryo bwuzuye aho guhora bagirana n'abandi imishyikirano mu bundi buryo. Inzego zimwe na zimwe zasohoye amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imyororokere agomba gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Mu bindi, hatanzwe inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'abo mubana gusa, abo mubana kandi mufite icyizere ko badafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Abantu basanganywe COVID-19 n'abakekwaho kuyandura basabwa kwigunga mu ngo zabo.
Ibigo nderabuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwicungira ukwabo. Guverinoma z'ibihugu byinshi na zo zategetse cyangwa zasabye abaturage bose bo mu duce twibasiwe n'icyorezo kwicungira ukwabo.
Abantu bari mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi, bategetswe kuba mu kato gakomeye.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'abanduye COVID-19, cyangwa bakaba baherutse gusura igihugu cyangwa akarere kizahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, basabwe kuguma mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bagiranye isano.
Uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo ni uguhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo, kugikumira cyangwa kugikumira.
Gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara bikorwa mu bihe bya mbere kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye, kandi bikubiyemo izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu no gukingira mu rwego rwo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara mu bandi baturage.
Mu gihe gukwirakwira kw'indwara bitagishoboka, imbaraga zigamije kugabanya ingaruka: hafatwa ingamba zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira no kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo ku buzima n'abaturage.
Ingamba zo gukumira no kugabanya ingaruka z'ikwirakwira ry'indwara zishobora gufatwa icyarimwe.
Gutegeka ubwandu bisaba ingamba zikomeye cyane kugira ngo iki cyorezo kiveho, ku buryo umubare w'ubwandu wagabanutse ugera munsi ya 1.
Ibyo bikorwa bigabanya ibyago byo kuremererwa n'ubuvuzi kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibipimo by'ubutabazi bishobora gufasha guhangana n'iki cyorezo birimo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'isuku y'intoki, gukoresha udupfukamunwa n'ubwirinzi; ingamba zo kwirinda abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibikorwa by'imbaga; gushishikariza abaturage gufasha no kwitabira ibyo bikorwa; ndetse n'ingamba zo kurengera ibidukikije, nko gusukura aho hantu.
Ibindi bihugu na byo byafashe ingamba zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho uburyo bwo gupima abantu benshi no gushyira mu duce dutandukanye abantu bari mu kato, ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubamenyesha ko banduye.
Singapore yahaga inkunga y'amafaranga abantu banduye bari mu kato, kandi igafatira amande menshi abananirwaga kuyatanga.
Mu gihugu cya Taiwan, hakozwe ibikorwa byinshi byo gukora udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi no gucibwa amande kubera kubungabunga imiti.
Gushyiraho politiki nziza yo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bapfa ku rugero rwo hejuru ku buryo bwa kabiri, ariko bigatuma abantu ibihumbi amagana bapfa kandi ubuzima bukangirika.
Gukumira bishobora kuba uburyo bwiza, ariko bigomba gukoreshwa igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze gukorwa, niba ari ubwa mbere), kuko bitabaye ibyo, ikwirakwira ry'indwara rizongera vuba igihe ingamba zizagabanuka.
Gushyiraho ingamba z'igihe kirekire mu guhashya icyorezo bitera ingaruka mbi mu mibereho y'abaturage no mu bukungu.
Kugeza ubu nta miti ya virusi yemewe kuvura COVID-19, ariko hari imbaraga zirimo gukorwa mu kuyikora, harimo no gupima imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti yo mu bwoko bwa "freeze" (umuti utangwa n'abaganga), kunywa amazi ahagije no kuruhuka bihagije bishobora gufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'uburwayi, umurwayi ashobora gukenera imiti ya ogisijeni, guterwa amazi mu muhogo no gufasha guhumeka.
Gukoresha imiti ikoreshwa na Steroids bishobora kwangiza gusa.
Imiti imwe n'imwe yari yemewe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi iri no gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS yatangaje kandi ko hari imiti gakondo n'imiti yo mu rugo ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
OMS ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuvuzi n'ibyo abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ari byo by'ingenzi mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC) n'Ikigo cy'Akarere k'u Burayi cya OMS byatanze amabwiriza ku mavuriro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo bifashe kongera gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa ku buryo butandukanye, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gupima COVID-19, gukuraho uburyo butari ngombwa igihe bishoboka, gutahura virusi no gushyira mu kato abarwayi bagaragaweho COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bababaye cyane binyuze mu kwigisha abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho bya VTE n'ibitanda biboneka.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku hantu umuntu wa mbere wanduye  uwitwa umurwayi wa ero ashobora kuba yaraturutse.
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho kwandura coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yarabayeho ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus mu ntara ya Hubei wagendaga wiyongera buhoro buhoro.
By'umwihariko, byari bifitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibikomoka ku nyanja rya Huanan, ryagurishirizwamo n'inyamaswa nzima, kandi imwe mu nyigisho ni uko virusi yinjiye mu mubiri w'umuntu iturutse kuri imwe muri izi nyamaswa; mu yandi magambo, virusi ifite inkomoko yo mu nyamaswa. Ku ya 26 Ukuboza, mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei, hari haranditswe umuntu warwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero itaramenyekana inkomoko, wakoranye na muganga Ch Tianjin, ku ya 27 Ukuboza, yatangaje iby'iki kibazo mu Kigo cyo kugenzura no gukumira indwara cya Jianghan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, baburiye bagenzi babo ku byerekeye coronavirus isa na SARS.
Abaganga umunani muri abo, barimo Li Wenliang, bari barahawe umuburo na polisi ko bazahanwa kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha by'ibinyoma, naho umuganga witwa Ai Feng, yahawe igihano n'abayobozi be kubera ko yateje impagarara.
Nyuma yaho, ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan yatangaje itangazo ku mugaragaro maze imenyesha OMS uko byagenze.
Abashinzwe ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan batangaje ko umubare w'abarwaye indwara y'ibihaha itaramenyekana, wari munini bihagije ku buryo batangiye iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo, umubare w'abarwaye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yakwirakwiriye no mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, byatewe n'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa n'uko Wuhan ari umuyoboro w'ingendo n'umuhanda w'indarayi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, u Bushinwa bwavuze ko hari abantu bashya 140 banduye mu munsi umwe, barimo abantu babiri barwaye i Beijing n'umwe mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Nk'uko amakuru yemewe nyuma yaho yabigaragaje, ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu 6 174 bari baramaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatsinze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani ku mubare munini w'abanduye ku isi. Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, ku isi hose hari hamaze kwandura abantu barenga miliyoni 1,61, abantu basaga 97,000 barapfuye, abarenga 364,000 barakize.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byamaze kugaragaza nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera iki cyorezo, ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu kandi bishyiraho igenzura ku mipaka.
Ingamba z'igihugu zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo harimo ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo, nk'igitaraganya (zwi ku izina rya Guma mu rugo, guhisha mu rugo cyangwa kwicungira), hamwe n'isaha yo gutaha. Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abatuye Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, bari mu buryo runaka bwo kwicungira, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu kato muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu kato muri Afurika y'Epfo n'abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo runaka bwo kwicungira ukwabo, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, uwo mubare wariyongereye ugera kuri miliyari 2.6  hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 yabonywe i Wuhan ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; hari indi raporo itari yemewe ivuga ko uwo munsi ari  17 Ugushyingo.
Ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, umuganga Zhang Jisiang yakoraga ku murwayi w'ubwoko butazwi bw'indwara y'ibihaha, maze ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, ivuriro rye rimenyesha Ikigo cya Jianghan cyo mu mujyi wa Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara.
Ibizamini bya mbere byagenewe ibipimo by'abarwayi, byabaye ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, byagaragaje ko hari coronavirus isa na SARS.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan yashyize ahagaragara itangazo rusange.
OMS yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
Kubera izo nkuru, polisi yaburiye abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ko bazahanwa "kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha" by'icyorezo.
Mu mizo ya mbere, Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa yavuze ko nta gihamya igaragara y'uko iyi virusi nshya ishobora kwanduzwa n'abantu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye bwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi, nyuma y'aho ikaba yiswe "intambara y'abaturage" n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, Xi Jinping.
Ibintu byatangiye kwiyongera, kuri 23 Mutarama hatangajwe gahunda yo kwirinda abantu benshi kwinjira no gusohoka mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nyuma y'aho iyo gahunda yakwirakwijwe mu mijyi 15 yo mu ntara ya Hubei, kandi abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Mu mujyi babujije abantu gukoresha imodoka zabo bwite.
Mu duce twinshi, ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (ku ya 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo bya Huoshenshan, bikaba byarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari ikindi bitaro byubatswe, Leishengshan, cyakira abandi barwayi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwongeye guhindura ibindi bigo 14 byo muri Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'inama na stade, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yafashe izindi ngamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga impapuro z'ubwisungane mu kwivuza ku bagenzi no kongera igihe cyo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa.
Amashuri n'amashuri yisumbuye byari byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Intara za Hong Kong na Macao zashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Mu turere dutandukanye two mu Bushinwa, abayobozi bashyizeho uburyo bwo gukora ku buryo bwa kure.
Mu ntara ya Hubei no hanze yayo hashyizweho amategeko abuza abantu gutembera.
Amasaha y'ingendo y'imodoka z'abantu bose yarahindutse, kandi inzu ndangamurage zo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa zarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi hashyizweho uburyo bwo kugenzura urujya n'uruza rw'abaturage, kandi byatekerejwe ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahuye n'uburyo bumwe cyangwa ubundi bwo kugabanya urujya n'uruza mu ruhame. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyinjiye mu cyiciro cy'isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira "kuzana" virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, i Beijing hashyizweho iminsi 14 yo kwitarura abantu bose baturutse mu bindi bihugu binjira muri uwo mujyi. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa bw'ibanze hari umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu gihugu, akaba yari amaze iminsi itanu yanduye, muri iki gihe akaba ari umuntu wari wavuye i Istanbul agaruka i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwandura mu gihugu hafi ya bwose bwahagaritswe, kandi ko icyorezo cy'ubwandu mu Bushinwa cyagenzurwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo zibujijwe mu ntara ya Hubei, uretse Wuhan, zakuweho, nyuma y'amezi abiri iyo ntara ifunze kubera gufunga. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko kuva ku ya 28 Werurwe, kwinjira ku bantu bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizahagarikwa.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula z'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 30 Werurwe, leta y'u Bushinwa yasabye inganda n'inganda gusubukura imirimo no guha ibigo ingamba zo kubikemura. Ku ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo habaye "Iminuta itatu yo guceceka" ku rwego rw'igihugu, hatangijwe umunsi wo kwibuka abantu bishwe na coronavirus watangajwe n'Inama y'Igihugu, ukaba wahuriranye n'umunsi mukuru wa Kuinmin, ariko leta nkuru yasabye abaturage guha icyubahiro abapfuye kuri interineti, bakurikiza intera hagati yabo kugira ngo birinde kongera kwibasirwa na COVID-19.
Byaremejwe ko COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 20 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu yatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane, ahanini bitewe n'uko i Taegu hari umubare munini w'abayoboke b'umuteguro mushya w'idini uzwi ku izina rya Shinchhonji Church of Jesus.
Abayoboke ba Shinchhonji baje i Taegu baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho bivugwa ko iki cyorezo cyaturutse.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9 336 b'iryo torero, 1 261 (hafi 13%) batangaje ko bafite ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara. Ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite ikibazo cy'indwara y'uburwayi.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2.000 bemejwe ko banduye iyi ndwara muri Koreya, maze ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, uwo mubare uragera ku 3.150.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare byo muri Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu basuzumwe bagasanga basanze bafite virusi.
Icyorezo cyagize ingaruka ku ngendo, bityo gahunda y'indege y'indege yarahindutse. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yo gupima abaturage kugira ngo bamenye niba hari virusi, gukurikirana abo bahuye no gushyiraho ingamba zo guhagarika abantu bahuye. Iyi gahunda ifatwa nk'iyikomeye kandi nziza cyane ku isi yose mu bijyanye n'imikorere yayo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwagombaga kuba bugizwe no gusaba abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga kubamenyesha ibimenyetso byabo bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima umuntu wese kuri virusi, ibisubizo bikaba byarabonekaga ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kwagura ubushobozi bwo gupima, bigatuma abantu bagera ku 20.000 bapimwa buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'ifitwe n'ingaruka nziza mu kurwanya iki cyorezo, nubwo nta mijyi yose yatangiye kwicamo ibice.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zishimira ibyo Perezida yakoze cyangwa zisaba ko Bwana Moon acibwa ku butegetsi kubera ibyo babona ko ari ibidakwiye leta yakoze ku cyorezo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko imaze ibyumweru bine ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi umwe.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Amakuru atangwa n'ibitangazamakuru avuga ko ibihugu 121 byasabye Koreya y'Epfo ubufasha mu gupima virusi ku ya 1 Mata.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Irani yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 muri Qum, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi yatangaje ko abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma yaho kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere leta yashyizeho, harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco na siporo, amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, ndetse no gufunga kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'Amerika yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yatangaje ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko leta itateganya gushyira mu kato uturere twose twatewe n'iki cyorezo, ahubwo ko abantu ku giti cyabo ari bo bonyine bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Muri Werurwe, hatangajwe gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi, ariko ingendo zikomeye hagati y'imijyi mbere y'umwaka mushya w'abaperesi zakomeje.
Ibibanza byera by'aba Shiite i Qum byari byuguruye ku bayoboke b'idini rya Islam kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Mu gihe hari ibitangazwa byo guhisha urugero rw'icyorezo muri Irani, kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare ibihugu birenga icumi byari byaravuze ko Iran ari yo ifite ubwandu bwayo, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha abanduye 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze kubona.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yari ifunze, kandi 23 mu bagize 290 bayo, ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, batangajwe ko basanze basanzwemo virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza ya Irani kurekura burundu abavugizi ba leta bafunzwe bazira ko batemera ibyo bavuga kandi bagasohora by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite ubwo burenganzira.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima rivuga ko hari ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virus mu bigo bifunze, nk'ama gereza, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije buhari.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe  umubare munini w'abapfuye mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Irani n'abakozi ba leta bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, muri Irani buri saha habaga habonetse abantu 50 bashya banduye coronavirus, kandi buri minota icumi habaga hapfuye umuntu umwe.
Umuvugizi wa OMS yavuze ko umubare w'abarwayi muri Iran ushobora kuba ukubye inshuro eshanu uwo bivugwa ku rwego rw'ubutegetsi.
Hari kandi amakuru avuga ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ushinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani, bigabanywa.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, byemejwe ko iyi ndwara yageze mu Butaliyani ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bapimwa SARS-CoV-2 i Roma, bagasanga baranduye.
Umubare w'abandura watangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege zijya mu Bushinwa no ziva mu Bushinwa, kandi itangaza ko ibintu byihutirwa.
Nyuma yaho, havumbuwe itsinda ry'abantu batanduye COVID-19. Byose byatangiye igihe habonekaga abantu 16 bemejwe ko banduye muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yasohoye itegeko rishya ryo gukumira icyorezo, aho abantu barenga 50.000 bo mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani bashyizwe mu kato.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yavuze ko kwinjira no gusohoka mu gace k'icyorezo bizasubikwa.
Muri utwo turere, imirimo y'inganda yari imaze guhagarikwa kandi ibikorwa by'imikino byari byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 4 Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza zose zo mu gihugu hose zifungwa, kuko muri icyo gihe mu Butaliyani hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 100 bapfuye.
Imikino ikomeye yose, harimo n'imikino y'umupira w'amaguru yo mu cyiciro cya A, yagombaga kubera inyuma y'imiryango ifunze kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yasubitswe nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa hafi ya byose by'ubucuruzi no gufunga ibigo uretse amaduka manini n'amaduka y'imiti. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Abaganga b'Abaganga b'Abaganga b'Abaganga, Abatabara, Abatabara n'Abavura mu buryo bw'Ibitekerezo (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama ku bijyanye n'imyifatire y'abaganga ku bijyanye n'amategeko agenga gahunda yo kugenzura uko abarwayi bakurikirana mu kwivuza, bishobora kuba ngombwa ko akoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwateye u Bushinwa mu gipimo cy'abapfa bishwe na coronavirus, buza ku mwanya wa mbere ku isi, nyuma yo gutangaza ko hapfuye abantu 3,405.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byamenyekanye ko u Burusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'intambara mu Butaliyani zifite ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari hamaze kuboneka abantu 128,948 banduye coronavirus, abantu 15,887 bapfuye n'abantu 21,815 bakize, abenshi muri abo bantu bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN ivuga ko ibipimo by'urupfu biri hejuru mu Butaliyani bishobora kuba biterwa n'ibintu bibiri: umubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru mu gihugu no kutagira ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bose barwaye coronavirus.
Ubwongereza ni cyo gihugu cyitabiriye iyi virusi mu buryo bworoheje kurusha ibindi bihugu byayibasiye, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyari yarasabye abaturage bayo kubahiriza uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda cyangwa gushyira mu kato.
Ibyo byatumye leta inengwa kuba itarakiriye neza kandi mu buryo bwihuse akaga abaturage b'igihugu bari barimo. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatanze itangazo ryasabaga abantu kwirinda ingendo zose n'imishyikirano itari iy'ingenzi, asaba abantu gukorera mu rugo igihe bishoboka no kwirinda ahantu hahurira abantu benshi nko mu tubari, muri resitora no mu mazu ya sinema.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro, nk'ahoba n'amakipe y'imikino, bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi yasezeranyije abaturage bakora ko bazishyurwa 80% by'umushahara ariko ntibarenze £2,500 ku kwezi nk'ingamba zo gufasha abaturage mu gihe cy'ibibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda abantu, abuza abantu guteranira hamwe barenze babiri kandi agabanya ingendo n'imyidagaduro yo hanze gusa mu bihe by'ingenzi.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uburyo bwari busanzwe, ibi bihano byashyizweho hakoreshejwe abapolisi, ibihano no guhagarika imbaga.
Ibigo byinshi byategetswe gufunga, usibye ibigo by'ubucuruzi bitanga ubuzima bw'abaturage, harimo supermarket, farumasi, banki, amaduka y'ubucuruzi, aho bakoresha lisansi n'amatara.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika muri Leta ya Washington, umugabo wari wavuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama, yemejwe ko ari we muntu wa mbere w'igihugu wanduye COVID-19.
Ku ya 29 Mutarama, mu nzu y'Ubutegetsi bw'Amerika hashyizweho itsinda ry'abakozi rishinzwe kurwanya coronavirus.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe mu by'ubuzima rusange kandi bushyiraho amategeko abuza abantu kwinjira mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima rusange, cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho byacyo bwite byo gupima.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, gupima abaturage muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ntibyatangiye ako kanya, bituma umubare nyawo w'icyorezo muri icyo gihe utamenyekana.
Kwipimisha byatewe n'ibura ry'ibikoresho by'ibizamini byatanzwe na guverinoma ya federasiyo muri Gashyantare, kubura kw'ibyangombwa bya guverinoma ya federasiyo kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare byo gukoresha ibikoresho by'ibizamini bya leta bitari ibya leta byakozwe n'imiryango y'ubushakashatsi, ibigo bitandukanye n'amavuriro, ndetse n'amabwiriza yo kugabanya mbere y'ukwezi kwa gatatu yemerera abaturage kwipimisha (byashoboraga gukorwa gusa ku itegeko rya muganga ubitaho).
Ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyatangaje ko kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hari hasigaye ibizamini 4000.
Ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, hari hasigaye ibizamini 14 000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko "abarwayi benshi, nubwo bari bafite ibimenyetso kandi bahamagariwe kwa muganga, bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi myinshi kugira ngo bakore isuzuma". Nyuma y'aho leta ya Washington itangarije ko hari umuntu wa mbere w'umwandu wa coronavirus wapfuye muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe, bidatinze n'izindi leta na zo zitangira kubitangaza.
Ku ya 3 Werurwe, amashuri yo mu mujyi wa Seattle yahagaritswe, maze mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati amashuri yose afungwa mu gihugu. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'ibyorezo bo muri Imperial College, i Londres, bamenyesheje Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ko Coronavirus nshya ishobora kuzagira ingaruka ku gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'inyongera ry'amafaranga yo kwitegura no guhangana na coronavirus, ryemerera leta ya Amerika inkunga y'ingoboka ingana na miliyari 8,3 z'amadolari ya Amerika kugira ngo ibashe guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amategeko abuza abakozi kujya mu mahanga, yahagaritse inama kandi asaba abakozi gukorera mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'umwaka byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari iminsi 30 y'amabwiriza yo guhagarika ingendo mu bice byinshi by'u Burayi, usibye Ubwongereza, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yaguyeho amategeko agenga ingendo, yongeraho n'u Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, perezida yatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe mu gihugu, bituma hakoreshwa amafaranga ya leta mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi byatangiye gufunga cyangwa kugabanya amasaha y'akazi hirya no hino muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, mu rwego rwo kurwanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu bihugu 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko muri New York hari hamaze kwandura abantu 10.700 ku munsi, barenze umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu bishobora kuba ingamba nziza, kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanutse iva ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, muri New York hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 32 308 banduye, naho abantu 672 barapfuye. Byatangajwe ko ku ya 26 Werurwe muri Amerika hari hamaze kugaragara abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha mu bindi bihugu byose byo ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 8 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 400 335 banduye, abantu 12 841 barapfuye.
Amakuru yo ku wa 30 Werurwe avuga ko Perezida Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera igihe cyo kwitandukanya n'abandi kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort bw'ibitanda 1000 bwageze ku cyambu cya New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, muri Amerika hamaze kwandikwa abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Mu ntara ya New York, ku itariki ya 3 Mata, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000. Ibiro bya White House byanenzwe kubera ko bidaha agaciro akaga n'amakuru agera ku baturage, binyuze mu biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence bigenzura imvugo n'ibitabo by'abayobozi n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima bijyanye na virusi.
Muri rusange, abafana ba Perezida Trump ntibumva neza uko yahangana n'ikibazo.
Bamwe mu bayobozi n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika kubera ko ikoresha ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi cyane, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ibanze, biva mu Bushinwa.
Hagati ya Mutarama 2020, ikinyamakuru Travel Medicine cyasohoye isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege zakoreshejwe mu gukora amakarita no guhanura uburyo indwara ikwirakwira.
Ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'ingendo mu kirere ryatangaje ko mu 2018, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei byakira ingendo nyinshi zaturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne nabyo byafatwaga nk'ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abo bakerarugendo.
Mu mihanda 20 ikunzwe cyane y'ubukerarugendo, Bali ni yo yavuzwe ko ititeguye cyane guhangana n'iki cyorezo, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya ifatwa nk'iyiteguye cyane. Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Ositaraliya yemeje gahunda yayo y'ibikorwa byihutirwa bijyanye na coronavirus nshya (COVID-19).
Muri iyo nkuru, bavuga ko hari byinshi bigikenewe kumenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izita cyane ku kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu gihe habayeho ibyago.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habaye ikibazo cy'ubukene mu bijyanye n'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima.
Bitewe n'ingamba nziza zo kwitarura abantu mu buryo bw'ibinyabiziga mu bice bya Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byateguye kwimura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako gace, ahanini binyuze mu ndege z'indege z'ibihugu byabo, ibyo bikaba byemejwe n'ubutegetsi bw'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byateguye guhungisha abaturage babyo.
Pakisitani yatangaje ko itazatera abaturage bayo kuva mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Bresil yakuye muri icyo gihugu Abaturage 34 b'Abanyabrezili/abavandimwe b'Abanyabrezili, hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umushina n'Umuhinde.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'Ubuhinde barohamye muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brazil yahagaze mbere yo kujya muri Brezil nk'uko byari biteganyijwe.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari basuye Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi y'umujyi wa Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, abaturage 215 ba Kanada (176 mu ndege ya mbere na 39 mu ndege ya kabiri yari ikodeshejwe na leta ya Amerika) bakuwe muri Wuhan, bajyanwa ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada cya Trenton, bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye abaturage 185 ba Canada, na bo bari bavuye i Wuhan, yageze ku kigo cya CFB Trenton.
Ku ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi ba Ositaraliya bakuye abaturage babo 277 mu gihugu cyabo, babashyira mu kigo cy'igihe gito kiri ku kirwa cya Noheli, cyaje guhindurwa ikigo cy'ihagarikwa ry'abantu, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, indege y'i Nouvelle-Zélande yageze i Auckland; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cy'inyanja i Vangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gucyura abaturage ba Amerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bavuye mu ndege ya Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye kwimura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya kompanyi y'indege ya South African Airways, yari yaraguzwe na guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo, yahagurutse ifite abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bari bayirimo.
Abagenzi basuzumwe mbere yo gutangira urugendo, kandi abanyafurika y'epfo bane bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus baragumye mu Bushinwa kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragayeho coronavirus ni bo bavuye muri icyo gihugu.
Ibizamini byafashwe ku baturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi ba ndege, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, kandi bose bagumye bagenzurwa kandi bashyizwe mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri The Ranch Resort nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje ubufasha bwabyo mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa biga muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bishyize hamwe kugira ngo bakusanyirize hamwe imfashanyo kandi bazishyikirize uturere two mu Bushinwa twatewe na virusi, aho itsinda ryo muri Chicago bivugwa ko ryohereje udupira tw'ubuhumekero tw'ubwoko bwa N95 50.000 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi Direct Relief ufatanyije na FedEx, ku ya 30 Mutarama, wohereje indege y'ubutabazi 200,000 mu bitaro bya Wuhan Union, hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi birimo utwenda two mu ntoki n'udupfukamunwa.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya Amerika ku izina rya OMS mu rwego rwo gushyigikira iterambere ry'urukingo n'ubuvuzi bwa coronavirus, ndetse no kurinda abaturage bo mu bihugu byo muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo bafite ibyago byo kwandura iyi virus.
Interaksyon yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare, leta y'Ubushinwa yahaye Filipine udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko 200,000 nk'impano nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapuru yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga y'amadolari miliyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani kandi bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Uburusiya  toni zirenga 13 z'imiti, Maleziya yatangaje ko yatanze uturindantoki tw'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18, Ubudage bwohereje ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo udupfukamunwa 10,000, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'imiti, ndetse zisezeranya gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari nk'inkunga y'amafaranga ku bihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko ibintu byoroheye mu Bushinwa, igihugu na cyo cyatumye ibindi bihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje imiti n'impuguke mu Butaliyani kugira ngo zifashe abaturage guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yoherereje Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe, Addis Abeba, Ethiopia, ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda umubiri kugira ngo uwo muryango ubikwirakwize mu bihugu biwugize.
Nyuma yaho, yohereje kandi ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibyuma 5 bya V.I.P. muri Panama.
Ubudage, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Czech byatangaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'udupfukamunwa n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe n'Abashinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yahagaritse ibikoresho 58,000 by'Ubushinwa byo gupima coronavirus bifite ubuziranenge bwa 30% gusa, naho Ubuholandi buhagarika 600,000 by'udupfukamunwa tw'Abashinwa dufite inenge.
Ububiligi nabwo bwasubije mu bikorwa udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko 100 000 tutakoreshwa: twitwaga ko twakorewe mu Bushinwa, ariko nyuma byaje kugaragara ko twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'Ubushinwa bwakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangiye ibikorwa byo gufasha mu buryo bwihutirwa ibihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye cyane imbaraga z'ubutegetsi bw'Ubushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo no kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro rigaragara hagati y'icyorezo cya Pneumonia yo mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga kudahishira amakuru, ngo bibangamiye kwirinda indwara no kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo, n'ikibazo cy'iki gihe, aho guverinoma nkuru yagiye itanga amakuru agezweho ku buryo butari buke kugira ngo hatagira ubwoba mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubutegetsi bwo hagati cyo guhagarika ingendo z'ibinyabiziga muri Wuhan, umuvugizi wa OMS, Goden Galea, yavuze ko nubwo iyi ngamba itari ihamagarirwa na OMS, ariko kandi ari "igikorwa gikomeye cyane cyo kwemeza ko iki cyemezo cyakozwe mu rwego rwo gukumira icyorezo mu gace kiganjemo icyorezo", avuga ko "nta kindi cyigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko ubwandu bushobora guhererekanywa hagati y'abantu hanze y'u Bushinwa no kwiyongera kw'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki ari ikibazo cy'ubukene mu buzima rusange gifite agaciro mpuzamahanga (PHEIC); iki ni icya gatandatu kuva mu 2009 ubwo icyo cyemezo cyatangwaga mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane byo mu gihugu cy'u Bushinwa.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko gutangaza PHEIC biterwa n'ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abifite ubukungu buciriritse, bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu kuvuga ku ngamba zo kugabanya ingendo, Bwana Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zibuza abantu kujya mu mahanga no gucuruza" kandi ko "WHO idatanga inama yo kugabanya ingendo n'ubucuruzi".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amerika yo gufasha mu buryo bw'ibanze ibihugu bifite amikoro make guhangana n'icyorezo, ivuga ko hakenewe ubufasha bwihutirwa mu bihugu bitagira uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye nubwo icyorezo kitaragera muri ibyo bihugu.
Bwana Tedros yavuze kandi ko "igaragaza ko twiteguye" ari uko twiteguye guhangana n'icyorezo mu gice cyacu gikennye cyane, asaba amahanga "guhitamo gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura ejo hazaza". Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yashyizeho izina ryemewe ry'iki cyorezo  COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gutanga "ubushobozi bw'umuryango w'abibumbye mu guhangana n'iki kibazo".
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko hashyizweho itsinda rya ONU rishinzwe guhangana n'ibiza rihuza ibisubizo byose by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye; izo ntambwe, nkuko OMS ibivuga, zizatuma "bishyira imbaraga mu guhangana n'ubuzima, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gukoresha ubunararibonye bwazo mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo mu buryo bwagutse mu rwego rw'imibereho n'ubukungu".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, OMS n'Ubushinwa byatangije itsinda ry'abahanga mpuzamahanga n'abakozi ba OMS mu Bushinwa kugira ngo bafashe mu gukemura ikibazo cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus mu gihugu no gusuzuma "uburemere bw'iki cyorezo n'ubwandu bwacyo", bateguye amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'ibanze z'igihugu, ndetse bajya ku isi gusuzuma "imikorere myiza y'ibikorwa byo guhangana n'iki cyorezo mu ntara no mu turere, harimo n'imidugudu n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yavuze ko isi ikeneye gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus, ivuga ko "bitaraza vuba cyane ko icyorezo cyitwa icyorezo, ariko ibihugu bigomba kubitegura".
Ubwo iki cyorezo cyatangiraga muri Irani, OMS yoherejeyo itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa kugira ngo basuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko amahirwe yo gukwirakwira kw'icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi yose azamuka ava ku "gipimo cyo hejuru" ajya ku "gipimo cyo hejuru cyane" cyo kwitegura no guhangana n'akaga.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'umuryango w'abibumbye ishinzwe kwihutisha ubuzima, yatanze umuburo mu itangazo agira ati: "Iki ni ikigeragezo kuri buri butegetsi ku isi kugira ngo turebe niba bwiteguye guhangana n'ibihe by'ibanze: igihe kirageze cyo kugira icyo bukora.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira igana mu gihugu cyanyu, kandi mugomba kuba mwiteguye", kandi ashimangira ko uburyo bukwiye bwo gusubiza bushobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibihe bibi cyane".
Ryan yavuze kandi ko ibipimo biriho ubu bitagaragaza impamvu zatuma abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi, yongeraho ko gutangaza iki cyorezo bivuze ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura iyi virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko OMS ihangayikishijwe cyane n'icyiciro cyo gukwirakwira no gukomera k'iyi ndwara, ndetse n'icyiciro cyo kutagira icyo ikora ku kibazo cy'iki kibazo. OMS iramagwa bikomeye kubera uburyo bufatwa nk'ubudahagije bwo gufata icyerekezo cy'icyorezo, harimo gutangaza ibyago bidasanzwe by'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu byiciro nk'icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kwamagana ibi, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yashyikirijwe ibaruwa isaba kwegura, ikaba yarashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke nyinshi z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ku burenganzira bwa muntu zashimangiye akamaro ko kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira bwo guhabwa ingamba zo kurokora ubuzima, kandi ko leta ari yo ifite inshingano yo kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba kuba urwitwazo rwo guca urwikekwe ku itsinda runaka ry'abantu.
Abahanga bemeje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira bwo kurindwa ubuzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abasanzwe bagize amatsinda mato mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abahunze, abatagira aho baba, abaturage batuye mu bihe bibi cyane, imfungwa, impunzi n'andi matsinda adasobanutse akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ya leta irimo gusuzuma ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage z'ikibazo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubutwererane mu by'Ubukungu n'Iterambere washyizeho urubuga rugamije gutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi arambuye ku ngamba za politiki mu bihugu byo ku isi, no gusangira ibitekerezo no gutanga inama.
Uru rubuga rufite amakuru y'ingamba za politiki z'ibihugu bitandukanye (Country Policy Tracker) zo gukomeza uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima n'ubukungu bw'isi, gukemura ingaruka z'igenzurwa ry'abantu n'ingamba zo kutagenda mu gihugu, mu rwego rwo gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no guteza imbere uburyo bwo guhangana na coronavirus ku isi hose.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Inama y'Abaminisitiri y'Ubwongereza Michael Gove na Eduardo Bolsonaro, umuhungu wa Perezida wa Bresil, Jair Bolsonaro, kubera ibikorwa byakozwe mu kurwanya icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi benshi b'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CCP) ku rwego rw'intara birukanywe kubera ingamba z'ikumira bari bafatiye mu gace k'iburengerazuba bw'u Bushinwa, kandi ibyo birukanwa byerekana ko badashimishijwe n'ibikorwa by'ubutegetsi bwo muri ako karere byo kwishyura iki cyorezo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko icyo cyemezo cyari kigamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti b'u Bushinwa, Xi Jinping, uburakari bw'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ibyavuzwe mbere ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, ariko bashyigikira igitekerezo cy'ubuvugizi kivuga ko COVID-19 yakomotse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Donald Trump bwise coronavirus virusi yo mu Bushinwa cyangwa virusi yo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, buvuga ko gushyiraho igitutu mu Bushinwa byongera ikibazo cya virusi ubu imaze kuba icyorezo ku isi, kandi ibyo byavuzwe na bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo, bavuga ko ubwo buryo ari ubw'ivangura rishingiye ku moko kandi bwibagiza ubushobozi bw'ubuyobozi bwa Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
The Daily Beast yabonye telegrama ya leta ya Amerika irimo amayeri y'itumanaho, bigaragara ko yateguwe n'akanama gashinzwe umutekano w'igihugu, harimo amagambo avuga ku buryo: "Byose biri mu Bushinwa".
Dusabwe gukwirakwiza aya makuru mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama n'abanyamakuru no kuvugira kuri televiziyo. Imiryango nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg, yavuze ko imbaraga z'Ubushinwa mu gufasha ibihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari igice cy' "ibikorwa by'itangazamakuru" mu rwego rwo gushaka kugira ijambo ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'ishami ry'ububanyi n'amahanga rya EU, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "igice cya politiki y'isi, kirimo guharanira kugira uruhare binyuze mu itumanaho n'abandi n'ibyo bita politiki y'ubuntu".
Borrell kandi yavuze ko Ubushinwa bushishikarira guteza imbere igitekerezo cy'uruhare rwabwo nk'umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe, bitandukanye na Amerika.
Ubushinwa bwasabye kandi Amerika gukuraho ibihano ku bihugu bya Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ndetse hari amakuru avuga ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Jack Ma yatanze udupfukamunwa 100,000 tw'ubuvuzi muri Cuba twabujijwe kubera ibihano bya Amerika byashyizweho ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kandi bashinjwa kuyobora imfashanyo zigenewe ibindi bihugu mu gihugu cyabo.
Ku bijyanye n'udupfukamunwa twa muganga, kandi havutse impaka hagati y'ibindi bihugu nk'u Budage, Autriche n'Ubusuwisi, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Uretse ibyo, Turukiya yemeye ibikoresho amagana bya I.V.L byateguriwe Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi utabashyigikiye mu gihugu cy'Ubutaliyani cyugarijwe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwagize icyo bukora ku buryo bw'impande zombi".
Ibi ntabwo bigaragaza ko hari ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'i Burayi.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuganira kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yateguye kohereza mu Butaliyani abasirikare b'abasilikare b'Abarusiya, imodoka zihariye zo kwanduza indwara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo y'umuntu utazwi umutungo wa politiki wo ku rwego rwo hejuru uvuga ko 80% by'ubufasha bw'Uburusiya bwari nta cyo bumaze cyangwa nta kamaro bufitiye Ubutaliyani.
Uwo muyobozi yashinje u Burusiya gushaka gutangaza ku isi hose ko bufite imyumvire myiza ku rwego rwa "geopolitique na diplomatie".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, n'umushikiranganji w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, banenze ibitero by'itangazamakuru, bashimira ubufasha bahawe.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege itwara imizigo iherekejwe n'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gufasha bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, [Putin] avuga ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bo muri Amerika bazongera umuvuduko w'umusaruro, na bo bazaba bashobora gutanga ubufasha mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO Umurinzi-2020, iteganijwe mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique  imyitozo ya gisirikare nini ya NATO nyuma y'iherezo ry'intambara y'ubutita  izakorwa mu buryo buciriritse.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament, Kate Hudson, yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 (Umurinzi-2020) ati: "Mu bihe by'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, iyi myitozo ntabwo iteza akaga gusa abasirikare ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi bigize uyu mutwe, ahubwo n'abaturage bo mu bihugu bigomba kuyoborerwamo iyo myitozo".
Ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi mu ibaruwa ifunguye asaba ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye gifite ibibazo byo guhangana n'icyorezo kubera kutagira amahirwe yo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyateje impaka ku Bufaransa ngo bwemere politiki z'imibereho y'abaturage nk'uko bimeze mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo gushyiraho uburyo bumwe bwo kwivuza no kwita ku bana, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihabwa amafaranga no kongera inkunga y'ubuzima rusange.
Abahanga mu bya politiki bari biteze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida yo mu 2020.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "ingamba z'igenzura zidahuje n'ukuri kandi zidafite icyo zivuze" zafashwe n'Ubuyapani nyuma y'aho Ubuyapani butangaje ko umuturage wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twateganyijwe na leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo watangiye ugabanyijwemo ibice n'igisubizo cy'umukuru w'igihugu Moon Jae-in kuri iki kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zishimira ibyo perezida yakoze cyangwa zisaba ko Bwana Moon acibwa ku butegetsi kubera ibyo babona ko leta itakoze neza mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko bafite impungenge ko iki cyemezo kizatuma ubutegetsi bw'igihugu bukomeza ububasha bwabwo.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yatoye guha Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orban uburenganzira buhoraho bwo gutegeka binyuze mu mategeko, guhagarika imirimo y'inteko ishinga amategeko, no gukora amatora no guhana abashinjwa gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi n'ingamba za leta zo guhangana n'ikibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyavuzwe ko ari cyo cyateye ibibazo byinshi byo kutagira ibikoresho byo gukoresha mu kurwanya iki cyorezo, kugura ibicuruzwa mu bihe by'ubwoba no guhagarika ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura ireme ry'ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, byatewe n'ubwiyongere bw'ibyifuzo by'abakiriya n'imikorere mibi y'abaguzi.
Mu duce tumwe na tumwe na ho habaye kugura ibintu mu buryo bwo gutinya; byatumye ibintu by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi y'ibyatsi biva ku maduka, bituma habaho ubukene.
Mu buryo bwihariye, inganda z'ikoranabuhanga zirimo kuburira ku bijyanye n'ibihombo byo gutinda gutanga ibicuruzwa bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije uko umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, abivuga, ibyifuzo by'ibikoresho byo kwirinda umubiri byazamutse inshuro 100.
Ibyo byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro makumyabiri ugereranyije n'ibiciro bisanzwe, kandi bituma ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bidatangira gutangwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Nanone kandi, byateje ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku isi hose, kandi OMS yatanze umuburo w'uko abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bashoboraga guhura n'ikibazo cy'ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Muri Australia kubera icyorezo, abaguzi bakoresheje uburyo bwa daigoo bahawe uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Australia mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye ibiribwa by'abana bibura mu masupamaketi amwe na amwe, nyuma bibuzanywa na leta ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 ari mwinshi mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, ndetse n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, muri utwo turere twombi habayeho gukemura ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubukungu no gucuruza ibinyabuzima mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko, zagize icyo zigeraho, bituma hatagira ibura ry'ibiribwa rikomeye ryari riteganyijwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani, aho ubuhinzi bufite ibipimo bito, nta gaciro kanini kabaye, ariko abacuruzi bavuga ko ibiciro by'ibiribwa bishobora kwiyongera.
Amashelfu y'amaduka y'ibiribwa yagumye ubusa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa batanze uburyo bwo kubona inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya bihagije.
Amategeko nk'ayo asaba abacuruza ibiribwa kubika ibiribwa mu gihe habaye ibyago, arahari no mu Butaliyani.
Ingaruka z'iki cyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zageze no mu Bushinwa: nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibitangazamakuru ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kurwanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, bituma ibicuruzwa by'abacuruzi bigabanukaho 20,5%.
Ubushinwa  ni ikigo gikomeye cy'ubukungu n'inganda; ni yo mpamvu bivugwa ko iki cyorezo cyateye kigamije guhungabanya umutekano w'isi.
Agatha Demarai, ukora mu kigo cy'ubutasi cya Economist Intelligence Unit, avuga ko ibiciro bizakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe hazabaho gusobanukirwa neza uko bizagenda.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bahanga mu gusesengura bavuze ko ingaruka z'icyorezo kiriho ubu ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga ingaruka z'icyorezo cya Pneumonia yo mu 2002-2004.
Hari umuhanga wo muri kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, wavuze ko ingaruka mbi z'ibyo bishobora kuba ku isoko ry'ibiribwa ku isi hose zishobora kurenga miriyari 300 z'amadolari, kandi ko zishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Bitangazwa ko Umuryango w'ibihugu bitanga peteroli (OPEC) watangiye gufata "ingamba z'ako kanya" nyuma y'igabanuka rikomeye ry'ibiciro by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli kubera kugwa kw'ibyifuzo by'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yarasenyutse kubera ubwiyongere bukomeye bw'abantu banduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera ubwoba bukomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo bitandukanye by'imari ya Amerika, birimo NASDAQ-100, index ya S&P 500 na Dow-Jones index y'imigabane y'amasosiyete y'inganda, byerekanye ugutaha cyane guhera mu 2008, hamwe na indice ya Dow yagabanutseho amanota 1191  ugutaha cyane mu munsi umwe kuva mu makuba y'imari yo mu 2007-2008 .
Mu mpera z'icyumweru, ibipimo byose uko ari bitatu byagabanutseho 10 ku ijana.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, ikigo cy'ubwishingizi cya Scope Ratings GmbH cyemeje indangamuntu y'ubusugire bw'Ubushinwa, ariko gikomeza igishoro kibi.
Ibiciro byongeye kumanuka kubera impungenge z'ikwirakwira rya coronavirus, ku itariki ya 16 y'ukwezi kwa gatatu.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko bishoboka ko ubukungu buzahinduka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba zihutirwa zafashwe n'amabanki yo hagati n'ibihugu.
Banki nkuru z'ibihugu zitabiriye vuba cyane kurusha uko byagenze mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'imari byo mu 2008.
Ubukerarugendo  ni kimwe mu bice byahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye kubera amategeko abuza abantu kugenda, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ahantu nyaburanga ho gutemberera, ndetse na leta zigira inama abantu kutagira ingendo.
Kubera izo ngamba zose, kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zahagaritse ingendo kubera ko ibyifuzo by'amatike byagabanutse cyane, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, kandi kompanyi y'indege y'akarere ka Ubwongereza Flybe yaretse kubaho.
Ingaruka mbi ku bucuruzi bw'amato y'ubwato bwagaragaye ko zikomeye kurusha mbere hose.
Sitasiyo nke z'indarayi n'ibibuga by'indege na byo byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyahuriranye na Chong-Yun, igihe cy'ingenzi cy'ubukerarugendo mu birori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa.
Guverinoma z'igihugu n'iz'akarere zahagaritse ibikorwa byinshi byitabiriwe n'abantu benshi, harimo n'ibirori ngarukamwaka byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya; ibigo byigenga na byo byafunze amaduka n'ahantu nyaburanga ho gutemberera nk'ahitwa Hong Kong na Shanghai Disneyland.
Imikino myinshi yo kwizihiza umwaka mushya yahagaritswe, kandi ahantu nyaburanga haherereye abantu benshi hafungiwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda abantu benshi; urugero nko mu mujyi wa Beijing, Umujyi wabuzanyijwe warafunzwe kandi amasoko y'urusengero gakondo yahagaritswe.
Mu ntara 24, mu ntara 31 z'u Bushinwa, abayobozi bongereye ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka inganda nyinshi kudakora kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ibi bice byabaga bifite 80% bya GDP y'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Abategetsi ba Hong Kong bazamuye igipimo cyo guhangana n'indwara zandura kugeza ku rwego rwo hejuru ndetse batangaza ibihe bidasanzwe, bafunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe kandi bahindura ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya. Urwego rw'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi rwahuye n'ingaruka ku rwego rw'isi yose: amasaha y'ubucuruzi yaragabanyijwe, ndetse n'amaduka amwe n'amwe afungwa by'agateganyo.
Gusura ibigo by'ubucuruzi mu Burayi na Amerika y'Amajyepfo byagabanutseho 40%.
Ibigo by'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwo muri Amerika ya Ruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati byagabanyije ibicuruzwa byabyo ku kigero cya 5060%.
Ibi byatumye muri Werurwe umubare w'abajya mu bigo by'ubucuruzi ugabanukaho 3343% ugereranyije n'uko byari bimeze muri Gashyantare.
Abafite ibigo by'ubucuruzi hirya no hino ku isi bashyizeho izindi ngamba nko kunoza isuku, gushyira ibikoresho byo kugenzura ubushyuhe bw'abashyitsi no guhagarika ibikorwa. Nk'uko byemezwa n'Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye gishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo, ubukene muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo buterwa n'icyorezo bushobora gutuma abantu miliyoni 14.22 barushaho kuba mu bukene ugereranyije n'uko byari kugenda mu gihe nk'icyo ariko nta cyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari cyogeye cyane mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni eshanu batakaje akazi mu Bushinwa.
Abenshi mu bakozi b'abimukira b'Abashinwa bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bari mu ngo zabo mu ntara zabo cyangwa bafungiwe mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi kabo maze basaba leta ubufasha.
Nk'uko byemezwa na Banki ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika ishinzwe imari n'imari (Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis), icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutuma muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika abantu miliyoni 47 batakaza akazi, kandi umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kugera kuri 32%. Ingamba zo kwigunga zashyizweho mu Buhinde zizatuma abakozi b'abimukira b'Abahinde babarirwa muri za miriyoni mirongo bahembwa buri munsi batagira akazi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cya Angus Reid bwagaragaje ko 44% by'ingo zo muri Kanada zagize ikibazo cy'ubushomeri. Abakozi b'Abanya Espagne bagera hafi ku 900,000 na bo batakaje akazi kabo kuva igihe muri Esipanye hashyirwaho gahunda y'igunga rikomeye hagati mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020.
Mu gice cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, abakozi b'Abafaransa miliyoni 4 basabye ubwishyu bw'akazi bw'agateganyo, naho abakozi b'Abongereza miliyoni 1 basabye amafaranga y'ubwishyu bw'akazi. Amashyirahamwe hafi ya miliyoni eshanu mu Budage yahinduye abakozi bayo ku kazi gahabwa inkunga na leta ko gukora amasaha make  amasaha y'akazi make.
Igishushanyo cy'amafaranga y'akazi k'iminota mike cyashyizwe mu Bufaransa no mu Bwongereza.
Urwego rw'ubuhanzi n'umurage w'umuco na rwo rwazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, cyibasiye ibikorwa by'imiryango ndetse n'abantu ku giti cyabo, baba abashinzwe akazi cyangwa abikorera, ku isi hose.
Amashyirahamwe y'umuco n'ubuhanzi yagerageje gushyigikira inshingano zayo (akenshi zitangwa na leta) zo kugeza ku baturage umurage w'umuco, bigatuma abakozi bayo n'abaturage babaho neza, kandi, aho bishoboka, bagashyigikira abantu b'ubuhanzi.
Muri Werurwe 2020, inzu ndangamurage, ibitabo, inzu z'ibitaramo n'izindi nyubako z'umuco byari bifunze ku isi hose igihe kitazwi cyangwa kwinjira muri byo bikaba byari bibujijwe mu buryo butandukanye, kandi imurikagurisha, ibikorwa n'ibitaramo byarahagaritswe cyangwa bisubikwa.
Ibindi byahise kandi bigenda byiyongera mu gukwirakwira kwa virusi ni ukuhagarika imirimo y'idini, ibikorwa bikomeye bya siporo n'ibindi bikorwa rusange nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga n'imurika imideli.
Mu by'ubucuruzi bw'amasinema na ho habaye ibibazo. Vatikani yatangaje ko yahagaritse ibikorwa by'icyumweru cya Pasika i Roma, kiba mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'igihe cy'ibyaha by'Abakristo  Igisibo.
Amadini menshi asaba Abakristo bageze mu za bukuru kuguma mu ngo zabo no kutajya mu materaniro yo ku Cyumweru; amadini amwe na amwe yatangiye gutangaza amateraniro kuri radiyo, kuri televiziyo cyangwa kuri televiziyo, mu gihe abayobozi b'andi madini batangiye gutanga inama yo guteranira hanze.
Diyosezi ya Roma-Gatolika yafunze insengero zayo, insengero n'ahantu hazwi nka St. Peter, aho abakirisitu batagaragara, nyuma y'aho andi madini nayo yahagaritse amasengesho kandi ahagarika kwinjira mu masengero, imisigiti, insengero, insengero n'amasengero.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu yahagaritswe mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo cya coronavirus, kandi nyuma yaho insengero zarafunzwe; Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abanyamahanga n'abaturage bayo kwinjira mu nsengero za Mecca na Medina.
Iki cyorezo cyatumye habaho impinduka zikomeye cyane ku ngengabihe y'imikino ku isi kuva mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Ibikorwa byinshi bikomeye by'imikino byarahagaritswe cyangwa byasubitswe, harimo UEFA Champions League 201920, Premier League 201920, UEFA Euro 2020, shampiyona ya NBA 201920 n'ishampiyona ya NHL 201920.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus kandi cyasenye gahunda yo gukora imikino ya Olympic yo mu mpeshyi ya 2020 yagombaga gutangira mu mpera za Nyakanga; ku ya 24 Werurwe, Komite Mpuzamahanga ya Olimpiki yatangaje ko iki gikorwa kizasubikwa nyuma ya 2020, ariko bitarenze impeshyi ya 2021. Kasino n'ibindi bigo by'imikino yo kwidagadura hirya no hino ku isi byafunzwe, kandi amarushanwa ya poker asanzwe yerekanwa imbonankubone nayo yasubitswe cyangwa yahagaritswe.
Ibi byatumye abakinnyi benshi bajya kuri interineti, kandi imbuga nyinshi zishinzwe gukina urusimbi zanditse ko umubare w'abashakaga gukina wazamutse cyane.
Amakinamico menshi akomeye, nka Broadway, nayo yahagaritse ibitaramo byose.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ibikorwa bisanzwe bitemewe, bamwe mu bahanzi n'abahanzi batangiye kwiga uburyo bwo gukomeza ibikorwa byabo no gusangira ibisubizo byabo kuri interineti, gutunganya ibiganiro byerekanwa kumbuga cyangwa ibirori byo kuri interineti; ibi bifasha abantu mu mwuga w'ubuhanzi gukomeza gukora, gutunganya cyangwa gutangaza ibihangano byabo.
Hari imyumvire myinshi kuri interineti ku byerekeye coronavirus, myinshi muri yo ikaba ari iy'urwenya kandi igamije guhosha imyumvire y'imihangayiko igaragara mu bihe by'umutekano muke.
Kuva COVID-19 yatangira, habayeho kwiyongera kw'ivangura, urwikekwe rw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura rishingiye ku moko ku baturage b'Ubushinwa n'abo mu bihugu byo muri Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, ndetse no ku baturage bo mu bihugu by'i Burayi, Amerika n'ahandi.
Hari ubwoba, gushidikanya n'urwango byagaragariye mu bihugu byinshi, cyane cyane mu Burayi, Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, Amerika ya Ruguru no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika.
Mu nkuru z'amakuru yo muri Gashyantare (igihe abenshi mu banduye bari bakiri mu Bushinwa) havugwamo umwuka w'ivangura rishingiye ku moko wagaragajwe n'amatsinda atandukanye ku isi yose ku baturage b'Ubushinwa bavuga ko bakwiriye iyi virusi cyangwa ko bahawe ibihembo bikwiriye.
Mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bya Afurika, hari kandi umwuka wo kurwanya Ubushinwa wiyongereye.
Abaturage benshi bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei bavuze ko bakorewe ivangura rishingiye ku moko yabo.
Abaturage b'Ubushinwa n'abatuye mu duce twatewe n'iyi virusi, bahawe ubufasha haba kuri interineti no hanze yayo.
Icyorezo cyatangiye gukwirakwira mu bihugu bishya, by'umwihariko mu Butaliyani  igihugu cya mbere mu Burayi cyahuye n'icyorezo gikomeye cya COVID-19; ku bw'ibyo, abaturage bo muri utwo turere bashobora gutangira kwiyumvisha ingaruka z'amakenga no kwanga abanyamahanga. Abaturage bo mu bihugu nka Malaysia, Nouvelle Zélande, Singapuru na Koreya y'Epfo mu ntangiriro bashyize umukono ku nyandiko isaba kubuza abaturage b'Ubushinwa kwinjira mu bihugu byabo mu rwego rwo guhashya icyorezo.
Mu Buyapani, hashtag #ChineseDontComeToJapan (#AbashinwaNtimuze mu Buyapani) yafashe umwanya wa mbere kuri Twitter.
Abashinwa ndetse n'abandi bantu bo muri Aziya baba mu Bwongereza no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, batangaza ko umwuka w'ivangura rishingiye ku moko ndetse n'ibitero by'ubwoko biri kwiyongera.
Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Donald Trump yanenzwe cyane kubera ko yise coronavirus virusi yo mu Bushinwa; abamusebya bavuga ko ari igitekerezo cy'ivangura rishingiye ku moko n'icya kinyamaswa.
Muri Ukraine abigaragambya bagabye igitero kuri bisi zitwaraga abaturage ba Ukraine n'abanyamahanga bari bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan bajya mu mujyi wa New Sanjar.
Abanyeshuri bava mu majyaruguru ashyira uburasirazuba bw'u Buhinde buhana imbibi n'u Bushinwa, biga mu mijyi minini y'u Buhinde, bavuze ko bakorewe ibikorwa by'ihohoterwa bijyanye n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Dilip Ghosh, Perezida w'ishyaka rya Bharatiya Janata, mu ntara ya Bengali y'uburengerazuba, yavuze ko Abashinwa basenyeye ibidukikije kandi ko "Imana yabahaye igihano".
Nyuma y'aho, ibyo yavuze byamaganiwe nabi n'ibiro by'ubuserukizi bw'Ubushinwa i Calcutta, bivuga ko ari "ikinyoma".
Ibinyamakuru byinshi bishyura amakuru byavanyeho izo mbogamizi ku bice bimwe na bimwe cyangwa byose byibasiwe na coronavirus.
