Ibizamini bya laboratwari bya coronavirus y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ifitanye isano na yo SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo kumenya niba virusi iriho n'uburyo bwo kumenya abasirikare b'umubiri baturuka ku cyorezo.
Kuba virusi ziboneka mu bipimo byemezwa na OT-PCR, imenya RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki kizamini ni icy'umwihariko kandi kigamije gusa gutahura RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu buherutse cyangwa bukomeje.
Kugaragaza antibody (serology) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma indwara no kugenzura umubare w'abantu.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo batajyanwa mu bitaro cyangwa batabonetse.
Ibipimo by'urupfu rw'iyo ndwara n'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara bishobora kumenyekana binyuze mu gupima.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira rya virusi mu baturage kubera ubushobozi buke bwo gupima.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarashoboye gupima abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi amakuru ku bipimo byakozwe mu bihugu bitandukanye aratandukanye cyane.
Birashoboka ko ubwo butandukanire mu makuru ari bwo bufite ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, ishobora kuba yarashyizwe hejuru cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa 'reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction' (rRT-PCR) ubu bushakashatsi bushobora gukorwa ku bipimo byo mu mwuka bivanze n'uburyo butandukanye, harimo no gufata isura y'umuhogo cyangwa isura y'umwanda.
Ibisubizo bikunze kugaragara mu gihe cy'amasaha make kugeza ku minsi ibiri.
Igishushanyo cya OTT-PCR cyakozwe ku bipande by'uruti rw'umugongo, kiba gihuje n'igihe cy'icyumweru cya mbere cy'uburwayi.
Nyuma virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo ariko ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku barwayi banduye, bapimwa mu cyumweru cya kabiri cy'indwara, mu buryo bunyuranye, bashobora gufata ibintu mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi hifashishijwe catéteur yo kumira, cyangwa se bashobora gukoresha ibyokurya byo guhekenya (umwanda).
Imwe mu ngero za mbere za PCR yakozwe mu bitaro bya Charité, Berlin, muri Mutarama 2020 ikoresheje uburyo bwa polymerase chain reaction with real-time reverse transcription (rRT-PCR) maze iba ishingiro ry'udupande 250,000 twaje gukwirakwizwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020, Ubwongereza nabwo bwakoze ikizamini cyabwo. Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, isosiyete yo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech yakoze igikoresho cyo gutahura SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR yo ku rwego rw'ubuvuzi (PowerChek Coronavirus).
Igaragaraho ingirabuzima fatizo E, ihuriweho na koronavirusi zose za beta, n'ingirabuzima fatizo RdRp, ihuriweho na SARS-CoV-2. Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa BGI Group ni kimwe mu bigo bya mbere byahawe uruhushya n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Imiti cyo mu Bushinwa rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa ibikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 bishingiye kuri PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyakwirakwiza ikigo cy'isi (International Reagent Resource) gikoresha ikigo cyacyo cyo gupima mu gihe nyacyo (Real-Time RT-PCR Diagnostic Panel) mu bigo by'ubuvuzi rusange.
Imwe mu bipimo bitatu bya jenoside byo mu bwoko bwa kera bw'ibipimo byatanze ibisubizo bidahagije kubera ibipimo bidakora neza n'akarere gato CDC ikoreramo ibizamini muri Atlanta; ku buryo mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare 2020 kose, ku kigereranyo, ibipimo 100 ku munsi byakozwe neza.
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyari byemewe kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi nyuma y'iyo tariki ni bwo laboratoire za leta n'iz'ibanze zemerewe gutangira gupima.
Ibizamini byemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indyo n'imiti mu rwego rw'uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa. Laboratwari z'ubucuruzi zo muri Amerika zatangiye gupima mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko ishobora gukora ibizamini bya COVID-19 bishingiye kuri RT-PCR mu gihugu hose.
Quest Diagnostics yatangiye gupima COVID-19 mu gihugu hose kuva ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta ngero z'ibimenyetso byatanzwe; gufata no gutunganya ibipimo bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyakozwe n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubushakashatsi mu Bumenyi bw'Ibinyabuzima n'Ibinyabuzima cya VEKTOR.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki kizamini cyanditswe n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ubugenzuzi bw'Ubuzima. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, byatangajwe ko Ivuriro rya Mayo ryateguye ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukoresha iki kizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3,5 ku bipimo byinshi, bigatuma imashini imwe ishobora gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwihuse rwo gukoresha (EUA) ku ma laboratoire ya Abbott kugirango ikore ibizamini by'uburyo bwa Abbott m2000; mbere FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya nk'urwo kuri Hologic, LabCorp na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid kandi yahawe EUA na FDA ku gipimo cy'iminota igera kuri 45.
FDA yemeje kandi ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongerera ingano za isothermic nucleic acid aho gukoresha PCR.
Kubera ko iki kizamini kidakeneye uruhererekane rw'ibihe by'ubushyuhe, ubu buryo bushobora kugaragaza ibisubizo byiza mu minota itanu gusa, naho ibisubizo bibi  mu minota 13.
Muri iki gihe muri Amerika hari imashini nk'izo zigera ku 18,000, kandi Abbott iteganya kongera umusaruro kugeza ku bipimo 50,000 ku munsi. Muri iki gihe muri Tayiwani hari gukorwa ikizamini gikoresha umuti wa monoclonal, wifatanya n'indwara ya coronavirus mu buryo bwihariye, kandi hari icyizere cyo kubona ibisubizo mu minota 15-20 nk'ikizamini cya vuba cya grippe.
Isesengura ry'ibitabo by'umwuga ryo muri Werurwe 2020 ryavuze ko rentgenograms z'igituza nta gaciro kanini zifite mu gusuzuma indwara mu bihe bya mbere, mu gihe ibiva mu isuzuma ry'imikorere ya CT [computing tomography] bishobora kugira agaciro kabyo mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragara muri CT birimo ibipimo bibiri by'ibice byinshi by'ibice by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure by'ibinure.
Subpleural domination, ikimenyetso cy'uruti rw'umugongo n'ubwiyunge bigenda byiyongera uko indwara igenda irushaho gukomera.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwagereranyije uburyo bwa PCR na CT bwakoreshejwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan igihe iki cyorezo cyatangiraga, byagaragaje ko CT ifite ubushobozi bwo kumva neza kurusha PCR, nubwo idakomeye cyane kuko imikorere yayo myinshi yo kureba ihura n'ibindi bikorwa byo kurwara ibicurane n'izindi ndwara.
Kuva muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe Imikorere y'Imiradiyo cyatangaje inama yo kudakoresha CT mu gupima cyangwa nk'uburyo bwo gupima bwa mbere mu gupima COVID-19. Kuva muri Werurwe 2020, CDC itera inkunga yo gukoresha PCR mu gupima bwa mbere.
Igisubizo cy'umubiri ku cyorezo kigaragarira mu gukora za antibody zirimo IgM na IgG.
Izi nsoro zishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ubwandu mu bantu nyuma y'umunsi wa 7 w'ibimenyetso, mu kumenya ubudahangarwa no mu rwego rwo kugenzura abaturage. Ibizamini bishobora gukorwa muri laboratwari nkuru (CLT) cyangwa binyuze mu gupima ku mwanya (PoCT)
Muri za laboratwari nyinshi, ibizamini bishobora gukorwa n'uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga bufite ubushobozi bwo gukora neza, ariko ubushobozi bwabyo buzaba bushingiye ku muvuduko buri buryo bwo gukora buzaba bwaragezeho.
Muri CLT, akenshi hakoreshwa icyitegererezo kimwe cy'amaraso y'uruhande, nubwo ibipimo byinshi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gukurikirana ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri.
