Ubwongereza bwabonye ko nta gikoresho na kimwe cy'isuzuma ry'umubiri cyatanga umusaruro ushimishije mu ntangiriro za Mata.
Muri Hong Kong, hashyizweho uburyo bwo kureka abarwayi bakekwaho virusi bagasigara mu rugo: abakozi bo mu bitaro by'ubutabazi bw'ibanze baha umurwayi akato ko gufataho ibipimo, umurwayi agateramo amate, akagarura maze nyuma y'igihe runaka akagira ibisubizo by'ibizamini. NHS y'Ubwongereza yatangaje ko yatangije gahunda yayo yo gupima abantu bakekwaho virusi mu rugo, ikuraho ibyago byo kwandura abandi bantu baza mu ivuriro, cyangwa gukenera kuvura imodoka ya ambulance niba yakoreshejwe mu gutwara umurwayi. Mu gihe cyo gupima COVID-19 mu buryo bwihuse, umukozi w'ubuzima afata ibizamini mu gihe hari abantu bakekwaho COVID-19, akoresha ingamba zose zikwiriye.
Ku ya 2 Werurwe, mu Budage, Ishyirahamwe ry'abaganga bafite ubwisungane mu kwivuza ry'igihugu (National Association of Compulsory Medical Insurance Doctors) ryavuze ko ryiteguye gukora ibizamini bigera ku 12.000 ku munsi mu bitaro, mu gihe mu cyumweru gishize ryashoboraga gukora ibizamini 10.700 gusa mu cyumweru.
Iyo umuganga aguhaye ibizamini, ubwisungane mu kwivuza burakwishyura.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na Perezida w'Ikigo Robert Koch, umusaruro rusange w'Ubudage mu gupima ni ibipimo 160.000 mu cyumweru.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, byatangijwe ko hatangwa uburyo bwo gupima mu mijyi minini.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'ibizamini byose byakozwe mu Budage ntiwari uzwi kuko hari ibizamini byerekana ko umuntu yanduye gusa.
