Nyuma yo gufungura laboratoire i Wuhan, laboratwari za Huo-Yan zahise zifungura i Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing na Shanghai  mu mijyi 12 yo mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, ubushobozi rusange bwa buri munsi bwari bwarageze ku bipimo 50,000 ku munsi. Imikorere ya Origami Assays yabonetse ku mugaragaro ishobora gupima ibipimo bigera ku 1,122 by'abarwayi ba COVID19 hifashishijwe ibipimo 93 gusa. Ibishushanyo mbonera nk'ibi bishobora gukora mu ma laboratwari mato, bikirinda gukoresha imashini zikoresha amazi.
Muri Werurwe, kubera ibura n'ibura ry'imiti, kugerageza abantu benshi muri EU, Ubwongereza na Amerika byabaye ikibazo.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko hari abanditsi bamwe na bamwe bahindukiriye ku mabwiriza yo gutunganya ibizamini, agena ko ibizamini bishyushye ku gipimo cya 98°C (208°F) mu gihe cy'iminota 5 kugira ngo genome za RNA zishobore gukurwaho kugira ngo zikore ibindi bizamini. Ku ya 31 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko umubare w'ibizamini bya coronavirus by'abatuye Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abarabu kuri buri muntu ubu urenze uw'ibindi bihugu byose, kandi ko vuba aha abaturage benshi bazaba bamaze gupimwa.
Ibi byatewe n'ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini byihuta, hamwe no kugura Group 42 na BGI ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku bantu benshi (cyashinzwe hashingiwe ku bigo byabo by'ubushakashatsi ku bibazo byihutirwa bya Huo-Yan mu Bushinwa).
Iki kigo cy'ubushakashatsi cyatangiye mu minsi 14, gishobora gukora ibizamini bya RT-PCR ibihumbi n'ibihumbi ku munsi, kikaba ari cyo kigo cya mbere ku isi cyakoze ibizamini byinshi biturutse hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Ibipimo bitandukanye byibanda ku bice bitandukanye by'imiterere ya koronavirusi byakozwe mu Bushinwa, u Bufaransa, u Budage, Hong Kong, u Buyapani na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima ryemeye gukoresha uburyo bw'Abadage bwo gukora udupfunyika two gupima, twoherezwa mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, bidafite ubushobozi bwo gukora udupfunyika twabyo.
Ubwoko bw'ikidage bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 17 Mutarama 2020; Itegeko Nshinga ryateguwe n'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo ntiryashoboraga kuboneka kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama, bituma nta bikoresho byo gupima muri Amerika biboneka. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, mu Bushinwa no muri Amerika habayeho ibibazo bijyanye no kwizerwa kw'ibikoresho byo gupima, kandi ibyo bihugu, kimwe na Ositaraliya, ntibyashoboye gutanga ibikoresho bihagije byasabwe n'inzobere mu by'ubuzima.
Ariko muri Koreya y'Epfo, abahanga bavuga ko kuba abantu benshi bashobora gupimwa byagabanyije ikwirakwira rya coronavirus nshya.
Mu myaka myinshi, leta ya Koreya y'Epfo yakoraga ku buryo haboneka uburyo bwo gupima, cyane cyane mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi byigenga.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko gahunda zo gupima zongera gukorwa nk'uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19. Kubera ko ubushake bwo gupima bwiyongera bitewe n'ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi mu buryo bwihuse, laboratwari nyinshi z'abikorera muri Amerika zari zifite ibipimo ibihumbi amagana by'ibipimo, zararushye cyane, kandi ibikoresho byo gufata ibipimo n'ibikoresho by'imiti byagabanutse vuba.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hari ibibazo by'ubuziranenge bw'ibikoresho by'ibizamini.
Ibikoresho by'ibizamini bya Amerika byakozwe na CDC byari bifite "inenge", kandi kubera iyo mpamvu guverinoma yakuyeho inzitizi z'ubutegetsi zabuzaga iterambere ry'ibizamini ku giti cyabo. Espagne yaguze ibikoresho by'ibizamini ku kigo cy'Ubushinwa Shenzhen Bioeasy Biotechnology Co Ltd, ariko isanga ibisubizo byo gukoresha ibyo bikoresho bitari ukuri.
Ikigo cyasobanuye ko kuba ibipimo bitagenze neza bishobora guterwa no gufata ibipimo nabi cyangwa gukoresha nabi ibipimo.
Minisiteri ya Espagne yatangaje ko izakuraho udupaki dutanga ibisubizo bidahuje n'ukuri, tukazahindurwa n'utundi dutanga ibisubizo bitangwa na Shenzhen Bioeasy. 80% by'udupaki dutanga ibizamini u Bushinwa bwaguze muri Repubulika y'Ubushinwa twagize ibisubizo bidakwiriye. Udupaki miliyoni 1,2 twaguzwe na Slovakia mu Bushinwa na two twafashwe nk'udatunganye.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Matovic yasabye ko izo mpapuro zishyirwa mu Ruzi rwa Danube. Atesh Kara, umukozi wa Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Turukiya, yavuze ko ibikoresho byo gupima byaguzwe mu Bushinwa byari bifite "ibipimo byinshi by'amakosa" kandi Minisiteri "ntiyakomeje kubikoresha". Ubwongereza bwaguze ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 3,5 mu Bushinwa, ariko mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020 byatangajwe ko ibyo bikoresho bitakibasha gukoreshwa.
Ingamba zo gushyira mu kato abantu bagaragaweho SARS-CoV-2 no kugenzura abantu bagiranye na bo imishyikirano, byagize ingaruka nziza.
Abashakashatsi bakorera mu mujyi wa Vaud wo mu Butaliyani, aho umuntu wa mbere wapfuye azize COVID-19 mu Butaliyani, bakoze ibizamini bibiri ku baturage bose bagera ku 3400, buri muntu agenzurwa mu gihe cy'iminsi igera ku icumi.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abantu basanze barwaye nta bimenyetso bagaragazaga, kandi abarwayi bose bari bamaze kwemezwa ko barwaye bashyizwe mu kato.
Kwinjira mu gace kagenzurwa n'abaturage byarahagaritswe, kandi iki cyemezo cyahagaritse burundu ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu.
Kubera ko abantu benshi bari gukurikiranwa, abantu bagahabwa ibihano byo kwinjira, gupimwa no gushyirwa mu kato, icyorezo cya coronavirus cyo mu 2020 muri Singapore cyarangwaga n'ubwiyongere buke ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu byateye imbere, kandi ntibyabaga ngombwa ko hashyirwaho amategeko akomeye nko gufunga amazu y'ubucuruzi n'amaresitora.
Imikino myinshi yarasubitswe, maze ku ya 28 Werurwe, Singapore itangira gusaba abaturage kuguma mu ngo, ariko amashuri yarangiye ku ya 23 Werurwe, yongeye gufungura nk'uko byari biteganyijwe.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe, urugero nka Isilande na Koreya y'Epfo, na byo byabashije guhangana n'iki cyorezo binyuze mu gukurikirana cyane abantu, kugabanya abajya mu bihugu bitandukanye, gupima no gushyira mu kato, ariko ibyo bihugu ntibyakoresheje ingufu nyinshi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko mu bihugu byagize ibipimo byinshi ugereranyije n'ibipfa, umubare w'abapfa wari muke cyane, wenda kubera ko ibyo bihugu byabashije kubona abarwayi benshi bafite ibimenyetso bike cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
OMS isaba ibihugu bidafite ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu benshi, ndetse n'amavuriro y'igihugu adafite ubumenyi buhagije mu guhangana na COVID-19, kohereza ibipimo bitanu bya mbere bya COVID-19 byabonetse n'ibipimo icumi bya mbere byabonetse ko nta bimenyetso bya COVID-19 byabonetse muri kimwe mu bigo 16 by'ubugenzuzi bya OMS kugira ngo bikore ibizamini.
Muri ibyo bigo 16 by'ubushakashatsi, 7 biri muri Aziya, 5 biri mu Burayi, 2 biri muri Afurika, 1 biri muri Amerika ya Ruguru na 1 biri muri Ositaraliya.
Mu mbonerahamwe ikurikira, imibare yo mu nkingi % y'ibisubizo byiza itandukana n'amategeko y'ibizamini yemewe mu gihugu runaka.
Igihugu kigenzura abarwayi bari mu bitaro gusa, kizaba gifite igipimo cyo hejuru cy'abanduye ugereranyije n'igihugu kigenzura abaturage bose, batitaye ku bimenyetso bya virusi, mu bindi byose bingana.
Gukaraba intoki, nanone bizwi nka isuku y'intoki  ni igikorwa cyo gusukura intoki hagamijwe gukuraho imyanda, ibinure, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu byangiza.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabuni mu bihe bimwe na bimwe bigoye mu gihe cy'umunsi birinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibiheri na kolera, zikwirakwizwa n'ibinure.
Umuntu ashobora kandi kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane bisanzwe, urugero nk'iyo akoze ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa (ni ukuvuga mu muhogo) n'amaboko adakaravye.
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi wo gukaraba intoki n'isabuni: mbere na nyuma yo gusama, nyuma yo gukaraba umwana cyangwa guhindura indimu, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere na nyuma yo guteka cyangwa gutunganya inyama, amafi n'inkoko.
Iyo nta mazi n'isabune bihari, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imyanda. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ritanga inama yo gukaraba intoki:
Mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Nyuma yo guhindura indimu cyangwa gukaraba umwana nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero.
Nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa gutera akabariro.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ibiryo cyangwa imyanda y'inyamaswa.
Isuku y'amaboko ni ibikorwa by'isuku bijyanye n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gufata imiti cyangwa se mbere yo gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina, bishobora gutuma indwara idakwirakwira cyangwa se ntizigire n'ingaruka nyinshi.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ukuzavura intoki zanduye (indwara, virusi cyangwa ibindi binyabuzima bishobora gutera indwara), ndetse n'ibinyabutabire bishobora kwangiza cyangwa gutera indwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora mu byo guteka cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bandi bantu bose.
Gukaraba intoki ni byiza cyane ku buzima bwacu, urugero nko kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zitandura, kwirinda indwara z'ibicurane, kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ubuhumekero,
kandi bikanagabanya impfu z'abana babyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwo mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iziterwa n'iseru ushobora kugabanuka binyuze mu kwitoza imico yoroheje, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Ubwo buryo bworoheje bushobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa kubera izo ndwara hafi 50%.
Kwibutsa abantu akamaro ko gukaraba intoki buri gihe bishobora kugabanya indwara y'umusongaho ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo bishobora kugereranywa n'inyungu zo kubona amazi meza mu turere dukennye.
Kugabanuka kw'ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'igifu ku kigero cya 48% bishobora kuba biterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni  ni bwo buryo bumwe rukumbi bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda igifu n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (IND), mu gihe habayeho imigenzo ikwiriye mu ngo zose, mu mashuri no mu bindi bibuga by'abaturage ku isi hose.
Pneumonia, imwe mu ndwara zikomeye ziterwa n'indwara z'ibicurane,  ni yo mpamvu nyamukuru ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, igahitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'igifu n'imyuka y'amaraso bihitana abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Bana rivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero, bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa ubundi buryo bwo kuvura, kandi bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri icyorezo cy'indwara y'igifu, naho icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero bikabije bikagabanya kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki bikunze gukoreshwa hamwe n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku bikorwa muri gahunda z'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda impetigo  indwara yandura iyo umuntu ahuriyeho n'undi muntu.
Ingaruka mbi nkeya zo gukaraba intoki kenshi ni uko bishobora gutuma uruhu rukomera, bityo rukangirika.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira itako n'uruhu rw'uruhu  indwara izwi nka eczema cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, ikunze kugaragara cyane mu bakora mu by'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane bishobora no kuba kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu byitwa ibihe bikomeye mu gihe cy'umunsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura indwara binyuze mu kanwa: nyuma yo gusama (gukorora, gutakaza), nyuma yo gukaraba ibere ry'umwana (guhindura indimu), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo guteka cyangwa gutunganya inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Hari ibindi bihe byo gukaraba intoki mu kwirinda kwandura: mbere cyangwa nyuma yo gukemura igikomere cyangwa igikomere, nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa guhumeka, nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'inyamaswa cyangwa inyamaswa, nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, gukaraba intoki n'isabune ntibyakoreshejwe cyane.
Ubushakashatsi ku myosozo y'amaboko bwakozwe mu 2015 mu bihugu 54 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo, imiryango 38.7% yoza intoki n'isabuni  ari umuco wemewe. Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko igipimo cyo hejuru, 97%, cyagaragaye muri Arabiya Sawudite; Amerika iri hafi y'uru rutonde, igipimo cyabo ni 77%; igipimo cyo hasi cyagaragaye mu Bushinwa  23%. Ubu hari uburyo bwinshi bwo guhindura imyitwarire no kwitoza imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mu bihe bikomeye. Mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki mu matsinda y'abanyeshuri ku masaha yemewe y'umunsi  ni bumwe mu buryo bufasha kwigisha abana gukoresha ubwo buryo.
Gahunda y'ubuvuzi bwihutirwa ishyirwa mu bikorwa na Minisiteri y'Uburezi ya Filipine,  ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'ubwisanzure mu kwita ku buzima bw'abana no kubongerera ubumenyi.
Muri gahunda y'igihugu hose, habaho kugabanya ibicurane by'amabere, bikorwa kabiri mu mwaka, gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune no gusukura amenyo buri munsi ukoresheje fluorine.
Iyo gahunda ni na yo ikomeje gukorwa neza muri Indoneziya.
Gukura udukoko duto mu ruhu birushaho kugenda neza iyo mu gihe cyo gukaraba wongeyemo isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gusukura.
Igikorwa cy'ibanze cya isabune n'ibikoresho byo gusukura ni ukuvanaho inzitizi zo gukama no kuzamura igipimo cyayo.
Amazi ubwayo ntabwo afatwa nk'umuti mwiza wo gusukura uruhu kuko ibinure na poroteyine, ari nabyo bigize imyanda iba mu mubiri, bitemba nabi mu mazi.
Ariko kandi, amazi ahagije atuma ibyo biruhuko biba byiza.
Amasabuni akomeye, kubera ko akoreshwa kenshi, ashobora no kuba arimo za bagiteri zishobora kuyatera iyo akoreshejwe mbere.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwakozwe ku mikorobe z'uruhu zanduye zivuye ku isabune ikomeye, bugaragaza ko nta mikorobe nyinshi zihaba kuko iyo mikorobe zinyura mu busa.
CDC iracyemeza ko isabune y'amazi ifite umutobe w'intoki ari bwo buryo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki.
Amasabuni arwanya za mikorobe arahabwa agaciro cyane mu baturage bita ku buzima bwabo.
Kugeza ubu nta gihamya na kimwe cyerekana ko gukoresha imiti yo guhanagura cyangwa guhanagura indwara bifasha mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'imiti.
Ariko rero, isabune irwanya za mikorobe irimo imiti isanzwe irwanya za mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, irwanya ubwoko bwinshi bw'ibinyabuzima bidashobora kwandura iyo mikorobe.
Bityo, nubwo udukoko twirinda imiti ya antibiyotike tutarobanura neza ku byerekeye isabune ya antibiyotike, dushobora kuba tudakora neza nk'uko byatangajwe.
Usibye ibintu bikora ku mubiri n'ibikoresho byo kurinda uruhu, ibintu bikomeye birashobora kuba birimo aside (acide, ascorbic, amata) nk'umugenzuzi wa pH, hamwe na aside ikora ku mikorobe yitwa benzoic hamwe n'ibindi bihumanya (aloe vera, vitamini, menthol, ibimera). isesengura ryuzuye ryakozwe n'Ishuri ry'Ubuzima bw'Abaturage muri Kaminuza ya Oregon ryerekanye ko mu kwirinda indwara no gukura mikorobe ku ruhu rw'amaboko, amoko yoroheje ya isabune afite ingaruka nziza nk'isabune isanzwe irwanya mikorobe irimo triclosan.
Amazi ashyushye afite ubushyuhe bw'uruhu rw'umuntu, ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ngo yice mikorobe.
Bakteriya zikubura vuba cyane iyo umubiri ufite ubushyuhe bwa dogere 37 C.
Ariko mu gukuraho ibinure by'ibanze bituma imyanda n'udukoko tudahita tubaho, amazi ashyushye ya savoni arakora neza kurusha amazi akonje.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babibona, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta cyo bihindura ku mikorobe ziba ku biganza.
Ikimera cyo guhanagura udukoko mu biganza (sanitizer) cyangwa umuti w'ibicurane mu biganza  ni umuti wo gusukura intoki udafite amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki ku bw'isukari bidafite amazi (bizwi kandi nk'imiti yo guhumanya intoki ku bw'isukari, imiti yo guhumanya intoki cyangwa sanitizer) byatangiye kwamamara.
Benshi muri ibi bikoresho bikozwe ku ishingiro rya isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol hamwe no kongeramo ibibyimba, nk'ibya karbomer (polymer ya acrylic acid) mu buryo bwa gel, cyangwa ibintu byoroshya, nk'ibya glycerine mu buryo bw'amazi cyangwa bw'ibihu, bitanga uburyo bwo gukoresha ibi bikoresho kandi bigabanya ingaruka zo kumesa uruhu na alcohol.
Kongeramo hydrogen peroxide yagabanutse bituma imiti yica mikorobe irushaho gukora neza. Imiti yica mikorobe irimo nibura 60-95% bya alukoro, yica mikorobe neza.
Imiti yica udukoko, harimo udukoko tw'ibiyobyabwenge twirinda imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), igituntu, ndetse na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo SIDA, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, urukingo, ibicurane na hepatite) na fungus.
Imiti yica udukoko tugize intungamubiri irimo 70% by'inzoga yica 99,97% by'udukoko (logarithme yo kugabanya 3,5 isa n'igabanyaho 35 decibel) ku maboko nyuma y'amasegonda 30 nyuma yo kuyikoresha na 99,99%  99,999% ya bagiteri (logarithme yo kugabanya 45) ku maboko nyuma y'umunota 1 nyuma yo kuyikoresha. Imiti yica udukoko iba ifite ingaruka nziza cyane ku mikorobe ariko ikaba idafite ingaruka nziza ku mikorobe zimwe na zimwe.
Imiti yica udukoko ikoreshwa na alcohol nta ngaruka igira ku mikorobe z'ubwoko bwa Norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ikaba ari yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara y'urwungano rw'amaraso.
Umutwe n'inyuma by'ibiganza byombi, hamwe n'ahantu hagati y'intoki ku burebure bwose, birasukwaho amasegonda agera kuri 30 kugeza amazi, ifu cyangwa umutobe byinjiye burundu.
Inkoranyamaganza z'intoki zombi na zo zigomba gukaraba neza. Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo guhitamo gukaraba intoki aho gukoresha imiti yica udukoko, cyane cyane iyo intoki zanduye cyane.
Kuba ibi bikoresho byanduza indwara byarakunzwe cyane biterwa n'uko byoroshye kubikoresha kandi bikuraho udukoko twangiza vuba, ariko ntibikwiye gusimbura gukaraba intoki neza niba hari uburyo bwo gukoresha amazi n'isabune.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yica udukoko mu ntoki ikoreshwa kuri alukoro bishobora gutuma uruhu rukonja, niba itarimo imiti yo koroshya uruhu na (cyangwa) imyuka imuhumuriza.
Ingaruka zo kumesa uruhu na alukoro zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa zikarandurwa hifashishijwe kongera glycerine na (cyangwa) ibindi bintu byoroshya mu buryo bw'imiti.
Mu igerageza ry'imiti, imiti yica udukoko ikoreshwa mu gusukura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga irimo ibintu bigabanya ubuhuha, yatuma uruhu rudakara cyane kandi rukagira isesemi kurusha isabune cyangwa imiti yo gusukura intoki.
Indwara y'uruhu ituma umuntu ahura n'ibindi bintu, indwara y'ibicurane cyangwa kumva inzoga cyangwa ibindi bintu biboneka mu bikoresho by'ubuvuzi, ntaho bihuriye n'iyo ndwara.
Kuba abantu badafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara y'uruhu rw'uruhu, byatumye bahitamo imiti yica udukoko ibafasha kurusha isabune n'amazi.
Nubwo bikora neza, imiti idafite amazi ntiyica ibigize intoki ahubwo irazihumanya.
Niyo mpamvu imiti yica udukoko twanduza intoki idakora neza mu gukumira mikorobe nyinshi zitera indwara nk'uko isabune n'amazi bisanzwe bikora, kuko iyo ikoreshwa mikorobe zitera indwara zikomeza kuba ku maboko.
Imikorere y'imiti yica udukoko mu ntoki itarimo inzoga, ahanini iba ishingiye ku bice by'umubiri n'ibikoresho byayo, kandi mu mateka yagiye iba iri hasi cyane ugereranyije n'imiti irimo inzoga cyangwa irimo inzoga.
Vuba aha cyane, byagaragaye ko imiti ikoresha benzalkonium chloride ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe buhoraho kandi bwongera, bitandukanye n'inzoga, yagaragaye ko itabasha gukora nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, bishoboka ko biterwa n'ingaruka ziterwa n'uruhu.
Abantu benshi mu baturage batunze amafaranga make ntibashobora kwigurira isabune, bityo bakayisimbuza ibumba cyangwa ibumba.
Ivu cyangwa ibumba bishobora kuba bifite akamaro kurusha amazi gusa, ariko bizahora bifite akamaro gake ugereranyije n'isabune.
Ikibazo kimwe kiri muri ubwo buryo ni uko iyo ibumba cyangwa umukungugu byanduye, bishobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira.
Kimwe n'isabune, ivu ni umuti wica udukoko kuko iyo rihuye n'amazi ritera umuti wa alkali.
Iyo isabune itaboneka, OMS itera inkunga yo gukoresha ivu cyangwa umucanga.
Kugira ngo wirinde kwandura, Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki, harimo:
Jya usukura intoki zawe mu mazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Amazi acuncubuka ni yo akwiriye kuko amazi ahagaze ashobora kwanduzwa, ariko ubushyuhe bw'amazi nta cyo buvuze.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune nyinshi, harimo n'iz'inyuma y'ibiganza, hagati y'intoki n'ibirenge.
Amasabuni akura mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko iyo abantu bakoresheje isabune (aho gukoresha amazi yonyine) bakunze gukaraba intoki neza.
Fata ikiganza cyawe nibura amasegonda 20.
Gusiga bituma mikorobe ziva ku ruhu, kandi uko ugenda usukura intoki zawe, ni na ko mikorobe nyinshi zivaho.
Ujye usukura intoki neza mu mazi arimo gutemba.
Gukaraba intoki mu mazi ahagaze bishobora gutuma wongera kwandura.
Ujye wisiga intoki z'umuntu ukoresheje agatambaro gashya cyangwa uzireke zimere.
Ibiganza byumye kandi byumye biranduzwa n'umuyaga, akenshi abantu birengagiza ahantu nko ku kiganza, ku ntoki, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'amano.
Inzara z'ibihangano n'amabara y'ibirenge yasakaye bishobora kuba birimo mikorobe nyinshi.
Akenshi, gukoresha umuti wo kwisiga mu ntoki ni ingirakamaro mu kwirinda ko uruhu rw'intoki rukonja, kuko bishobora kwangiza uruhu no kongera ibyago byo kwandura.
Niba amazi meza n'isabune bitaraboneka, hari uburyo bwinshi butari buhenze bwo gukaraba intoki: kuvoma amazi mu kabati karimo amazi cyangwa mu kabati k'ibyatsi karimo ibyuho, no (cyangwa) gukoresha imyanda niba ari ngombwa, nk'uko bigenda mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu duce dufite amazi make (urugero, mu mashuri cyangwa mu byaro mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari ibisubizo byo kugabanya amazi, nk'imashini z'amaguru n'izindi nzira zidakora.
Karanka ifite ikirenge cy'amaguru  ni uburyo bworoshye, bugizwe n'igikoresho gihanitse ku mugozi n'inkokora y'amaguru, ugomba gukubita kugira ngo amazi asendere ku maboko; ukoresheje isabune.
Gukaraba intoki neza  ni kimwe mu bigize isuku y'intoki, ariko hari impaka zimwe na zimwe ku buryo bwiza bwo gukaraba mu bwiherero rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko udupfukamunwa tw'impapuro ari twe dufite isuku kurusha utwuma two kumesa intoki dukoreshwa n'amashanyarazi, dusanga mu bwiherero bwinshi.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, Kaminuza ya Westminster i Londres yakoze ubushakashatsi bwatangijwe n'ikoraniro ry'i Burayi rishinzwe gukora utwenda two gusukura n'utwondo tw'impapuro; iki kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi cyagereranyijwe n'urwego rw'isuku rw'utwondo tw'impapuro, utwuma two gukaraba intoki dufite umwuka ushyushye n'utwuma two gukaraba intoki dufite umwuka usanzwe.
Byagaragaye ko nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki mu gikoresho cy'ubushyuhe, umubare w'udukoko duto duto ku ntoki wiyongeraho 194%, naho ku ntoki wiyongeraho 254%.
Basanze kandi iyo umuntu amaze gukaraba no kumesa intoki mu gikoresho cy'ubushyuhe, umubare w'udukoko duto cyane ku ntoki wiyongeraho 42 ku ijana, naho ku ntoki wiyongeraho 15 ku ijana.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki n'igitambaro cy'impapuro, umubare w'udukoko muri rusange ku nkokora z'intoki ugabanukaho 76%, naho ku ntoki ugera kuri 77%. Abahanga kandi bakoze ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba abantu benshi bajya mu bwiherero no mu bidukikije bishobora kwandura buri buryo bwo kumesa.
Ikimashini cy'umwuka gikoresha amazi, cyekura umwuka ku muvuduko wa metero 180 ku isegonda (650 km/h, 400 mi/h), gishobora guhosha mikorobe mu ntoki no mu cyumba cyacyo, kandi gishobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'ubwiherero mu birometero bibiri.
Gukoresha imashini zimesa intoki z'umwuka ushyushye bituma mikorobi zikwirakwira mu ntera ya metero 0.25 uvuye ku mashini zimesa intoki.
Mu mwaka wa 2005, ikigo TÜV Produkt und Umwelt cyakoze ubushakashatsi ku buryo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
Hari impinduka zikurikira mu mubare w'udukoko dutera indwara bitewe n'uburyo bwo kumesa intoki:
Hari ababikora batandukanye, kandi ibyo bikoresho bigereranywa n'ibikoresho byo gutunganya imyanda.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje udupfukamunwa twanduza indwara bishobora kuba ubundi buryo bwo gukemura ibibazo mu gihe uri mu rugendo, igihe nta isabune n'amazi bihari.
Ikimera cyo guhanagura ibicurane mu biganza kigomba kuba gifite nibura 60% bya alukoro.
Uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki bwabaye ngombwa cyane nyuma y'aho umuganga w'Umunya-Hongiriya witwa Ignaz Zemmelweis abonye ko ari bwo buryo bwiza cyane bwo kwirinda indwara mu bitaro (mu mwaka wa 1846).
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bifasha abakozi bo mu bitaro kwibuka ko bagomba gukaraba intoki mu gihe biba bibagiwe.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha ibyo bikoresho byagenewe abantu benshi bigabanya ubwandu.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi bigomba kumara nibura amasegonda 15, hakoreshejwe isabune, amazi cyangwa umutobe mwinshi wo gukaraba no gusukura buri gice cy'intoki.
Amaboko agomba gusama neza, ukamanika intoki.
Niba ufite umwanda munsi y'amano yawe, ushobora kuwukuraho ukoresheje isutiye.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi ari ku biganza, ni ngombwa ko uzisukura neza kandi ukazikorakora n'umwenda usukuye.
Nyuma yo kumesa intoki, mu gihe ufunga amazi, kandi niba ari ngombwa, mu gihe ufunguye cyangwa ufungura inzugi zose, ukoreshe agatambaro k'impapuro.
Ibi bituma udashobora kongera kwanduza intoki zawe uturutse kuri ibyo bintu.
Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu bigo by'ubuvuzi  gukuraho mikorobe ziterwa n'indwara (mikorobe) no kubuza ko zikwirakwira.
Ikinyamakuru cyitwa New England Journal of Medicine kivuga ko gukaraba intoki bikomeje kuba ibintu bidakwiriye mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, kuko abaganga benshi n'abaforomo bibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakwirakwiza mikorobe.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi bikorwa by'ibanze bishobora kugabanya ubwandu bw'amaraso buterwa no gukoresha imashini z'umuyoboro wa za kateri ku kigero cya 66%. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasohoye agatabo karimo urutonde rw'ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki n'ibindi bikorwa by'ubuvuzi.
Inyandiko y'inyigisho y'ubuvuzi y'intoki ya OMS kandi iboneka ku rubuga rwayo kandi irashobora kuganirwaho n'abaturage.
Isuzuma ryihariye ryakozwe na Whitby mu bufatanye.
Niba hakenewe kwemeza ko ibipimo byubahirije ibisabwa n'amategeko, ibipimo n'ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima isuku y'amaboko.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) rigaragaza ibihe bitanu byo gukaraba intoki:
nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso cyangwa ibiyeri,
mbere yo gukoresha umuti wica udukoko,
Iyo umuntu amaze gukora amavuriro, iyo amaze gukaraba intoki, yongeraho imiti yica mikorobe mu isabune (isabuni y'ubuvuzi cyangwa se isabune yica mikorobe) ifasha kwica za bagiteri.
Kugira ngo umuntu asukure intoki mbere yo kubagwa, bisaba ko akoresha amazi ya chlorhexidine cyangwa amazi ya iode mu gusukura intoki, agatambaro gasukura intoki nyuma yo gukaraba, isutiye yo gusukura no gukoresha ikindi gikoresho cyo gusukura munsi y'inzara.
Ibishushanyo byose bigomba gukurwaho.
Ubu buryo busaba ko ukaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, ubusanzwe mu gihe cy'iminota 2 cyangwa 6.
Si ngombwa ko usukisha ibiganza byawe igihe kirekire cyane, nk'iminota 10.
Mu gihe cyo gusukura, amazi ava mu ntoki z'imbere ntagomba gusubira ku ntoki.
Iyo bamaze gukaraba, amaboko arumishwa umwenda wanduye kandi bakambara ikanzu y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo ukureho mikorobe, ni byiza ko ukaraba intoki cyangwa ukoresha umuti wica udukoko mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Mu kurwanya indwara z'ibicurane mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu nyinshi zo gukaraba intoki zituruka ku masaha 20 y'ubwiherero, kandi ko hari inyungu nke cyane z'inyongera zagezweho iyo umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki wiyongereyeho 35%.
Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'isabune ikinga udukoko, ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune isanzwe, bituma indwara ziterwa n'indwara ziterwa n'udukoko zitandura zituruka ku biryo ziyongeraho inshuro zirenga eshatu. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'isupu ikinga udukoko, mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 kuri buri gikorwa, byagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'isupu ikinga udukoko byagabanyije ubwandu bw'udukoko ku kigero cya 26% ugereranyije n'isupu ikinga udukoko.
Ariko, isabune n'amazi biracyakora neza kurusha umuti w'intoki urimo inzoga mu kugabanya umubare w'agakoko ka 'influenza A H1N1' n'akoko ka Clostridium difficile ku biganza. Ibikorwa byo guteza imbere isuku y'intoki mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bishobora kuba bikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongera ubushobozi bwo kubona umuti w'intoki urimo inzoga, ndetse no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko no mu magambo ko bagomba gukaraba intoki.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bw'inyongera ku buryo bwiza bwo kwivuza mu bigo bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabuni byemewe ko ari uburyo buhendutse kandi bw'ingenzi bwo kongera ubuzima ndetse no kongera imirire.
Ariko kandi, kutagira amazi, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu kazi, bituma umuntu atamenya gukaraba intoki buri gihe.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro bya Afurika, si buri bwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa rusange bufite utuzu two gukarabamo intoki, nubwo hari uburyo buhendutse bwo gukarabamo intoki.
Ariko kandi, isuku nke y'amaboko ishobora guterwa n'ingeso zashinze imizi, aho guterwa n'ibura ry'amazi n'isabune.
Gutangaza no gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune bishobora guhindura imyanzuro ya politiki, kongera ubumenyi ku kamaro ko gukaraba intoki no guhindura imyitwarire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibi bikorwa bigire icyo bigeraho, ni ngombwa gukurikirana no gusuzuma ibisubizo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bushakashatsi 70 bwagaragaje ko kugira ngo abantu barusheho kugira isuku mu biganza mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make, ubugenzuzi bw'ibanze ku rwego rw'abaturage bugira ingaruka nziza, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza bufite ingaruka nke. Urugero rumwe rw'ubuvugizi ku bijyanye no gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni uburyo bw'Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Gishinzwe Abana  Three Star Approach: buvuga ko mu mashuri hakorwa ingamba zoroshye z'ubukungu zo gushishikariza abanyeshuri gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune, ndetse no kubahiriza ibindi bisabwa mu by'isuku.
Nyuma yo kubahiriza ibipimo byibanze, amashuri ashobora kuzamura urwego rwayo ruva ku nyenyeri imwe rukagera kuri eshatu.
Gushyiraho imashini zo gukaraba intoki  ni kimwe mu bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi mu bijyanye n'isuku y'intoki bigamije kugabanya uburwayi n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki (Global Hand Washing Day)  urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo kumenyesha abantu ku bijyanye n'imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Gishinzwe Abana kirimo gukaza gukoresha emoji zigaragaza gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bwakozwe bwagereranyije ingaruka zo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere n'imyaka y'ubuzima umuntu atakaza adafite ubumuga.
Ariko, ubushakashatsi bumwe bugaragaza ko gutera inkunga yo gukaraba intoki n'isabune  ari uburyo bw'ubukungu buhenze cyane ugereranyije n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu  cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo nk'ababyeyi bakiri bato cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro  byamenyekanye bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abantu babiri bashya mu bijyanye n'isuku y'intoki: Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga w'Umunya-Hongiriya wakoreraga i Vienne (Autriche), na Florence Nightingale, umuforomokazi w'Umwongereza akaba n'uwashinze uburyo bwo kwita ku barwayi muri iki gihe.
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bari bacyizera ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi zitwa miasma.
Mu myaka ya 1980, kubera ibyorezo by'indwara z'ibihaha n'indwara z'ibyorezo ziterwa no kwita ku buzima, Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'ubuvuzi cyatangiye gushishikariza abantu kugira isuku y'intoki nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda kwandura.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009 na COVID-19 mu 2020, abantu bo mu bihugu byinshi bamenye akamaro ko gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura.
Urugero, mu Budage, hafi y'aho abantu bose bakoresha imyanda mu bwiherero, mu mazu y'ibiro no ku bibuga by'indege, hari ibyapa byanditseho amagambo avuga ngo "uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki".
Amagambo "gukaraba intoki" asobanura ko umuntu adashaka kugira icyo abazwa cyangwa ngo abe ari we ugira uruhare mu kintu icyo ari cyo cyose.
Iyo mvugo yavuye muri Bibiliya, mu Ivanjiri ya Matayo: Ponsiyo Pilato yogeje amaboko igihe yafataga umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo; nyuma yaho, iyo mvugo yaje gukoreshwa cyane mu matorero amwe n'amwe yo mu Bwongereza.
Mu kinamico cya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo kwiyuhagira ikizinga cyo mu bwenge cy'umutima we wanduye, bitewe n'ibyaha yakoze kandi asunikira umugabo we kubikora.
Basanze kandi abantu bibuka cyangwa bareba ikintu kitari cyiza bakora bakunze gukaraba intoki kenshi ugereranyije n'abandi bantu, kandi ko kubikora ari ingenzi cyane.
Ikindi kandi, abantu bashoboye gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kubona ibyo babonye, ntibakunze kwifatanya mu bindi bikorwa byo "gusukura" nk'ubwitange.
Mu madini gukaraba intoki bifite intego yo kwiyeza no kugira icyo bisobanura mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo n'amazi ariko nta isabune, ni igice cy'umuhango w'idini mu madini menshi, harimo Baha'izimu, Abahindu, tevilah na netilat yadayim mu idini rya Kiyahudi, Lavabo mu Bukristo na Wudhu mu idini rya Isilamu.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abayisilamu bategeka ko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero.
Mu idini ry'abahindu, ababuda, aba sikhi n'abisilamu, gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya buri gihe ni ngombwa.
Kugenzura ibintu by'imikorere bijyanye na COVID-19
Kugenzura ibintu by'imikorere bijyanye na COVID-19 bivuga gukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga umutekano w'umurimo no kurinda ubuzima mu rwego rwo kugenzura ibyago no kurwanya coronavirus ya 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga neza ibyago mu kazi biterwa n'aho umuntu ari n'akazi akora, bishingiye ku gusuzuma ibyago, uburemere bw'icyorezo mu baturage n'ibyago by'abakozi bashobora guhura na COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA) cyavuze ko akazi gafite ibyago bike gafite guhura n'abantu benshi n'abo bakorana, kandi ko mu gihe ari ko bimeze hakenewe ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo gukaraba intoki, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'uburwayi, kubahiriza amabwiriza yo guhumeka no gukora isuku no guhumura ahantu bakorera buri munsi.
Imirimo y'ibyago biri hagati isaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera abantu badafite icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe cyangwa gikekwa, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo mu baturage cyangwa mu ngendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri iki cyiciro hashobora kuba harimo abakozi bafatanya n'abaturage, urugero nko mu mashuri, ahantu hari abaturage benshi no mu maduka manini.
Ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago kuri iryo tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, zirimo guhumeka ukoresheje imashini z'umwuka zikora neza, gukoresha udukingirizo n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku bantu bashobora guhura n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi n'abakozi b'ibiro by'abicanyi bahuye n'umuntu wemejwe ko yanduye cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura; kandi ko ibyo bishobora kwiyongera cyane iyo abo bakozi bakoze ibikorwa byo kuvura cyangwa gukusanya ibipimo ku muntu wemejwe ko yanduye cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19.
Ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago bibereye abo bakozi zirimo gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi by'umutekano, nk'ibyumba bifite umwuka uhumeka nabi, ndetse n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bibereye uwo murimo.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka zitandukanye ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaza ku kazi kubera uburwayi bwabo, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya kwandura.
Ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi bishobora guhinduka haba ku bwoko bw'ibicuruzwa bikenewe ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubigura (urugero, kugura mu bihe bidasanzwe byo gutwara cyangwa serivisi utari mu modoka).
Amaherezo, hari igihe ibicuruzwa bishobora kuzimira mu turere twazahajwe na COVID-19. Mu rwego rwo kubungabunga umutekano, ushobora gukoresha gahunda yo kwitegura no guhangana n'icyorezo.
Imigambi ikora ku bibazo by'ibyago bijyanye n'akazi gatandukanye n'inshingano, harimo isoko y'ubwandu, ibyago biboneka mu ngo no mu baturage, ndetse n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo, nk'iza bukuru cyangwa uburwayi buhoraho.
Iyo gahunda igaragaza kandi uburyo bwo kugenzura bukenewe mu guhangana n'ibibazo by'ibi byago, ndetse n'imigambi y'ibikorwa byihutirwa ku bibazo bishobora kuvuka bitewe n'icyorezo.
Gutegura no guhangana n'icyorezo bishobora gukurikizwa n'amabwiriza y'igihugu cyangwa y'intara.
Bimwe mu byo bagamije mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo ni: kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo mu bucuruzi bwabo.
Ibisubizo bigira ingaruka ku buremere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ubucuruzi buba.
Urutonde rw'ibikoresho byo kugenzura ibyago  ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu kubungabunga umutekano n'isuku ku kazi, kugirango utegure ibikoresho nk'ibyo ukurikije imikorere.
Iyo bidashoboka guca intege ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19, uburyo bw'ubwubatsi bw'ubwirinzi ni bwo bukora cyane, hakurikiraho  ingamba z'ubuyobozi, hanyuma  uburyo bwo kwirinda.
Ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ubwubatsi by'umutekano bivuga ko abakozi batandukanywa n'ahantu hateje akaga hakorerwa akazi, kandi ntibikwiye gushingira ku myitwarire y'umukozi, ibyo bikaba bishobora kuba ari byo bisubizo byiza cyane mu bukungu.
Ingamba z'ubuyobozi ni impinduka mu miyoborere y'akazi cyangwa mu mikorere, bisaba ko umukozi agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidashobora gukora neza ugereranyije n'ingamba z'ubwubatsi cyangwa z'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukemura ibibazo bimwe na bimwe.
Ubwoko bwose bw'ibikoresho byo kwirinda bikwiye gutoranywa bitewe n'akaga ku mukozi, bikagomba kuba bifite ubunini bukwiye (urugero, ibyuma byo guhumeka), bikagomba gukoreshwa igihe cyose kandi mu buryo bukwiye, bikagenzurwa buri gihe, bigakomeza kuba mu buryo bukwiriye kandi bigasimbuzwa igihe bibaye ngombwa, kandi bikagomba gukurwaho, gusukurwa no kubikwa neza cyangwa gukoreshwa neza kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA) kivuga ko akazi gafite ibyago bike gafite guhura n'abaturage n'abo bakorana ku buryo buciriritse.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kurwanya icyorezo zisabwa ku kazi kose zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, inama ku bakozi barwaye zo kuguma mu rugo, kubahiriza uburyo bwo guhumeka, harimo no gupfuka umunwa n'amaboko igihe ukoroye no kwitsamura, gutanga udupfukamunwa n'ibikoresho byo guhana imyanda, kwitegura gukora kure cyangwa mu masaha, igihe bibaye ngombwa, inama ku bakozi kwirinda gukoresha ibindi bikoresho n'ibikoresho, no gukora isuku no kwanduza imyanda ahantu bakorera buri munsi.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura vuba  ni intambwe ikomeye yo kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abasura n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitera inkunga abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe ubushyuhe, ubushyuhe no kutagira izindi bimenyetso byinshi bihagarariye mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 badafite imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti igabanya ibimenyetso, kandi bagasaba ko hashyirwaho politiki yo guhinduka ku byerekeye inyandiko z'abarwayi, bemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bita kuri umwe mu bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi bakamenyesha abakozi ibijyanye n'iyo politiki.
OSHA ivuga ko imyanya y'akazi ifite ibyago byo mu kigero cyo hagati isaba abantu guhura kenshi kandi bya hafi, ahantu hatabarirwa metero zirenga esheshatu (1,8 m) n'abantu badafite ibimenyetso cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko uwo muntu yanduye mu gace k'ubucuruzi cyangwa se kubera ko aherutse kujya mu gace karimo COVID-19.
Muri ibyo byiciro harimo abakozi bagiranye imishyikirano n'abaturage, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi, hamwe no mu maduka manini acuruza ibicuruzwa. Ingamba z'ubuyobozi ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi birimo gusaba abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza guhura imbonankubone n'abantu ku buryo bwo guhura n'abantu ku buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, gushyiraho gahunda z'akazi, guhagarika gahunda zo guhura n'abantu ku buryo budasanzwe, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'amasanduku y'ubwirinzi ya plastiki, no gushyiraho amadirishya yo gusukura abakiriya batiriwe basohoka mu modoka. Ingamba zo mu rwego rw'ubuyobozi ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi zirimo gusaba abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza imibonano y'imibonano y'abantu ku buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, gushyiraho gahunda zo guhura n'abantu ku buryo buhoraho, guhagarika gahunda zo guhura n'abantu ku buryo bwo guhura na COVID-19, gukora ibikoresho byo guhura n'abantu ku buryo bworoshye harimo n'uduporogaramu zo guhanahana amakuru n'ibizabagira ingaruka, ariko nanone dushobora gushyiraho amabwiriza ku bakozi, mu gihe cy'ikibazo, mu gihe cy'ikibazo cy'umutekano muke, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cy'akazi, mu gihe cyiciro cyiciro cy'akazi
Mu bihe bidasanzwe, abakozi bo mu itsinda ry'ibyago bashobora gukenera kwambara ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, kugira ngo abakozi n'abandi bagenzi birinde, bisaba ko umuntu arwaye ashyirwa kure y'abandi bantu, ku ntera ya metero 6, agashyirirwaho umuntu wo mu itsinda ryo mu ndege kugira ngo amwiteho, agahabwa agapfukamunwa cyangwa akasabwa gupfuka umunwa n'amazuru igihe akoroye cyangwa atutse.
Abagenzi bo mu ndege z'ubufasha bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'imashini zishobora gukoreshwa igihe begereye umushoferi urwaye cyangwa igihe bagiranye isano n'amazi cyangwa ahantu hashobora kwandura, kandi wenda n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umuntu ku giti cye, niba umurwayi afite umuriro, ukoroye kenshi cyangwa afite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Mu ngendo z'ubwikorezi, harimo n'amato y'ingendo z'ubwato n'andi mato atwara abagenzi, ingamba z'umutekano zirimo gusubika urugendo mu gihe urwaye, kwicungira mu kato no guhita ubwira ikigo nderabuzima cyo ku bwato niba hari umuntu ufite ubushyuhe cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso.
Mu buryo bwiza, isuzuma ry'ubuzima ryagombye kuba mu cyumba cy'umuntu nk'uwo. Mu gihe cy'amashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC itera inkunga yo gufunga by'igihe gito kugira ngo hasukurwe cyangwa hakurwemo udukoko duto duto, niba umuntu wanduye yari mu ishuri, hatitawe ku kuba indwara yiganje mu baturage.
Iyo ubwandu buri ku kigero cyo hasi cyangwa hagati mu baturage, hari uburyo bwo kwirinda abantu, urugero nko guhagarika kujya mu materaniro, mu materaniro no mu bindi bikorwa by'abantu benshi, nko gukora siporo cyangwa kuririmba, kurya mu kabari, kureka abantu bakajya ku meza, kugabanya igihe cyo kuhagera no kuhaguma, kugabanya abantu batajya mu bigo by'ubuzima, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye abana bafite ibimenyetso bya grippe baba.
Iyo ubwandu bwogeye cyane mu baturage, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda abantu, hashobora gushyirwaho ingamba zo kutajya ku ishuri igihe kirekire. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora imirimo yabo ya buri munsi, ibyago by'ubuzima bwihuse bifatwa nk'ibiri hasi, nk'uko CDC ibivuga.
Abashinzwe umutekano bagomba guhura n'abantu bagaragaweho cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, barasabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ayo abaganga batanga ubutabazi bw'ubutabazi, harimo no gukoresha ibikoresho bikwiye byo kwirinda.
Iyo habayeho guhura mu gihe cyo gufatwa, abakozi bagomba gusukura no kwanduza udupfunyika tw'imyenda n'imyambaro yabo mbere yo kongera kuyikoresha bakoresheje umwuka usukura mu rugo cyangwa binyuze mu kuyitsukamo, kubahiriza amabwiriza y'imikorere yo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu yakoresheje, ndetse no gukoresha no kumesa imyenda.
OSHA ivuga ko hari ibyiciro by'abakozi bo mu bigo by'ubuzima n'abakora mu bigo by'ubupfu bafite ibyago byinshi cyangwa byinshi.
Imirimo y'ibanze irimo abakozi b'ubuvuzi, abashinzwe ubufasha, abakozi ba laboratwari n'abakora mu modoka zitwara abafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kuyandura.
Bashobora kwandura cyane iyo bakoze ibikorwa birimo gukora umwuka wa aérosol cyangwa bakorakoranya ibipimo ku bantu bagaragaweho cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Mu bikorwa biherekezwa no kuvamo aérosol harimo gupima, ibikorwa biteza inkorora, bronchoscopie, bimwe mu bikorwa byo kuvura amenyo no gusuzuma cyangwa gufata ibipimo hakoreshejwe uburyo bw'ubuvuzi.
Abakozi ba marembo bafite ibyago byinshi ni abakora ku mirambo y'abantu bafite uburwayi bwemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 igihe bapfaga; niba abo bakozi bakora autopsie, bahinduka ibyago byinshi. Ibindi bikoresho by'ubwubatsi by'umutekano ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi birimo gukoresha ibyumba byigenga ku barwayi bafite uburwayi bwemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, harimo no gukora imikorere ijyanye no gukora aérosol.
Mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuzima no mu bigo by'abicanyi, gukoresha umwuka uhumeka ufite umuvuduko muke cyane bishobora kuba ingamba nziza.
Ibipimo bigomba gufatwa hakurikijwe ingamba zo kwirinda zatanzwe ku rwego rwa 3 rw'umutekano.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritegeka ko abarwayi baza mu bitaro bashyirwa mu byumba by'indembe bishingiye ku kuba bakekwaho COVID-19. Usibye ibindi bintu byo kwirinda, OSHA irasaba ko abakozi bakorana n'abarwayi bagaragaye ko barwaye cyangwa bakekwaho SARS-CoV-2 no gukora ibikorwa birimo gufungura umwuka bakoresha udupira two guhumeka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka byemewe na NIOSH bifite isuku ya N95 cyangwa iyirenze bigomba gukoreshwa mu buryo bw'inyandiko y'igitabo cy'ubuvuzi, aho hagaragazwa ibisabwa mu guhitamo ibikoresho no kugenzura.
Ubundi bwoko bw'imashini zo guhumeka zishobora kurinda no guhumuriza abakozi neza. OMS ntidusaba ko umuntu yambara imyenda y'ubwirinzi kuko COVID-19  yandura binyuze mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, aho kuba binyuze mu mazi.
OMS itera inkunga abakozi bakora ibizamini byo kwa muganga gukoresha udupfukamunwa gusa.
Abantu bakusanya ibipimo by'imyuka y'ubuhumekero ku barwayi bafite COVID-19 cyangwa abanduye iyo ndwara badafite uburyo bwo kuvura butuma habaho imyuka ituruka mu kirere, OMS ibasaba kwambara agapfukamunwa, indorerwamo cyangwa udukingirizo tw'amaso, imyenda n'utugati.
Mu gihe ukora imibonano mpuzabitsina irimo umwuka wa aérosol, aho kwambara agapfukamunwa ko kubaga, jya wambara agapfukamunwa ka N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ku isi hose nta bikoresho bihagije byo kwirinda umuntu afite, OMS irasaba ko hakorwa ibishoboka byose kugira ngo bikurweho hakoreshejwe ubuvuzi bw'uruhande, inzitizi z'umubiri nk'amadirishya agaragara neza, abantu bareba umurwayi wa COVID-19 gusa, abantu bareba abamufasha, gukoresha gusa ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu akeneye, gukoresha cyane cyane ibyuma by'ubuvuzi by'ubwoko bumwe, kugenzura no guhuza uruziga rw'ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu, no kutabika udupfukamunwa ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso.
