Icyorezo cya COVID-19  ni ikintu cyerekana neza isano abantu bafite ku isi hose n'inshingano dufitanye.
Nta kibazo nk'iki twigeze duhura na cyo, ariko tuzi ko kugira ngo ibyo dukora bigire icyo bigeraho, bisaba ko tugira impuhwe, ubufatanye n'iterambere mu baturage bo ku isi hose, ibyo bikaba ari byo bituma tugira umuryango nk'uyu.
Twabonye imishyikirano y'ubusabane n'urukundo hagati y'abo dukorana bose, byerekanwa n'ubutumwa bwo kuri interineti, guhamagara no kuganira - icyemezo cyiza cy'uko, ku bw'amahirwe, dufite abantu batangaje dukorana.
Mfite ishema n'ishema ryinshi kuba mvuga ko muri bagenzi banjye.
Mu cyumweru gishize, namenye ko umurimo wacu wishimirwa cyane.
Nibukijwe akamaro ko kugira Wikipedia muri iki gihe, n'akamaro ko kugira buri muntu wese ufite uburyo bwo gukoresha iyi soko y'ingenzi kuri interineti.
Kandi ibyo bishoboka kubera akazi mukora, yaba mu gutuma imbuga zikora, kwishyura abakozi bacu cyangwa kurinda umutekano w'abaturage.
Isi ikeneye amakuru ari muri Wikipedia, kandi uyu munsi ni ngombwa kurusha mbere hose.
Mu bihe nk'ibi, kugira ngo tugire icyo tugeraho ku isi, si ibyo dukora gusa bifite akamaro, ahubwo ni n'uburyo tubikora.
Kubera akamaro k'iki gikorwa n'uruhare rwanyu muri iki gikorwa, tugiye guhindura byinshi mu mikorere yacu duhereye mu cyumweru gitaha.
Ivugurura mu mikorere n'imikorere y'akazi kacu
Nkuko Robin yabivuze mbere, itsinda c-team ryahuye ejo nimugoroba kugira ngo rigire icyo rivuga ku buryo bwacu n'ingengabihe y'iminsi n'amezi biri imbere.
Mu kiganiro twagiranye, twasuzumye ibitekerezo byacu ku buryo bwiza bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubu ndetse n'uburyo bwiza bwo gutuma umuryango wacu ubasha guhangana n'iki gihe.
Abenshi muri twe twifuzaga kugabanya imihangayiko no gushyigikira umurimo wacu w'igihe kirekire.
Niba mushaka gusubira inyuma, nimubikore.
Ku bakozi bose, ba rwiyemezamirimo n'abakozi badafite akazi:
Dutegereje ko tuzakora amasaha agera kuri 4 ku munsi cyangwa 20 mu cyumweru kugeza ubwo tuzaba twumvise andi mabwiriza.
Ntabwo dutangaza iminsi y'ikiruhuko: niba ushobora gukora amasaha menshi mu buryo busanzwe, biremewe ku bw'intego z'umushinga wacu.
