Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzymes ifatanye n'urusobe rw'inyuma (urw'ingirabuzimafatizo) rw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ihangana n'ibikorwa bya enzyme ihindura angiotensin (ACE) ihuje na yo, igabanya angiotensin-II kandi igabanya Ang (1-7), bigatuma iba umuti wizewe wo kuvura indwara z'umutima. AC2 kandi ikora nk'ahantu ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe.
Ubwoko bwa muntu bwa enzyme akenshi buvugwa nka hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2  ni ferment y'icyuma irimo zinc, iri ku gice cy'imbere mu mubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 irimo N-impera ya peptidase domain M2 na C-impera y'umuvuduko wa transport ya collectrin ya amino acide y'impyiko.
ACE2 ni protein y'uruhu imwe yo mu bwoko bwa I, ingirabuzima fatizo zayo z'imikorere y'imyakura igera ku bice by'umubiri.
Uruhare rwa ACE2 rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ruva ku rukingo rw'uruhu rw'umubiri n'indi poroteyine yitwa sheddaze, maze uru rukingo ruvamo uruvange rw'indwara rukinjira mu maraso, amaherezo rukagenda mu cyuma.
ACE2 iri mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi z'ibihaha z'ubwoko bwa II, za enterocyte z'igifu gike, ingirabuzimafatizo z'imitsi n'imitsi n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'umusatsi n'iz'imisatsi y'ingingo nyinshi.
Bio synthesis ya ACE2 iRNA kandi iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa striatum, hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa brain stem.
Uruhare rw'ingenzi rwa ACE2 ni ugukora nk'uburemere bw'inguzanyo ya ACE.
ACE igabanya hormone angiotensin I mu angiotensin II ifasha mu kuvura imitsi.
ACE2, mu cyiciro cyayo, itandukanya amino acide ya carboxyl ya nyuma ya phenylalanine na angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayihindura angiotensin ya vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi gusenya izindi peptides nyinshi zirimo [des-Arg9] -bradikinin, apeline, neurotensin, dinorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi itegeka ubwikorezi bwa membrane bw'umuyoboro wa SLC6A19 w'umunyamideli udafite aho uhuriye na amino acides kandi iriho mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Kubera ko ACE2 ari poroteyine itera uturemangingo, ni yo nzira y'ibanze yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
Mu buryo bwimbitse, guhuza poroteyine S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 n'uruziga rw'umusemburo wa ACE2 ku gice cy'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bituma virusi n'iyo poroteyine bihinduka utundi duce tw'umubiri.
Iyi nzira yo kwinjira kandi isaba ko poroteyine S ibanza guterwa na serine protease itwara TMPRSS2, kubuza ubu biri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'umuti ushobora kuvura. Ibi byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Nyamara, inzego nyinshi z'ubuvuzi n'izigenga zisaba gukomeza gukoresha imiti isanzwe ya APF na BRAS.
Dukurikije isuzuma ryihariye n'isesengura ryakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, koresha inhibitors za APF byari bifitanye isano no kugabanya cyane ibyago byo kurwara amapfupfa ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'abatarwaye.
Byongeye kandi, ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane byaragabanutse no ku barwayi bahawe imiti igabanya umuvuduko w'amaraso (APF) bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara ibicurane by'amaraso, cyane cyane abarwayi bafite indwara y'igicuri n'umutima udakora neza.
Gukoresha abacunga APF nabyo byahujwe no kugabanya impfu ziterwa na pneumonie, nubwo ibisubizo byari bidafite icyizere nk'iby'abarwayi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara pneumonie.
Umuntu uvura ACE2 (rhACE2) byitezwe ko ari ikintu gishya mu kuvura uburwayi bukabije bw'ibihaha kandi bisa n'aho byongera umuvuduko w'amaraso mu bihaha no kongera umwuka wa ogisijeni mu ngurube zifite indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye inkeke iterwa na lipopolysaccharides.
Igihe cy'igice cy'igihe cyo gukuraho rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha agera kuri 10 kandi gutangira gukora ni iminota 30, uretse igihe cy'amasaha 24.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku bantu badahanganira inhibitors za classique za système renin-angiotensin (inhibitors za RAS) cyangwa indwara ziterwa no kuzamuka kwa angiotensin II. RhACE2 yashyizwe mu bikorwa yagenzuwe mu igerageza mu buvuzi mu kuvura indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero.
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za telefoni zigenewe gufasha mu iperereza ry'icyorezo mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, ni ukuvuga mu kumenya abantu (abari bahuye) bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'umuntu wanduye.
Mu turere tumwe na tumwe, hakozwe cyangwa hatangwa porogaramu nyinshi zishimangiwe n'ubutegetsi.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo gukurikirana abakiriya bwakozwe.
Ibi byateje impaka ku bibazo by'ibanga, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'izo gahunda zishingiye ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Amahitamo yoroshye muri ibi harimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugirango umenye aho umukoresha ageze kuri terefone zigendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple batangaje ko bagiye gufatanya imbaraga zabo mu guhuza imikorere yo gushyigikira izo porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu z'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta ifatanyije na Alipay bashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba baraganiriye n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore hari porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Muri iki gihe, muri Macedonia ya Ruguru, hashyizweho porogaramu ya StopKorona! ikoresha Bluetooth, ifasha gukurikirana abantu bashobora kwandura kandi ikanafasha mu guhita bavugana n'inzego z'ubuzima.
Porogaramu yakozwe ku bufatanye bwa Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwiyandikisha muri Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abakoraho iri mu byiciro bya nyuma by'iterambere kandi ko izaba iboneka mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'izo ziteganyijwe gutangira muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa (StopCovid).
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande birimo gusuzuma uburyo bwo gukoresha porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether yo muri Singapuru na BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite umugambi wo gukoresha porogaramu ifite imiterere y'akarere, igamije  kugenzura ko abarwayi bafite COVID-19 baba i Moscou batava mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu mu by'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, agaragaza ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere y'ikoranabuhanga, harimo gukora nabi no kudakora neza mu gihe ikoranabuhanga rikoreshwa n'abantu bake.
Apple yagabanyije urutonde rw'ibigo bishobora gutanga porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus muri App Store, ikoresha gusa "amashyirahamwe yemewe" cyangwa andi mashyirahamwe yizewe.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abari mu bukangurambaga bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka z'ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi ku bantu benshi binyuze muri porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus; by'umwihariko, ikibazo cyavutse cy'uko ibikorwa remezo byo kugenzura byashyizweho mu kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus bizasenyuka igihe akaga kazaba kavuyeho.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura bugabanuka.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani asaba imishinga ya leta:
Igenzura rigomba kuba ari ryemewe n'amategeko, rikenewe kandi rifite uburemere buhagije;
kwagura imikorere ya monitor na observation bigomba kujyanirana n 'ibyifuzo byo kugabanya igihe byumvikanyweho;
gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba mu rwego rwo kurwanya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19;
umutekano n'ubwisungane mu gutanga amakuru bigomba kurindwa kandi hagomba gutangwa ibimenyetso by'uko birindwa;
kugenzura mu buryo bwa digitale bigomba guca burundu ihohoterwa n ' ivangura rikomeye;
itumanaho iryo ari ryo ryose n 'abantu batatu rigomba kuba ryaragenwe ku rwego rw ' amategeko;
kurinda abaturage ibikorwa bibi, ndetse n'uburenganzira bwo kugira icyo bakora ku bikorwa bibi bigomba kubahirizwa;
Hakwiye "gufatanya" by'umwihariko "abakozi bose b'inzego z'ibanze" harimo impuguke mu by'ubuzima n'abahagarariye amatsinda akandamijwe.
Google na Apple batanze gahunda yabo ihuriweho yo gukemura ikibazo cy'ubugenzuzi buhoraho, aho gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana muri sisitemu z'imikorere y'ibikoresho byabo igihe cyose biba bitakiri ngombwa.
Mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe, aho gukoresha porogaramu hakoreshwa igenzura ry'ahantu hifashishijwe urusobe, ibyo bikaba bituma bidasaba ko hakoreshwa porogaramu kandi bikaba byoroshye kwirinda gukurikiranwa.
Muri Isirayeli, gukurikirana mu muyoboro byemewe.
Ibisubizo by'imbuga bigira ubushobozi bwo kubona amakuru y'aho umuntu ari, nabyo bifite ibibazo bikomeye by'ibanga.
Ariko, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru zigomba kubona amakuru yihariye yerekeye aho umuntu ari; hari sisitemu zimwe na zimwe zashyizweho zirinze kubeshya zikoresha seriveri nkuru gusa kugirango zitere inkunga (reba igice gikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo gukurikirana abakora imibonano mpuzabitsina, ariko nta porogaramu ikoreshwa.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana mu bitangazamakuru bitandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya mobile n'amakarita, hanyuma ayashyira hamwe kugira ngo ashobore gutanga amakuru mu buryo bw'ubutumwa bugufi bwohererejwe abantu bashobora kwandura.
Leta ntiyakoresheje gusa aya makuru kugira ngo iburire abaturage ku bantu bashobora kuba baragiranye ubwumvikane n'abantu banduye, ahubwo kandi yashyize ahagaragara amakuru y'aho umuntu ari, ibyo bikaba byashobotse kubera impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko yo kurinda amakuru zakozwe nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS muri icyo gihugu.
Amakuru nk'ayo ashobora kuboneka binyuze mu porogaramu nyinshi na website.Ibihugu birimo n'Ubudage birimo gusuzuma uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bw'ibanze n'ubw'ibanga.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru arambuye ntaragaragazwa.
Kurikirana abakora amakuru mu buryo bw'ibanga  ni igitekerezo cyemewe, inyandiko nyinshi z'ubushakashatsi kuri yo zitangira nibura mu 2013.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni umusaruro w'imihati yo guhuza, ikubiyemo uburyo bwigenga n'ubw'ibanze, kandi ntabwo ari protocole imwe. Ibiteganywa mu buryo butari ubw'ibanze birimo guhuza ibidukikije, bikomeza ibanga (DP-PPT/DP-3T), imibare y'igihe gito (TCN, fka Contact EventNumbers, CEN), protocols zo gutanga ibanga, uburyo bwo gukurikirana abakora kuri telefoni zigendanwa (PACT), n'ibindi.
Izi protocole zifite inshingano zo kureba ko amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye atajya ava ku gikoresho, ahubwo ko ibyo ahuza byose biba kuri icyo gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga, MIT Media Lab rirakora SafePaths, urubuga rufasha abantu kubungabunga ubuzima bwabo bwite mu gihe bakusanya no gukoresha amakuru y'aho bari cyangwa aho banyura kugira ngo bakurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Imirimo y'urubuga ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwatanzwe mu nyandiko Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic (Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic), yasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Ikindi gikorwa gisa ni urubuga rwa SafeTrace rwakozwe na Enigma MPC, isosiyete ihanga ikoranabuhanga ryo gucunga ubuzima bwite, na yo yari yashinzwe na MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga rikomeye ry'ibyuma, rituma abakoresha bashobora gusangira amakuru y'aho bari n'ubuzima bwabo n'abandi bakoresha n'abayobozi, nta guhungabanya ibanga ry'ayo makuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, amatsinda asangiye uburyo bumwe kandi akoresha protocol zisa, yashyizeho ihuriro mpuzamahanga rya TCN, rigamije  kugabanya ibice no gutanga ubufatanye ku isi hose bwa porogaramu zo gukurikirana no kumenyesha, ari nabyo bituma zikoreshwa cyane.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapuru yatangaje ko ifunguye kode y'ibanze ya BlueTrace ikoreshwa mu gukora porogaramu yayo yemewe.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenzura imikorere ya porogaramu za Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abakorana na bo, bavuga ko bizatuma ubuzima bwite bw'abantu bubaho, kandi bishingiye ku guhuza ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy n'ibanga ry'ibanga.
Basohoye kandi ibipimo by'ikoranabuhanga rikoreshwa mu mikorere y'urwo rwego.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, ubu buryo bugomba gushyirwa mu byiciro bitatu:
gushyiraho ibikoresho bituma leta zubaka porogaramu zemewe zo gukurikirana aho abaturage banduye coronavirus bagenda ariko zigakomeza ibanga ry'amakuru
Mu guhuza iyi mikorere mu buryo butaziguye muri iOS na Android, Google na Apple bateganya gukemura ibibazo by'ubugenzuzi buhoraho, babanje gushyiraho uburyo binyuze mu kuvugurura sisitemu y'imikorere, hanyuma bakabukura muri ubwo buryo nyuma yo gutakaza iterabwoba.
Gushyira umuti mu mwanya (zwi no ku izina rya re-profiling, re-direction, change of purpose or therapeutic re-direction of drugs)  ni ugushyira umuti mu mwanya wemewe mu rwego rwo kuvura indwara cyangwa uburwayi butandukanye n'ubwari buteganyijwe mu gihe cyo kuwukora.
Ni kimwe mu bice by'ubushakashatsi ubu bikoreshwa mu gukora imiti idahungabanya indwara ya COVID-19.
Mu bindi bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi harimo gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 no guterwa plasma y'umuntu. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zishobora gukoreshwa n'imiti, buri imwe ifite ibice byinshi by'uruhu.
Gusuzuma ibi bice by'ubufatanye ni ishingiro ryiza ryo gukora umuti wa virusi ufite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya poroteyine za COVID-19.
Poroteyine z'ingenzi cyane zigamije SARS-CoV-2 ni papaine-like protease, RNA-dependent RNA-polymerase, heliqa, protein S na ADF-ribophosphatase.
