Mu mwaka wa 2020, icyorezo gikomeye cy'iyi ndwara cyakwirakwiriye ku isi hose, bituma hashyirwaho amafaranga menshi mu gukora urukingo no gukora ubushakashatsi kuri urwo rukingo.
