Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi ba CEPI batangaje ko mu ntangiriro za 2020, hari porogaramu 10 zitandukanye z'ikoranabuhanga zari mu bikorwa byo gukora ubushakashatsi no gukora urukingo rukora neza rwa COVID-19.
Bimwe mu ntego z'ingenzi z'urubuga, zashyizwe mu bushakashatsi bw'umutekano w'icyiciro cya mbere:
nucleic acid (DNA na RNA) (umushakashatsi w'icyiciro cya mbere n'umuti w'urukingo: Moderna, iRNA-1273)
virusi (umushinga w'icyiciro cya mbere n'umuti w'urukingo: CanSino Biologics, virusi ya adenovirus y'ubwoko bwa 5)
Nk'uko abahanga muri CEPI babivuze muri Mata, inkingo 115 zishobora gukorwa ziri mu byiciro bya mbere by'iterambere, 78 muri zo zikoreshwa mu mishinga yemewe (79, nk'uko ikigo Milken kibitangaza); kandi hari izindi nkingo 37 z'abakandida zatangajwe ariko nta makuru menshi azwi (bivugwa ko ziri mu byiciro byo gutegurwa cyangwa gutunganywa).
Mu byiciro I-II, igeragezwa ryambere ry'umutekano n'ubudahangarwa, ubusanzwe, ryakorewe mu buryo butunguranye, rigenzurwa na placebo kandi mu bice byinshi, hamwe no kugena ibipimo byuzuye kandi byikora.
Icyiciro cya III cy'igerageza akenshi kirimo abenshi, harimo n'itsinda ry'abashinzwe kugenzura; muri iki cyiciro, imiti igeragezwa ku bushobozi bwayo mu kwirinda indwara kandi icyarimwe hakagenzurwa ingaruka mbi ku bipimo byiza.
