Gukoresha iki kiyobyabwenge ntibyigeze bigeragezwa mu buvuzi, kuko bigomba gukorwa kugira ngo byemezwe ko ari ubuvuzi bufite ubuziranenge kandi bukora neza.
Muri Gashyantare 2020, u Bushinwa bwatangije porogaramu ya telefoni igamije kurwanya icyorezo.
Kugira ngo winjiremo, abakoresha bagomba kwandika izina ryabo n'umubare w'irangamimerere.
Porogaramu ishobora kumenya abari bafitanye isano  hakoreshejwe amakuru y'ibanze, bityo ikamenya ibyago byo kwandura.
Buri mukoresha ashobora kandi kureba uko abandi bakoresha batatu bameze.
Iyo hari ibyago by'ubwandu byamenyekanye, iyo porogaramu ntiyiyamamaza gusa ahubwo kandi igatuma inzego z'ubuzima zo mu karere zibimenyeshwa. Isesengura ry'amakuru menshi yakusanyijwe kuri telefoni zigendanwa, ikoranabuhanga ryo kumenya isura, gukurikirana telefoni zigendanwa n'ubwenge bw'abantu  ibikoresho nk'ibyo bikoreshwa mu gukurikirana abantu banduye n'abo bahuye na bo muri Koreya y'Epfo, Taiwan na Singapuru.
