Abantu bashobora guhangayikishwa n'igenzurwa ry'imiti, kugabanya ingendo, ingaruka z'imiti cyangwa gutinya ubwandu ubwabwo.
BBC ivuga ko Rory O'Connor yagize ati "Kwitarura abantu, kwigunga, guhangayikira ubuzima, guhangayika no guhungabana mu bukungu, ni ibintu byiza cyane ku buzima bw'abantu n'ubuzima bwabo bwo mu mutwe".
Iyi ndwara ishobora kuba yoroshye, nta bimenyetso byinshi cyangwa se nta bimenyetso na bimwe, nk'izindi ndwara z'ubuhumekero bwo hejuru, nk'ibicurane.
Abarwayi bafite indwara yoroheje, ubusanzwe bakira mu byumweru bibiri, mu gihe abarwayi bafite indwara ikomeye cyangwa ikomeye bashobora gukenera hagati y'ibyumweru bitatu na bitandatu.
Abagore batwite bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura COVID-19 ikomeye bitewe n'amakuru ku zindi virusi zisa na SARS na MERS, nubwo nta makuru nk'ayo ariho kuri COVID-19. Mu bantu bamwe na bamwe, COVID-19 ishobora kugira ingaruka ku bihaha kandi igateza amapfa nk'indwara ikomeye.
Mu bantu barwaye COVID-19 mu buryo bukomeye cyane, ishobora guhita ikura ikaba indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba (ARDS), igatuma umuntu aba afite ibibazo byo guhumeka nabi, guhungabana mu bwonko cyangwa se kugira ibibazo by'ingingo nyinshi.
Mu bibazo bya COVID-19 harimo sepsis, kuvura mu mubiri, ibibazo by'umutima, impyiko n'umwijima.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe by'imikorere y'amaraso, cyane cyane igihe cy'imikorere ya prothrombin, byavuzwe kuri 6% by'abarwayi bari mu bitaro bafite COVID-19, mu gihe ibibazo by'imikorere y'impyiko bigaragara kuri 4% by'aba bari muri iryo tsinda.
Hafi 2030% by'abarwayi bafite COVID-19 bafite ibipimo by'umusemburo w'umwijima (transaminases) byiyongereye.
Nk'uko raporo yabigaragaje, igihe cy'umunsi umwe hagati yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso no gupfa cyari iminsi icumi, kandi muri iyo minsi itanu abarwayi bari mu bitaro.
Ariko kandi, igihe cy'impunzi hagati yo kujya mu bitaro no gupfa mu barwayi bahinduriwe mu byumba by'indembe cyari iminsi irindwi.
Ubushakashatsi ku barwaye indwara mu bihe bya mbere, bwagaragaje ko kuva ibimenyetso bya mbere byatangira kugaragara kugeza ku munsi w'urupfu, byamaze iminsi 14, mu gihe cy'iminsi itandatu kugeza kuri 41.
Nk'uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa (NHC) bubigaragaza, igipimo cy'urupfu mu bagabo ni 2.8% naho mu bagore ni  1.7%.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bw'ibihaha nyuma y'urupfu, bugaragaza ko hari ibyangiritse mu bice by'ibihaha byombi.
Mu bice by'ubuhumekero, habayeho impinduka z'imiterere y'imiterere y'umubiri.
Isura y'ibihaha byasaga n'iby'uburwayi bukomeye bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (SDR).
Mu bantu 11,8% bapfuye, bashyizwe ahagaragara na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa, ibibazo by'umutima byari byatewe n'umubare munini wa troponin cyangwa umutima uhagaze.
Dukurikije amakuru yatanzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika muri Werurwe, 89% by'abarwayi bari mu bitaro bari bafite ibibazo by'ubuzima. Kubona ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi no kuba mu karere hari ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho bishobora no kugira ingaruka ku bipfa.
Ibipimo by'urupfu bitewe n'uburwayi bitandukanye bitewe n'uko mu turere hatandukanye, ndetse n'ibibazo by'uburyo.
Kubara neza ku bantu barwaye indwara zidakomeye bishobora gutuma umubare w'abapfa wiyongera.
Nyamara, kuba abantu bapfa bazize indwara z'uburwayi, bishobora kuba bigaragaza ko umubare w'abapfa ubu utagishyize mu gaciro.
Abanywa itabi bari bafite ibyago byo kugira ibimenyetso bikomeye bya COVID-19 bikubye inshuro 1.4 ugereranyije n'abatanywa itabi, kandi bari bafite ibyago bikubye inshuro 2.4 byo gukenera ubuvuzi bw'indembe cyangwa gupfa ugereranyije n'abatanywa itabi. Hari impungenge z'ingaruka z'iyo ndwara mu gihe kirekire.
Ubuyobozi bw'ibitaro byo muri Hong Kong bwabonye ko hari abarwayi bakize iyo ndwara bari bafite ibihaha byagabanutseho 20 kugeza kuri 30 ku ijana, kandi ko ibipimo byafashwe byagaragaje ko bari bafite ubumuga.
Nyuma yo gukira, bishobora no gutuma umuntu agira indwara y'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, ntibyari bizwi niba abarwayi bakize virusi bagira ubudahangarwa buhoraho kuri yo.
Ukurikije uko izindi koronavirusi zagiye ziterwa, birashoboka ariko kandi hari n'abagiye bageragezwa bagasanga COVID-19 yarakize ariko bakongera bagasanga nta virusi ya coronavirusi bafite.
Bivugwa ko muri izo ndwara, indwara y'ibicurane yariyongereye cyane, aho kongera kwandura.
Bivugwa ko iyi virusi ari iy'ibanze, ikomoka ku nyamaswa kandi ko ari indwara y'ubwandu.
Inkomoko nyayo ya virusi ntizwi, ariko kugeza mu Ukuboza 2019, ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu ryari hafi cyane bitewe no kwanduzanya kw'umuntu n'undi.
Ubushakashatsi ku bantu 41 ba mbere banduye COVID-19, bwashyizwe ahagaragara muri Mutarama 2020 mu kinyamakuru The Lancet, buvuga ko tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 ari bwo bwa mbere umuntu yabonetse.
Nk'uko amakuru yemewe yashyizwe ahagaragara na OMS abivuga, uwo munsi ni  8 Ukuboza 2019.
Kugira ngo umubare w'abapfa ugereranywe, hakoreshwa uburyo bwinshi.
Ibipimo byose bigenda bitandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe cy'ikwirakwira ry'indwara, biganirwaho kandi n'umubare w'abantu bapimwa, ireme ry'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kwivuza bwakoreshejwe, igihe cy'indwara n'ibipimo by'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange.
Mu mpera za 2019, OMS yahaye iki cyorezo kode z'ubutabazi bwa ICD-10: U07.1  ku bantu bapfuye bazize indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 na U07.2  ku bantu bapfuye bazize COVID-19 ariko nta gihamya cy'uko banduye SARS-CoV-2.
Nk'uko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins ibigaragaza, ku itariki ya 17 Mata 2020, umubare w'abamaze guhitanwa n'iki cyorezo ku isi yose ni 6,9% (153 822/2 240 191).
Iyi mibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere. Ubundi buryo bumwe ni ukumenya umubare w'abapfa kubera indwara (CFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abarwayi basanzwemo indwara bapfuye kubera iyo ndwara, ndetse no kumenya umubare w'abapfa kubera ubwandu bwanduye (IFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abarwayi banduye (bose basanzwemo indwara n'abatarasanzwemo) bapfuye kubera iyo ndwara.
Aya makuru ntabwo afitanye isano n'igihe runaka kandi agaragaza imibare y'igice runaka cy'abaturage kuva igihe cyo kwandura kugeza igihe indwara irangiriye.
Nubwo abanduye bose batagira abanduye, iyo abanduye bafite abanduye, ushobora kumenya umubare w'abanduye.
Mu gihugu cy'Ubutaliyani, mu gace k'icyorezo, ahitwa Castellone d'Adda, umudugudu muto utuwe n'abaturage 4.600, abantu 80 (1.7%) ntibakiriho.
Mu mujyi wa Gangelt, iyi ndwara yakwirakwiriye mu gihe cy'ibirori bya Carnival mu rubyiruko, bituma hapfa abantu bake cyane, kandi si abantu bose bapfuye bazize COVID-19 bashoboraga kugenzurwa nk'abapfuye.
Byongeye kandi, ubuvuzi bw'u Budage ntibwari buremerewe cyane.
Mu Buholandi, 3% by'abaturage bashobora kuba bafite abanduye, ukurikije ibipimo by'amaraso yatanzwe.
COVID-19  ni yo mpamvu yemewe y'abantu 69 bapfuye (0,004% by'abaturage).
Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'imfu zitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani bugaragaza ko abagabo ari bo bapfa cyane.
Itsinda ry'abari mu kaga gakomeye  ni abagabo barengeje imyaka 50 y'amavuko; itandukaniro mu bipimo hagati y'abagabo n'abagore rigabanuka gusa kuva ku myaka 90 y'amavuko.
Mu Bushinwa, igipimo cy'urupfu cyari 2.8% ku bagabo na 1.7% ku bagore.
Impamvu nyayo y'uko batandukana ntizwi, ariko bishobora kuba biterwa n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima cyangwa imyitwarire.
Itandukaniro ry'ubushobozi bw'umubiri hagati y'ibitsina, kuba abagore batanywa itabi cyane, indwara ziterwa n'isukari mu bagabo (urugero: umuvuduko w'amaraso ukabije mu bagabo bakiri bato ugereranyije n'abagore) bishobora kuba intandaro y'urupfu rw'abagabo.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye ni abagabo, naho 72% by'abahitanywe na COVID-19 ni abagabo.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika nta mibare igaragaza igitsina ku COVID-19 ikora.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bwa Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na virusi itera SIDA, zigira imibare itandukanye y'ibitsina.
Abakozi benshi mu by'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore, bityo bakaba bafite amahirwe menshi yo kwandura.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje izina ry'ubu burwayi ku mugaragaro ari ryo  COVID-19.
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Bwana Tedros Adanom Gebreyesus, asobanura: CO bisobanura corona, VI  virus, D  uburwayi, kandi 19  umwaka iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye bwa mbere: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Iri zina ryatowe mu rwego rwo kwirinda ko ryerekeza ku gace runaka (urugero: Ubushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa amatsinda y'abantu nk'uko bisabwa n'inama mpuzamahanga ku mazina agamije kwirinda gutukwa. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa severe acute coronavirus respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Mu butumwa bw'abantu bose, OMS ikoresha amagambo virusi ya COVID-19 na virusi itera COVID-19.
Iyo ndwara na virusi ubwayo byitwa koronavirusi.
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byitwaga coronavirus na  Wuhan coronavirus.
Muri Mutarama 2020, mu buryo buhuje n'inama yo mu 2015 ku gukoresha ahantu mu mazina y'indwara na virusi, OMS yasabye gukoresha amagambo Indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV nk'amazina y'agateganyo ya virusi n'indwara.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, amazina yemewe  COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yarasohotse.
Kubera ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibicuruzwa, hari abacuruzi ba serivisi za digitale bacapa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, nk'udupira two mu mazuru, hamwe n'ibice by'imashini za VTE.
Mu bihe nk'ibi, ivuriro ryo mu Butaliyani ryari rikeneye cyane umufuka wo guhumeka, kandi umucuruzi ntiyabashije kuwugeza mu gihe cyari gikenewe, ubwo umwe mu mirimo yo muri ako gace yahinduriwe imiterere, maze ashobora gucapa za fovu 100 zari zikenewe mu ijoro rimwe.
Kuva icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangira, ibitekerezo bitandukanye by'ubuhotozi, amakuru atari yo n'amakuru y'ibinyoma ku nkomoko ya virusi, ingano yayo, kwirinda, kwivuza n'ibindi, byatangiye gukwirakwira kuri interineti ku muvuduko ukabije.
Birashoboka ko abantu bashobora kwanduza izindi nyamaswa.
Ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi ntibyagaragaje ko virusi yanduye ingurube, amasazi n'inkoko.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo rwemewe kuri iyi virusi cyangwa imiti yo kuyivura.
Muri iki gihe, imiryango ya leta, amatsinda y'abanyeshuri n'abashakashatsi mu by'inganda barimo gukora ubushakashatsi ku nkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 ku rwego mpuzamahanga.
Muri Werurwe, OMS yatangije gahunda ya SOLIDARITY Trial, igamije gusuzuma ingaruka z'imiti ine iriho ubu, ifatwa nk'ifasha cyane.
Nta rukingo rwamaze gukorwa rwigeze rubaho, ariko imiryango itandukanye irimo gukora cyane ku buryo haboneka urukingo.
SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi binjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu binyuze mu cyuma cyakira ACE2, bityo ubushakashatsi bukoresha ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe kuri SARS-CoV.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi bifuza gukora urukingo rufite virusi zose.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba idafite ubuzima cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu ubasha guhangana n'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, gukora urukingo rw'udupira, ni ugukora urukingo rwongerera ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya udupira tw'ubwoko runaka bwa virusi.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubwo bushakashatsi bugamije gusenya poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi kwinjira mu cyuma cyakira ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu  ni ugushyiraho inkingo zishingiye kuri nucleic acides (DNA cyangwa RNA-inkingo, uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza zakozwe hakurikijwe ubwo buryo bwose zigomba kugeragezwa ku mutekano n'ubushobozi. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, i Seattle hatangiye igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ku bantu bane bitangiye gukora.
Uru rukingo rufite kode y'imiterere idahumanye yakuwe muri virusi itera indwara. Kwongera ingufu z'umubiri wanduye byashyizwe ku rutonde rw'ibibazo bishobora kuvuka mu gukora inkingo za SARS-COV-2, ariko icyo gitekerezo kiravuguruzanya.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 biri gukorwa.
Imiti yemewe kuvura malariya yagenzuwe mu igerageza irindwi, ine muri zo zari ku muti wa hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Gusubiza mu buryo imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi ni byo bituma ubushakashatsi bwinshi bw'Abashinwa bukorwa; mu mpera za Mata, ibihugu byinshi byari bimaze gukora ubushakashatsi icyenda bw'icyiciro cya III cya Remdesivir.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari igishushanyo mbonera cy'iterambere ry'inkingo n'imiti ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19 cyakozwe. Hari n'indi miti ya virusi ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19 irimo Remdesivir, Chloroquine na Hydroxychloroquine, Lopinavir/Ritonavir, na Lopinavir/Ritonavir ikoreshwa hamwe na Interferon beta, iri gusuzumwa mu rwego rumwe.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hari amakuru y'ibanze ku bijyanye n'ingaruka za Remdesivir.
Iterambere mu buvuzi ryagaragaye mu barwayi bahawe remdesivir nk'uko bisanzwe.
Icyiciro cya III cy'igeragezwa mu buvuzi kirimo kirakorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ikoreshwa rya chlorokhine, yari isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, ryatangiye gusuzumwa mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, kandi hari ibisubizo bya mbere.
Nyamara, hari hakenewe ko ubushakashatsi bushimwa n'impuguke.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'igihugu cya Koreya n'ubw'Ubushinwa bwemeza ko chlorine ikoreshwa.
Ikigo cya Wuhan cya Virology gitanga urugero rw'igarama imwe ku munsi, ariko kivuga ko kongera iyo dosiye kabiri ari ibintu biteje akaga kandi bishobora guhitana umuntu.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa ry'imiti ya hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu bihe by'impanuka, ku bushake bw'abaganga bavura abarwayi ba COVID-19. Amabwiriza y'Ubushinwa yo ku ncuro ya 7 kandi agaragaza interféron, ribavirine cyangwa umifenovir nk'imiti yo kurwanya COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibanze byerekana ko ibipimo byinshi bya ribavirini ari ngombwa mu kubuza SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitasoxanide yasabwe kwiga byimbitse in vivo, igaragaza ko ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu rugero rwo hasi. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire binyuze mu guhura n'urwunge rw'imyanya ndangagitsina rwa ACE2, bisaba ko poroteyine ya spine ihuzwa na serine transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2).
Ubushakashatsi ku ikoreshwa rya chlorhexin na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite izo nkingo bufite inzitizi zikomeye zituma umuryango w'abaganga udashobora gukoresha ubwo buryo bwo kuvura hatabanje gukorwa ubushakashatsi bwimbitse. Ozeltamivir ntibuza SARS-CoV-2 in vitro, kandi uruhare rwayo mu kuvura COVID-19 ntiruzwi neza.
Umuntu ashobora kugira ikibazo cy'imyanya ndangagitsina y'inyuma mu gihe cy'indwara ikomeye ya COVID-19.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cy'imyanya ndangagitsina. Ubushakashatsi buto bwakozwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa, bwatumye tosilizumab ishyirwa mu mabwiriza yo kuvura coronavirus.
Uyu muti winjiye mu cyiciro cya 2 cy'igerageza ridakorewe ku buryo bwemewe n'amategeko, rikorerwa ku rwego rw'igihugu mu Butaliyani, nyuma yo kubona ibisubizo byiza ku murwayi ufite indwara ikomeye.
Iyo ikoreshejwe hamwe n'isuzuma ry'amaraso ku bupfumu bwa ferritin kugira ngo hamenyekane ibihuha bya sitokine, iba igamije kurwanya ibintu bivugwa ko bituma abantu bamwe na bamwe bapfa.
Mu 2017, FDA yemeje interleukin-6 receptor antagonist hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwakozwe mu gihe cyashize bwo kuvura indwara yo gusohora sitokine z'ubwoko bwa Steroid Refractory zitangwa n'indi mpamvu, CAR T-cell therapy.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya na kimwe cyakozwe mu buryo butunguranye kandi bugenzurwa cyerekana ko Tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wo kuvura indwara yo kugabanya imisemburo.
Gutanga abasirikare b'umubiri basukuwe kandi bagizweho ingufu z'umubiri w'abarwayi bakira COVID-19 ku bantu babikeneye ubu bifatwa nk'uburyo butari urukingo bwo gukingira abantu.
Ubwo buryo bwakozwe mu kuvura abarwayi ba SARS, ariko nta cyo bwagezeho.
Kugabanya virusi  ni ingaruka yitezwe, aho imiti ya antibody idakora ishobora kurinda SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, hari ubundi buryo bushobora gukoreshwa, nk'ubwandu bw'ingirabuzimafatizo bushingiye ku mubiri na/cyangwa fagocytosis.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura abarwayi, urugero nko gukoresha abarwayi ba monoclonal, buri gukorwa.
Hashobora kongerwa ikoreshwa rya serumu y'amaraso yo gukira, igizwe n'igice cy'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi gifite abasirikare barwanya iyi virusi.
Indwara za Koronavirusi, itsinda ry'indwara zisa cyane
Li Wenliang, umuganga wo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, nyuma yaje kwandura kandi arapfa azize COVID-19 nyuma yo gutangaza ko iyi virusi yanduye.
